var book = {
	"name": "Hesekiel",
	"numChapters": 48,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so aduasa, bosome a ɛtɔ so nnan, da a ɛtɔ so nnum no, berɛ a na mewɔ atukɔfoɔ no mu, Asuo Kebar ho no, ɔsoro bueeɛ, na mehunuu Nyankopɔn hɔ anisoadehunu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bosome no da a ɛtɔ so nnum, (Ɔhene Yoiakin tukorɔ afe a ɛtɔ so nnum mu no),",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> AWURADE asɛm baa Busi ba Ɔsɔfoɔ Hesekiel nkyɛn, wɔ Kaldeafoɔ asase so, Asuo Kebar ho. Ɛhɔ AWURADE nsa baa ne so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na mehwɛe, na hwɛ, ahum bi tu firi atifi fam bae, mununkum kɛseɛ ne ogya a ɛtoatoam, na ɔharan atwa ho ahyia. Na biribi te sɛ sika ne dwetɛ mfrafraeɛ a adɔ ahoa ani firi ogya no mfimfini baeɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na emu na abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ baanan nsɛsoɔ bi firi pueeɛ, na sɛdeɛ wɔn su teɛ nie: Wɔwɔ onipa suban;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> wɔwowɔ anim nnan nnan, na wɔn mu biara wɔ ntaban nnan nnan.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wɔn nan yɛ torodotorodoo, na wɔn nan ase te sɛ nantwie ba tɔte a ɛho hyerɛn sɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ a wɔabere ho dɛhyɛdɛhyɛ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wɔwɔ nnipa nsa, wɔn ntaban ase, wɔn afa nnan no, na wɔn baanan no wowɔ anim ne ntaban sɛɛ:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Wɔn ntaban no toatoa mu; wɔnnanedane wɔn ho wɔn nanteɛ mu; wɔn nyinaa kɔ anim tee.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na sɛ wɔn anim suban no teɛ nie: Wɔn baanan mu biara wɔ onipa anim wɔ anim; wɔn baanan no wɔ gyata anim wɔ nifa; wɔn baanan no wɔ nantwie anim wɔ benkum; na wɔn baanan no wɔ kɔdeɛ anim wɔ wɔn akyi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Sɛ wɔn anim teɛ nie. Wɔn ntaban mu apae firi soro ba fam; wɔn ntaban mmienu mmienu sisi anim, na mmienu mmienu katakata wɔn nipadua ho.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔn nyinaa nenam kɔ wɔn anim tee, deɛ honhom no rekorɔ hɔ na wɔkorɔ, wɔn nanteɛ mu wɔnnanedane wɔn ho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no suban no, ne wɔn su te sɛ nnyansramma a ɛredɛreɛ, sɛ tɛnee; ɛno na ɛnenam abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no ntam, na ogya no hyerɛnn, na anyinam firii ogya no mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no de mmirika redi akɔneaba te sɛ anyinam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na merehwɛ abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no, na hwɛ, na nkyimiiɛ baako si asase so wɔ abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no nkyɛn mu, anim nnan no mu biara deɛ koro.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Nkyimiiɛ no tebea ne ne yɛbea te sɛ sikaberɛboɔ ani, na nnan no kura suban korɔ, na wɔn su ne wɔn yɛbea te sɛ nkyimiiɛ a ɛhyɛ nkyimiiɛ mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sɛ wɔnante a, wɔnam wɔn afa nnan so, wɔnnanedane wɔ wɔn nanteɛ mu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Wɔn hankra korɔn ma no yɛ hu, na aniwa ayeyɛ hankra no ho amaama atwa nnan no nyinaa ho ahyia.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na sɛ abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no nante a, nkyimiiɛ no nso siane wɔn, na sɛ abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no ma wɔn ho so firi fam a, na nkyimiiɛ no nso ama ne ho so.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Baabiara a honhom no dane korɔ no, wɔkɔ; deɛ honhom no bɛkorɔ no, nkyimiiɛ no memaa ne ho so, wɔn nkyɛn mu kɔ bi, ɛfiri sɛ abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no honhom wɔ nkyimiiɛ no mu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Wɔnante a, yeinom nso nante, na sɛ wɔgyina a, yeinom nso gyina, na wɔma wɔn ho so firi fam a, nkyimiiɛ no nso mema wɔn ho so, wɔn nkyɛn mu, ɛfiri sɛ abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no honhom wɔ nkyimiiɛ no mu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na biribi wɔ abɔdeɛ ateasefoɔ no atifi te sɛ ntrɛmu a ɛte sɛ ahwehwɛboɔ a ɛyɛ nwanwa ani a wɔatrɛ mu akatakata wɔn atifi wɔ soro.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔn ntaban tene tee sisi anim, ntrɛmu no ase, na mmienu mmienu nso katakata yeinom ne yeinom nipadua ho.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wɔnante a, na mete wɔn ntaban no gyegyeɛ sɛ asuo bebree gyegyeɛ, sɛ Otumfoɔ nne, huuyɛ gyegyeegye a ɛte sɛ ɛdɔm nne; sɛ wɔgyina a, wɔgyaagyaa wɔn ntaban mu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na ɛnne firi ntrɛmu a ɛwɔ wɔn atifi no so; wɔgyina a, wɔgyaagyaa wɔn ntaban mu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ntrɛmu a ɛwɔ wɔn atifi no soɔ no te sɛ hoaboɔ ahennwa nsɛsoɔ, na ahennwa no nsɛsoɔ so na obi a ɔte sɛ onipa nsɛsoɔ teɛ wɔ soro.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na mehunui, na ɛte sɛ sika ne dwetɛ mfrafraeɛ a adɔ ahoa ani, ɛte sɛ ogya a emu fam hyia, ɛfiri deɛ ɛte sɛ n’asenem de rekɔ soro, nanso ɛfiri deɛ ɛte sɛ n’asenem de reba fam no, mehunui na ɛte sɛ ogya, na ɛhran twa ho hyia.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Sɛdeɛ nyankontɔn a ɛwɔ mununkum mu osutɔ da teɛ no, saa ara na hyerɛn a ɛtwa ho hyia no teɛ. Ɛno ne AWURADE animuonyam hwɛbea no tebea. Na mehunuiɛ no, mehwee ase de m’anim butuu fam, na metee ɛnne a ɛrekasa."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, sɔre gyina wo nan so, na me ne wo nkasa.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔrekasa akyerɛ me no, honhom bi baa me mu, na ɛmaa me so gyinaa me nan so, na metiee deɛ ɔne me kaeɛ no.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, meresoma wo Israel mma nkyɛn, ɔman atuatefoɔ a wɔate m’anim atua no nkyɛn; wɔne wɔn agyanom na afom me de bɛsi nnɛ da yi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wɔyɛ aniɛdenfoɔ a wɔapirim wɔn akoma; me na meresoma wo wɔ wɔn nkyɛn, na woaka akyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sei na AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na sɛ wɔtie oo, wɔantie oo, (ɛfiri sɛ abusua atuatefoɔ ne wɔn nti), ɛnyɛ dɛn ara a, wɔbɛhunu sɛ odiyifoɔ bi aba wɔn mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, nsuro wɔn, na nsuro wɔn nsɛm nso, na nsansono ne nkasɛɛ ne wo na ɛwɔ hɔ, na anyanyankyerɛ ho na woteɛ, nanso nsuro wɔn nsɛm, na mma w’akoma nntu wɔ wɔn anim; na wɔyɛ abusua atuatefoɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wɔtie oo, wɔantie oo, ka me nsɛm kyerɛ wɔn, na wɔyɛ atuatefoɔ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, tie deɛ mereka akyerɛ woɔ yi, nyɛ atuateni sɛ atuatefoɔ fie yi; bae w’anomu, na di deɛ mede merema woɔ yi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mehwɛe, na hwɛ, nsa bi atene hwɛ me so, na hwɛ, na nwoma mmobɔeɛ wɔ mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔtrɛɛ mu wɔ m’anim, na wɔatwerɛ emu ne akyire, na wɔatwerɛ mu kwadwom, apinisie ne mmusuo."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, deɛ wohunu no, di! Di nwoma mmobɔeɛ yi, na kɔ kɔkasa kyerɛ Israel fie.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛnna mebuee m’anomu, na ɔmaa medii nwoma mmobɔeɛ no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, fa nwoma no hyɛ wo yafunu ma. Na medi hyɛɛ me yafunu ma. Na ɛte sɛ ɛwoɔ wɔ m’anomu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, sim kɔ Israel fie nkyɛn, na fa me nsɛm kɔka kyerɛ wɔn.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɛnyɛ ɔman a wɔn kasa mu dɔ na wɔn tɛkyerɛma yɛ duro nkyɛn na wɔasoma woɔ, na mmom Israel fie nkyɛn;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ɛnyɛ aman pii a wɔn kasa mu dɔ na wɔn tɛkyerɛma yɛ duro a wonte wɔn nsɛm nkyɛn, ampa, sɛ wɔn nkyɛn na mesomaa wo a, anka wɔn deɛ, wɔbɛtie wo.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Israel fie mpɛ sɛ wɔtie woɔ, ɛfiri sɛ wɔmpɛ sɛ wɔtie me. Na Israel fie nyinaa moma so ayɛ den, na wɔn akoma apirim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hwɛ, mayɛ w’anim denden wɔ wɔn anim, na mama wo moma so ayɛ den atia wɔn moma so.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mayɛ wo moma so sɛ ahemmoɔ a ɛyɛ den sene twerɛboɔ; nsuro wɔn, na mma w’akoma nntu wɔ wɔn anim, na wɔyɛ atuatefoɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, me nsɛm a mɛka kyerɛ woɔ nyinaa, fa w’akoma gye na fa w’aso tie,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na si mu kɔ atukɔfoɔ, wo man no nkyɛn, na kɔka kyerɛ wɔn, na wɔtie oo, wɔantie oo, se wɔn sɛ: Sei na AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛnna honhom no maa me soɔ, na metee ɔwosoɔ kɛseɛ nne wɔ m’akyiri sɛ: Nhyira ne AWURADE animuonyam firi deɛ ɔteɛ hɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na metee ateasefoɔ no ntaban a ɛtwitwi mu no nne, ne nkyimiiɛ a ɛwowɔ wɔn nkyɛn mu no nne, ne ɔwosoɔ kɛseɛ nne.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na honhom no maa me so faa me kɔe, na mekɔɔ no nwononwono mu, me honhom anibereɛ no mu, na AWURADE nsa yɛɛ me so den.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na mebaa Tel-abib atukɔfoɔ a wɔtete Asuo Kebar ho no nkyɛn deɛ wɔteɛ hɔ no, na metenaa hɔ nnanson, na me ho dwirii me wɔ wɔn mu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na nnanson twaa mu no, AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Onipa ba, mede wo masi Israel fie wɛmfoɔ; enti tie m’anomu asɛm na bɔ wɔn kɔkɔ ma me.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Sɛ mese ɔbɔnefoɔ sɛ: Wuo na wobɛwuo, na woammɔ no kɔkɔ, na woankasa ankyerɛ no, antwe ɔbɔnefoɔ no amfiri n’akwammɔne so, na wannya nkwa a, ɛnneɛ ɔno ɔbɔnefoɔ no bɛwu n’amumuyɛ mu deɛ, nanso ne mogya deɛ mɛbisa no wɔ wo nsam.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na sɛ wobɔ ɔbɔnefoɔ no kɔkɔ, na wansane amfiri ne bɔne no mu ne n’akwammɔne no so a, ɔbɛwu n’amumuyɛ mu, na wo deɛ, woagye wo kra.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Bio, sɛ ɔteneneeni sane firi ne tenenee mu na ɔyɛ abusudeɛ a, mede suntidua bɛto n’anim, na wawu. Sɛ woammɔ no kɔkɔ a, ɔbɛwu ne bɔne no mu, na wɔrenkae n’adetenenee a ɔyɛeɛ no; na ne mogya deɛ, wo nsam na mɛbisa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nanso sɛ wobɔ ɔteneneeni kɔkɔ, sɛdeɛ ɛbɛyɛ na ɔteneneeni bi renyɛ bɔne, na ɔno nso anyɛ bɔne a, nkwa na ɔbɛnya, ɛfiri sɛ watie kɔkɔbɔ, na wo nso woayi wo kra.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na AWURADE nsa baa me so wɔ hɔ, na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Sɔre firi adi kɔ bonhwa no mu, na me ne wo nkɔkasa wɔ hɔ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛnna mesɔre firi kɔɔ bonhwa no mu, na hwɛ, na AWURADE animuonyam no gyina hɔ sɛ animuonyam a mehunuu no Asuo Kebar ho no; na mede m’anim butuu fam.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na honhom no bɛhyɛnee me mu maa megyinaa me nan so, na ɔne me kasae, ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Kɔ na kɔto wo ho mu hyɛ wo fie.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, hwɛ, wɔde nhoma bɛgu wo so de akyekyere wo, na worentumi mfiri adi nkɔ wɔn mu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na wo tɛkyerɛma nso, mɛma no afam wo dodo mu, na woatɔre mum, na woanyɛ wɔn ɔkasakyerɛfoɔ, ɛfiri sɛ wɔyɛ atuatefoɔ fie.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na sɛ me ne wo rebɛkasa a, mɛbue w’ano na woaka akyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sei na AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ. Ma ɔtefoɔ nte, na ogyaefoɔ nnyae; na wɔyɛ asowuiɛ fie."
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wo onipa ba, fa ntaayaa to w’anim, na kurukyire so kuro a ɛne Yerusalem,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ka no hyɛ mu, na to aban wɔ ho, na bɔ ho pie, na kyere ho nsraban hyia, na fa ɔfasuobuo afidie sisi ho hyia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na wo nso, fa dadeɛ ayowa, na fa yɛ dadeɛ fasuo, wo ne kuro no ntam, na dane w’ani kyerɛ no, na ɛnni ntekamu, na tua no; ɛno nyɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ mma Israel fie.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na wo deɛ, da wo mfe benkum so, na mede Israel fie amumuyɛ bɛto wo so; ɛnna dodoɔ a woda soɔ no, na wobɛsoa wɔn amumuyɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na me deɛ, mede wɔn amumuyɛ mfeɛ no mayɛ nna dodoɔ mama wo, nna ahasa aduɔkron na wobɛsoa Israel fie amumuyɛ no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wowie yeinom a, sane da wo mfe nifa so soa Yuda fie amumuyɛ adaduanan; mede afe baako biara mayɛ wo da koro.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na dane w’ani kyerɛ Yerusalem nkahyɛmu no a wo nsa ho da hɔ, na hyɛ nkɔm gu ne so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na hwɛ, mede nhoma bɛgu wo so, na woantwa adafa amfiri wo mfe so ankɔ wo mfe so, de bɛkɔ akɔsi sɛ wobɛwie wo nkahyɛmu nna no ansa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wo deɛ, fa ayuo ne atokoɔ ne asɛ ne asedua ne kɔkɔte ne aburoo hyɛ adeɛ baako mu fa, na fa yɛ w’aduane di nna dodoɔ a wode bɛda wo mfe soɔ no, ɛne nna ahasa aduɔkron;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na w’aduane a wobɛdie no, kari nnwetɛbena aduonu da koro, fa firi berɛ mu kɔsi berɛ mu di.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na nsuo nso susu na nom, susutoa nkyɛmu nsia mu baako, na nom firi berɛ mu kɔsi berɛ mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na di no atokoɔ ɔfam a wode sɛbeɛ a ɛfiri onipa mu atoto, wɔn anim.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na AWURADE kaa sɛ: Saa ara na Israelfoɔ bɛdi wɔn aduane a ɛho akum, amanaman a mɛsum wɔn akɔ hɔ no mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛnna mese: Ao, AWURADE Nyankopɔn, hwɛ, me kra ho nkumii, na adeɛ a atɔ anaasɛ wɔtete mu nso, mennii bi da, de firi me mmɔfraase bɛduru sɛsɛɛ, nanso ɛnam a wɔkyire bi nkaa m’ano da.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Hwɛ, mede nantwie bini masi onipa sɛbeɛ ananmu ama wo, na woato wo paanoo wɔ so.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, hwɛ, paanootoɔ bɛtwam wɔ Yerusalem, na wɔadi paanoo nkariiɛ so ne nhwɛyie mu, na nsuo nso wɔanom no nsusuiɛ ne ahodwirie so,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na paanoo ne nsuo ho ahia wɔn, na wɔn ho adwiri wɔn, onipa ne ne nua ho, na wɔatete wɔ wɔn amumuyɛ mu."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wo onipa ba, fa nkrantɛ nnamnnam na fa yɛ oyifoɔ yiwan na fa yi w’atifi ne wo bɔgyesɛ, na fa nsania kari nwi no, na kyɛ mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nkyɛmu mmiɛnsa mu baako, fa ogya hye wɔ kuro no mfimfini, berɛ a nkahyɛmu nna no awie duro no, na fa afena bobɔ ho hyia. Na nkyɛmu mmiɛnsa mu baako nso fa pete mframa mu, na mɛtwe nkrantɛ madi akyire.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na fa emu kakraa bi a ne dodoɔ sua kyekyere w’atadeɛ ano.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na fa emu bi bio, na to gu ogya mu, fa ogya hye: Ɛno mu na ogya bɛfiri aba Israel fie nyinaa so.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Yei ne Yerusalem, mede no asi amanaman ntam, na nsase atwa ne ho ahyia.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔte m’atemmudeɛ atua di abɔnefosɛm sene amanaman no, ne m’ahyɛdeɛ nso, sene nsase a atwa ne ho ahyia no; na wɔapo m’atemmudeɛ, na wɔannante m’ahyɛdeɛ mu:",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛno nti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ modii asɛmmɔne sene amanaman a wɔatwa mo ho ahyia, na moannante m’ahyɛdeɛ mu, na moayɛ m’atemmudeɛ, na moanyɛ sɛ amanaman a wɔtwa mo ho hyia no atemmudeɛ mpo no,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ɛno nti, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne wo anya, na mɛbu wo atɛn, amanaman no anim.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɛsiane w’akyiwadeɛ nyinaa nti, mɛyɛ wo deɛ menyɛɛ bi da, na merenyɛ ne nsɛsoɔ bio.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Enti wo mu na agyanom bɛdi mma nam, na mma adi wɔn agyanom nam, na mabu wo mu atɛn, na mabɔ wo nkaeɛ nyinaa apete mframa nyinaa ano.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Enti sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa ara, ɛsiane sɛ wode w’atantanneɛ nyinaa, ne w’akyiwadeɛ nyinaa agu me kronkronbea ho fi nti, me nso mɛpra wo, na m’ani renni wo ho adɔna, na me nso merenhunu mmɔbɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Wo mu nkyɛmu mmiɛnsa mu baako bɛwuwu owuyadeɛ ano, na ɛkɔm bɛdwerɛ wɔn wo mu, na nkyɛmu mmiɛnsa mu baako bɛtotɔ nkrantɛ ano atwa wo ho ahyia, na nkyɛmu mmiɛnsa mu baako nso, mɛbɔ wɔn apete mframa nyinaa mu, na matwe nkrantɛ madi wɔn akyi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na m’abufuo bɛwie na mama m’anibereɛ adwo wɔn so, na me werɛ akyekye; na sɛ meyɛ m’anibereɛ no so adeɛ wɔn so a, wɔahunu sɛ me, AWURADE, makasa me ninkuntwe mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mɛyɛ wo amamfo ne ahohora, amanaman a wɔatwa wo ho ahyia mu, wɔn a wɔtwam nyinaa anim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na wɔbɛyɛ ahohora ne yea, asotwe ne ahodwire ama amanaman a wɔatwa wo ho ahyia no, ɛberɛ a mɛbu wo mu atɛn, abufuo ne anibereɛ ne anibereɛ animka mu no, me AWURADE na maka.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛberɛ nso a mede ɛkɔm agyan bɔne bɛtoto wɔn ama ɔsɛeɛ aba no, deɛ mɛtoto sɛ mede meresɛe mo, na mɛma ɛkɔm adɔɔso mo so, na mabu mo paanoo dua no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na mɛma ɛkɔm ne mmoa bɔne aba mo so, na wɔama woadi mmasugya, na owuyadeɛ ne mogya bɛfa wo mu, na mede nkrantɛ bɛba wo so; me, AWURADE, na maka."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, fa w’ani kyerɛ Israel mmepɔ, na hyɛ nkɔm tia wɔn,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ka sɛ: Mo Israel mmepɔ, montie AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn ka kyerɛ mmepɔ ne nkokoɔ, nsubɔnhwa ne mmonhwa nie: Hwɛ mede nkrantɛ mereba mo so mabɛsɛe mo sorɔnsorɔmmea,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na mo afɔrebukyia adane afo, na wɔabubu mo aduhwam adum no, na mama mo atɔfoɔ agugu mo abosom ahoni anim,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na mede Israelfoɔ afunu magu wɔn abosom anim, na mabɔ mo nnompe apete mo afɔrebukyia ho ahyia.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mo tenabea nkuro nyinaa bɛdane amamfo, na sorɔnsorɔmmea no bɛdane ahodwirideɛ, sɛdeɛ ɛbɛyɛ na mo afɔrebukyia adane afo ne ahodwirideɛ, na wɔabubu mo abosom ahoni asɛe no, na wɔatwitwa mo aduhwam adum, na wɔagu mo nneyɛɛ no.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na atɔfoɔ bɛhwehwe ase mo mu, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nanso mɛgya mo mu ebinom a wɔbɛfiri nkrantɛ ano aka, amanaman mu, berɛ a wɔbɛbɔ mo apete nsase soɔ no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mo mu nnipa a wɔbɛfiri mu afire no, bɛkae me, amanaman a wɔafa wɔn nnommum kɔ hɔ no mu, sɛ mabubu wɔn adwamammɔ akoma a atwe afiri me ho, ne wɔn ani a ɛdi wɔn abosom akyiri adwamammɔ mu no; na wɔn ara wɔn ho bɛyɛ wɔn nwunu, nnebɔne a wɔayɛ, wɔn akyiwadeɛ nyinaa mu no ho.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔbɛhunu sɛ mene AWURADE; ɛnyɛ ɔkwa na maka sɛ mɛyɛ wɔn bɔne yi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Bɔ wo nsam, na fa wo nan pempem fam, na ka sɛ: Ao, Israel fie akyiwadeɛ bɔne nyinaa nti wɔnnue, sɛ wɔbɛtotɔ nkrantɛ ne ɛkɔm ne owuyadeɛ ano.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Deɛ ɔwɔ akyirikyiri bɛwu owuyadeɛ ano, na deɛ ɔbɛn nso bɛtɔ nkrantɛ ano, na deɛ waka ne deɛ wɔakora no no bɛwu ɛkɔm ano, na m’anibereɛ bɛwie wɔn so.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na mobɛhunu sɛ mene AWURADE, sɛ wɔn atɔfoɔ bɛdeda wɔn abosom ahoni ntam, atwa wɔn afɔrebukyia ho ahyia, nkokoɔ a ɛkorɔn nyinaa so ne mmepɔ atifi nyinaa ne nnua frɔmfrɔm nyinaa ase ne adum akusukusuu nyinaa ase, deɛ wɔhye hɔ aduhwam ma wɔn abosom ahoni nyinaa no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mɛtene me nsa atia wɔn, na mɛyɛ asase no afo ne ahodwirideɛ asene Ribla serɛ so, wɔn tenabea nyinaa mu, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Wo onipa ba, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn ka kyerɛɛ Israel asase nie: Awieeɛ! awieeɛ na ɛreba asase no ntwea nnan soɔ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Afei awieeɛ reba wo so, na mɛsoma m’abufuo aba wo so, na mabu wo w’akwan ho ntɛn, na mede w’akyiwadeɛ nyinaa bɛba wo so.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na m’ani renni wo ho adɔna, na merenhunu wo mmɔbɔ, na w’akwan na mɛma no aba wo soɔ, na w’akyiwadeɛ atena wo mu, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Adebɔne, adebɔne baako bi, hwɛ, ɛreba!",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Awieeɛ aba, awieeɛ no aba, asɔre atia wo, hwɛ ɛreba!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Asase soteni, deɛ wɔahyɛ no reba wo so; ɛberɛ no aduru, ɛda no abɛn, hooyɛ berɛ, na ɛnyɛ mmepɔ so anigyeɛ huro!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Afei ɛrenkyɛre na mahwie m’abufuhyeɛ agu wo so, na mawie m’abufuo wo mu, na mabu wo w’akwan ho atɛn, na mɛtea wo wɔ w’akyiwadeɛ nyinaa ho.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na m’ani rennodo wo ho, na merenhunu wo mmɔbɔ; w’akwan ho ntea na mede bɛma woɔ, na w’akyiwadeɛ atena wo mu, na moahunu sɛ me, AWURADE na mebobɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hwɛ, ɛda no nie, hwɛ, ɛreba; deɛ wɔahyɛ no refifi, aban no refefɛ, ahantan no ahanehane.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Atiritirasɛm asɔre ayɛ abɔnefosɛm abaa; wɔn ne wɔn asafo yuu ne wɔn hooyɛ no mu hwee nka, na yie biara nni wɔn mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛberɛ no aba, ɛda no rebɛn; mma ɔdetɔfoɔ ani nnnye na ɔdetɔnfoɔ nnni abooboo, na abufuhyeɛ no aba n’asafo yuu nyinaa so;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na ɔdetɔnni, sɛ ɔda so te ase nso a, ɔrensane mma deɛ watɔn no ho, na adehunu a ɛfa n’asafo yuu nyinaa ho no rensane, na obiara remfa n’amumuyɛ nhyɛ ne nkwa mu den.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Wɔhyɛne totorobɛnto na wɔsiesie ade nyinaa deɛ, nanso deɛ ɔkɔ ɔsa nni hɔ; na m’anibereɛ ba wɔn asafo yuu nyinaa so.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nkrantɛ wɔ mfikyire, na owuyadeɛ ne ɛkɔm wɔ efie. Deɛ ɔwɔ wiram bɛwu nkrantɛ ano, na deɛ ɔwɔ kuro mu no, ɛkɔm ne owuyadeɛ bɛkum no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wɔn mu adwanefoɔ firi mu a, wɔbɛkɔ akɔtena mmepɔ so, na wɔn nyinaa ayɛ sɛ mmonhwa mu mmuburo a wɔsisi apini, obiara n’amumuyɛ ho.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nsa nyinaa mu bɛgogo, na nkotodwe nyinaa ahono sɛ nsuo;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na wɔafirafira ayitoma, na awɔse agu wɔn so; na aniwuo akata anim nyinaa, na wɔn nyinaa atifi bɛpa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Wɔbɛtoto wɔn dwetɛ agugu mmorɔno so, na wɔn sika adane sɛ sumina; wɔn dwetɛ ne wɔn sika rentumi nnye wɔn AWURADE abufuo da no mu, wɔremfa mma wɔn kra mmee, na wɔremfa nhyɛ wɔn ayamdeɛ mu mama, ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛɛ wɔn amumuyɛ ho suntidua.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔn ahokekadeɛ fɛfɛ no, wɔde dii ahantansɛm, na wɔde yɛɛ wɔn akyiwadeɛ mfonini, wɔn atantanneɛ no, ɛno nti na mɛma no adane efi ama wɔn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na mede bɛhyɛ ananafoɔ nsa, na wɔafom, ne asase so abɔnefoɔ nsa, na ayɛ wɔn asadeɛ, na wɔagu ho fi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na mɛdane m’ani afiri wɔn so, na wɔagu m’akoradeɛ ho fi, na adwotwafoɔ bɛhyɛne mu agu ho fi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Yɛ nkɔnsɔnkɔnsɔn! Na mogya ho atemmuo ayɛ asase no ma, na atirimuɔden ahyɛ kuro no ma;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> enti mede amanaman nnipa bɔne bɛba, na wɔbɛfa wɔn afiafi afa, na mɛtwa ahoɔdenfoɔ ahantan to ma wɔagu wɔn akronkronneɛ ho fi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ɔsɛeɛ reba; na wɔhwehwɛ asomdwoeɛ, nso ebi nni hɔ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mmusuo pae mmusuo so, akwansosɛm pae akwansosɛm so. Na wɔhwehwɛ odiyifoɔ hɔ adehunu, na mmara bɔ ɔsɔfoɔ, na afotuo bɔ mpanimfoɔ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ɔhene di abooboo, na ɔberempɔn fira ahodwirie, na asase no so aman aba mu abu. Wɔn akwan ho adeɛ na mɛyɛ wɔn, na wɔn atemmudeɛ na mede bɛbu wɔn atɛn, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so nsia, bosome a ɛtɔ so nsia, da a ɛtɔ so nnum a mete me fie na Yuda mpanimfoɔ tete m’anim no, AWURADE Nyankopɔn nsa tɔɔ me so wɔ hɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na mehwɛe, na hwɛ, onipa suban bi a ɛte sɛ ogya nie, ɛfiri deɛ ɛte sɛ n’asene mu de rekɔ fam yɛ ogya, na ɛfiri n’asene mu de rekɔ soro no te sɛ ɔhyerɛn, ɛte sɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ a adɔ ahoa ani.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔyii biribi a ɛte sɛ nsa nsɛsoɔ, na ɔsɔɔ m’atifi nwi mu, na honhom no maa me so faa asase ne ɔsoro ntam de me kɔɔ Yerusalem, Nyankopɔn anisoadehunu no mu, de me baa emu fam ponkɛseɛ a ɛkyerɛ atifi fam no ano, deɛ ninkuntwe honi bi a ɛyi ninkunu sie hɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na hwɛ, na Israel Nyankopɔn animuonyam wɔ hɔ sɛ adeɛ a mehunuu no bonhwa no mu no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, ma w’ani so kɔ atifi fam ɛ! Na memaa m’ani so kɔɔ atifi fam, na hwɛ, afɔrebukyia ponkɛseɛ no atifi fam na ninkuntwe honi no sie wɔ aboboano.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, wohunu deɛ wɔreyɛ yi? Akyiwadeɛ akɛseɛ a Israel fie reyɛ wɔ ha yi, sɛ memfiri me kronkronbea menkɔ akyirikyiri. Na wobɛsane ahunu akyiwadeɛ akɛseɛ bio.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔde me baa abannwa so pono ano, na mehwɛe, na hwɛ, na tokuro baako wɔ ɔfasuo no mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, bɔne fasuo no mu tokuro ɛ! Na mebɔnee ɔfasuo no mu tokuro, na hwɛ, ɛpono bi nie.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Hyɛne mu kɔhwɛ akyiwadeɛ bɔne a wɔreyɛ no wɔ ha.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna mehyɛnee mu mekɔhwɛeɛ, na hwɛ, mmoa a wɔwea ne mmoa ahodoɔ a wɔkyire nyinaa ne Israel fie abosom ahoni nyinaa na wɔakurukyire wɔ wɔn ɔfasuo no ho ahyia yi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na mmarima aduɔson a wɔfiri Israel fie mpanimfoɔ mu a Safan ba Yaasania gyina wɔn mu gyinagyina wɔn anim, na wɔn aduhwamhyeɛ kukuo kurakura wɔn nsam, na aduhwamhyeɛ wisie no hwa sɔree.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, wohunu deɛ Israel fie mpanimfoɔ reyɛ no esum mu, wɔn ahoni mpia mu mmaako mmaako? Ɛfiri sɛ wɔka sɛ: AWURADE nhu yɛn, AWURADE agya asase no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Wobɛsane ahunu akyiwadeɛ akɛseɛ a wɔreyɛ bio.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me baa AWURADE fie ponkɛseɛ a ɛkyerɛ atifi fam no ano, na hwɛ, ɛhɔ na na mmaa teteɛ resu Tamus.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, woahunu? Wobɛsane ahunu akyiwadeɛ akɛseɛ a ɛsene yeinom bio.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me baa AWURADE fie mu fam abannwa soɔ, na hwɛ, AWURADE asɔredan ano, ntwonoo ne afɔrebukyia no ntam no, mmarima aduonu nnum a wɔn akyiri kyerɛ AWURADE asɔredan na wɔn anim kyerɛ apueeɛ resɔre owia nie.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, woahunu yei? Ɛyɛ hare ma Yuda fie sɛ wɔyɛ akyiwadeɛ a wɔyɛ no ɛha yi, sɛ wɔde atirimuɔden rehyɛ asase yi so ma, na wɔasane abɛhuru me boɔ? Na hwɛ, wɔde duban no ka wɔn hwene.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na me nso, mɛdi no anibereɛ so; m’ani renni ho adɔna, na merenhunu mmɔbɔ; na wɔde nne kɛseɛ bɛsu agu m’aso mu deɛ, nanso merentie wɔn."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na ɔde nne kɛseɛ teaa mu guu m’aso mu sɛ: Ma kuro no so ahwɛfoɔ ntwe mpini, na obiara mfa n’akodeɛ a ɔde sɛe adeɛ nkura ne nsam.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na hwɛ, mmarima baasia firi atifi ponkɛseɛ a ɛkyerɛ atifi fam kwan no so reba, wɔn kɔdiawuo nnadeɛ kurakura wɔn nsam, na ɔbarima baako wɔ wɔn mu a ɔhyɛ nwera, na ɔtwerɛfoɔ toa bɔ n’asene, na wɔbaa mu bɛgyinaa kɔbere mfrafraeɛ afɔrebukyia no ho.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na Israel Nyankopɔn animuonyam no firii Kerub a ɛwɔ soɔ no so baa ɛdan no pono ano, na ɔfrɛɛ ɔbarima a ɔhyɛ nwera atadeɛ a ɔtwerɛfoɔ toa bɔ n’asene no,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ no sɛ: Sene fa kuro no mu, Yerusalem mu na hyɛ nnipa a wɔsisi apini di akyiwadeɛ a wɔyɛ wɔ mu no ho abooboo no nyinaa moma so agyiraeɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na wɔn a aka no, ɔka guu m’aso mu sɛ: Monkɔdi n’akyi mfa kuro no mu, na monkunkum; mommma mo ani nnnodo ho, na monnhunu mmɔbɔ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nkɔkoraa, mmeranteɛ ne mmabaa ne mmɔfra ne mmaa, monkum wɔn nsɛe wɔn; na obiara a wɔahyɛ no agyiraeɛ no deɛ, monnka no; na me kronkronbea hɔ na momfiri aseɛ. Ɛnna wɔfirii aseɛ, firi mpanimfoɔ a wɔwɔ efie no anim no soɔ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Mongu efie no ho fi, na momfa atɔfoɔ nhyehyɛ abannwa no so ma ma; momfiri adi! Na wɔfirii adi kɔkunkumm wɔ kuro no mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wɔkunkumm no, ɛkaa me nko ara. Na mede m’anim butuu fam, na meteaa mu sɛ: Ao, AWURADE Nyankopɔn, woresɛe Israel nkaeɛ nyinaa wɔ w’abufuhyeɛ a worehwie agu Yerusalem soɔ no mu anaa?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Israel ne Yuda fie amumuyɛ no yɛ kɛseɛ pa ara, na mogya ayɛ asase no so ma, na ntɛnkyea ayɛ kuro no ma; na wɔka sɛ: AWURADE agya asase no, na AWURADE nhunu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Enti me nso m’ani renni ho adɔna, na merenhunu mmɔbɔ; mede wɔn kwan bɛbua wɔn atifi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na hwɛ, ɔbarima a wɔhyɛ nwera atadeɛ a ɔtwerɛfoɔ toa bɔ n’asene no de asɛm sane baa sɛ: Mayɛ sɛdeɛ wohyɛɛ me no."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na mehunui, na hwɛ, na ntrɛmu a ɛwɔ Kerubim no atifi no so biribi te sɛ hoaboɔ a wɔhwɛ a, ne suban ne ne tebea te sɛ ahennwa nsɛsoɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ ɔbarima a ɔhyɛ nwera atadeɛ no sɛ: Kɔ nkyimiiɛ no ntam, Kerub no ase hɔ, na fa nnyansramma firi Kerubim no ntam hyehyɛ wo nsam ma ma, na fa pete kuro no so. Na ɔkɔɔ mu wɔ m’anim.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Nso ɔbarima no kɔɔ mu no, na Kerubim no gyinagyina ɛdan no nifa so, na mununkum no ayɛ emu fam abannwa no so ma.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE animuonyam no maa ne ho so firii Kerub no so kɔɔ ɛdan no aponnwa atifi, na mununkum no hyɛɛ ɛdan no ma, na AWURADE animuonyam hyerɛn hyɛɛ abannwa no so ma.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔtee Kerubim no ntaban mu gyegyeɛ no kɔsii ɛho fam abannwa no so, sɛ Onyankopɔn Tumfoɔ a ɔrekasa no nne.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔhyɛɛ ɔbarima a ɔhyɛ nwera atadeɛ no sɛ: Fa ogya firi nkyimiiɛ no ntam, Kerubim no ntam no, ɔkɔɔ mu kɔgyinaa nkyimiiɛ no ho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na Kerub no tenee ne nsa firii Kerubim no ntam de kɔɔ Kerubim no ntam gya no ho, na ɔfaa ebi guu deɛ ɔhyɛ nwera atadeɛ no nsam, na ɔgyee de firii adi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na Kerubim no wɔ biribi a ɛte sɛ nipa nsa wɔ wɔn ntaban ase.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mehunui, na hwɛ, na nkyimiiɛ nnan wowɔ Kerubim no nkyɛn mu, nkyimiiɛ baako wɔ Kerubim no mu biara nkyɛn mu, na nkyimiiɛ no ani te sɛ sikabereɛboɔ ani.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na nnan no nyinaa suban yɛ su korɔ, te sɛdeɛ nkyimiiɛ hyɛ nkyimiiɛ mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnante a, ɛnam n’afanan so, ɛnnanedane wɔ ne nanteɛ mu, na deɛ etire no hwɛ no, ɛdi akyire saa; ɛnnanedane wɔ ne nanteɛ mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔn honam nyinaa ne wɔn akyi ne wɔn nsa ne wɔn ntaban ne nkyimiiɛ no, ani ayeyɛ ɛho ma ma atwa ho ahyia, wɔn baanan no wowɔ wɔn nkyimiiɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nkyimiiɛ no, m’aso mu na wɔtoo no din sɛ: Kyinhyia nkyimiiɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔwowɔ anim nnan nnan; deɛ ɔdi kan no anim yɛ Kerub no deɛ, na deɛ ɔtɔ so mmienu no anim yɛ onipa anim, na deɛ ɔtɔ so mmiɛnsa no anim te sɛ gyata, na deɛ ɔtɔ so nnan no deɛ yɛ ɔkɔdeɛ anim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na Kerubim no memaa wɔn ho so. Yeinom ne ateasefoɔ a mehunuu wɔn Asuo Kebar ho no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Kerubim no nante a, nkyimiiɛ no siane wɔn; na Kerubim no mema wɔn ntaban so sɛ wɔde rema wɔn ho so afiri asase so a, nkyimiiɛ no nso nnane mfiri wɔn nkyɛmu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sɛ wɔgyina a, yeinom nso gyina, na sɛ wɔmema wɔn ho so a, yeinom nso mema ne ho so, ɛfiri sɛ ateasefoɔ no honhom wɔ mu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE animuonyam firii ɛdan no pono ano kɔgyinaa Kerubim no soɔ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na Kerubim no memaa wɔn ntaban so, na wɔmemaa wɔn ho so firii asase so, m’anim, sɛ wɔrefiri adi, na nkyimiiɛ no wowɔ wɔn nkyɛn mu; na wɔkɔgyinaa AWURADE fie apueeɛ fam ponkɛseɛ no ano, na Israel Nyankopɔn animuonyam no wɔ wɔn atifi wɔ soro.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Yeinom ne ateasefoɔ a mehunuu wɔn Israel Nyankopɔn aseɛ, Asuo Kebar ho no, na mehunuu sɛ ɛyɛ Kerubim.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Obiara wɔ anim nnan nnan, na obiara wɔ ntaban nnan nnan, na onipa nsa nsɛsoɔ wowɔ wɔn ntaban no ase.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na wɔn anim nsɛsoɔ ne anim a mehunuu no Asuo Kebar ho no yɛ pɛ. Wɔn nyinaa nante kɔ wɔn anim tee."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na honhom no maa me so de me kɔɔ AWURADE fie no apueeɛ fam ponkɛseɛ a ɛkyerɛ apueeɛ no ano; na hwɛ, na mmarima aduonu nnum gyina ɔponkɛseɛ no ano, na mehunuu Asur ba Yaasania ne Benaia ba Pelatia, ɔman no mu mmapɔmma no, wɔ wɔn mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, yeinom ne mmarima a wɔdwene abususɛm na wotu fo bɔne, kuro yi mu.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wɔse: Berɛ a wɔde sisi adan mpinkyɛnee. Kuro yi ne ɛsɛn no, na yɛne nam no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛno nti, hyɛ wɔn ho nkɔm, hyɛ nkɔm, onipa ba!",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na AWURADE honhom tɔɔ me so, na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Ka, sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Saa na moka, Israel fie, na deɛ ɛba mo adwene mu no, me deɛ, menim.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Moama mo atɔfoɔ adɔɔso kuro yi mu, na mode atɔfoɔ funu ahyehyɛ emu mmorɔno so ma ma.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛno nti, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mo atɔfoɔ a mode agugu mu no, wɔne nam no, na kuro no ne ɛsɛn no, na mo deɛ, wɔbɛyi mo afiri mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nkrantɛ na mosuro, nso nkrantɛ ara na mede bɛba mo soɔ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mɛyi mo afiri mu, na mede mo mahyɛ ananafoɔ nsa, na mɛbu mo atɛn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Nkrantɛ ano na mobɛtotɔ, Israel hyeɛ so na mɛbu mo atɛn, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kuro no renyɛ mo ɛsɛn, na mo nso morenyɛ mu nam; Israel hyeɛ so na mɛbu mo atɛn,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE a moanni m’ahyɛdeɛ soɔ, na moanyɛ m’atemmudeɛ, na amanaman a wɔatwa mo ho ahyia no atemmudeɛ so na modiiɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɛbaa sɛ merehyɛ nkɔm no, Benaia ba Pelatia wui. Ɛnna mede m’anim butuu fam de nne kɛseɛ suu sɛ: Ao, AWURADE Nyankopɔn, wie na worewie Israel nkaeɛ koraa?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Onipa ba, wo nuanom, wo nuanom mpo ne w’abusuafoɔ, ne Israel fie mu nyinaa, ne Yerusalemfoɔ na ka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Momfiri AWURADE ho nkɔ akyirikyiri, yɛn na wɔde asase yi ama yɛn sɛ yɛnni soɔ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛno nti ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛwom sɛ mede wɔn kɔɔ akyirikyiri, amanaman mu, na mebɔɔ wɔn petee nsase so deɛ, nanso mayɛ wɔn kronkronbea kakra, nsase a wɔakɔ soɔ no so.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛno nti ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mɛboa mo ano afiri aman mu, na matase mo afiri nsase a wɔabɔ mo apete soɔ no so, na mede Israel asase no mama mo,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na wɔbɛba hɔ abɛyi emu atantanneɛ nyinaa ne emu akyiwadeɛ nyinaa afiri mu akɔ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mɛma wɔn akoma korɔ, na mede honhom foforɔ mahyɛ wɔn mu, na mayi ɔboɔ akoma no afiri wɔn honam mu, na mama wɔn honam akoma,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na wɔanante m’ahyɛdeɛ mu, na wɔadi m’atemmudeɛ so ayɛ, na wɔayɛ me ɔman, na me nso mayɛ wɔn Onyankopɔn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wɔn a wɔn akoma di wɔn atantanneɛ ne wɔn akyiwadeɛ akyire no deɛ, mede wɔn kwan bɛbua wɔn atifi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛnna Kerubim no memaa wɔn ntaban soɔ, na nkyimiiɛ no di wɔn nkyɛnmu, na Israel Nyankopɔn animuonyam no wɔ wɔn so wɔ soro.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na AWURADE animuonyam no maa ne ho so firii kuro no mu, na ɛkɔgyinaa bepɔ a ɛda kuro no anim no so.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na honhom no maa me so de me kɔɔ Kaldea, atukɔfoɔ no nkyɛn, anisoadehunu mu, Nyankopɔn honhom mu. Na adeɛ a mehunuiɛ no firii me so kɔɔ soro.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na mekaa AWURADE nsɛm a ɔmaa mehunuiɛ no nyinaa kyerɛɛ atukɔfoɔ no."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, wote atuatefoɔ fie, nnipa a wɔwɔ ani a wɔde hunu adeɛ nanso wɔnhunu, na wɔwɔ aso a wɔde teɛ nanso wɔnteɛ;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na atuatefoɔ fie ne wɔn. Na wo, onipa ba, yɛ otukorɔ adeɛ fa, na tu kɔ awia, wɔ wɔn anim, na tu firi wo tenabea kɔ baabi foforɔ, wɔn anim; ebia wɔbɛhunu; na asowuiɛ fie ne wɔn.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na yi wo nnoɔma firi adi sɛ ɔtukorɔ adeɛ awia, wɔn anim, na wo ara deɛ, firi adi anwummerɛ, sɛ atukɔfoɔ kɔ no no.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Tu ɔfasuo no mu tokuro, wɔn anim, na fa mu firi adi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Wɔn anim ara na fa nnoɔma no to wo kɔn ho, na anim biri a, wode afiri adi. Kata w’ani na woanhunu asase no, na mede wo mayɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ mama Israel fie.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnna meyɛɛ saa, sɛdeɛ wɔhyɛɛ me no, meyii me nnoɔma firii adi sɛ otukorɔ adeɛ awia, na anwummerɛ no, mede me nsa tuu ɔfasuo no mu tokuro, na anim rebiribiri no, mede firii adi bɔɔ akɔnkɔn wɔ wɔn anim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn anɔpa sɛ:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Onipa ba, Israel fie, atuatefoɔ fie no, nka nkyerɛɛ wo sɛ: Ɛdeɛn na woreyɛ yi?",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Adesoa yi fa ɔberempɔn a ɔte Yerusalem ne Israel fie a wɔwɔ wɔn mu no nyinaa ho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka sɛ: Mene mo nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ; sɛdeɛ meyɛeɛ no, saa na wɔbɛyɛ wɔn, otukorɔ mu, nnommumfa mu na wɔbɛkorɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɔberempɔn a ɔwɔ wɔn mu no, anim rebirie no, ɔde n’adesoa bɛto ne kɔn ho, na wafiri adi; ɔfasuo mu na wɔbɛtu tokuro sɛ wɔrefa mu afiri adi; ɔbɛkata n’ani na wamfa n’ani anhunu asase no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na mede m’asau bɛgu ne so, na wɔayi no me fidie mu, na mede no akɔ Babel, Kaldeafoɔ asase so. Na ɛno mpo ɔrenhunu, na ɛhɔ na ɔbɛwuo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔn a wɔatwa ne ho ahyia sɛ wɔbɛboa no nyinaa ne n’asafo nyinaa, mɛbɔ wɔn apete mframa nyinaa ano, na matwe nkrantɛ adi wɔn akyi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na sɛ mesunsum wɔn kɔ amanaman mu, na mebɔ wɔn pete nsase so a, wɔbɛhunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na mɛgya wɔn mu nnipa kakraa bi afiri nkrantɛ ne ɛkɔm ne owuyadeɛ ano, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔaka wɔn akyiwadeɛ no nyinaa, amanaman a wɔkɔ hɔ no mu, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Onipa ba, fa ahopopoɔ di w’aduane, na fa ahopopoɔ ne awerɛhoɔ nom wo nsuo.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ka kyerɛ asase no so aman no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn ka no Yerusalemfoɔ a wɔwɔ Israel asase soɔ no ho nie: Wɔde awerɛhoɔ na ɛbɛdi wɔn aduane, na wɔde ahodwirie bɛnom wɔn nsuo, ɛsiane sɛ n’asase adane afo na ne mayɛ abɔ no, ɛsofoɔ nyinaa mmusubɔ no nti.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na nkuro a wɔtete mu no bɛsɛe, na asase no adane afo, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Onipa ba, abebusɛm bɛn na mowɔ no Israel asase so sɛ: Nna no rekyɛ, na adehunu nyinaa reyera?",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Ɛno nti, ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mɛma abebusɛm yi to atwa, na wɔremmu no Israel mu bio; na mmom kasa kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Nna no ne adehunu nyinaa asɛm abɛn.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na adehunu hunu biara ne atorɔ nkɔmhyɛ biara rentena Israel fie bio.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na mene AWURADE, na mɛkasa; asɛm a meka no, na ɛbɛyɛ hɔ, wɔrentwe nkɔ akyiri bio: O atuatefoɔ fie, mo berɛ aso ara, na mɛka asɛm na mɛyɛ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Onipa ba, hwɛ, Israel fie ka sɛ: Adehunu a ɔhunu no bɛba nna bebree akyi, na ɛberɛ a ɛwɔ akyirikyiri ho nkɔm na ɔrehyɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ɛno nti ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Wɔrentwe me nsɛm mu biara nkɔ akyiri bio; asɛm a meka no, wɔbɛyɛ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, hyɛ Israel adiyifoɔ a wɔhyɛ nkɔm no ho nkɔm, na ka kyerɛ wɔn a wɔfiri wɔn ara wɔn tirim hyɛ nkɔm no sɛ: Montie AWURADE asɛm.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Wɔnnue, adiyifoɔ nkwaseafoɔ a wɔdi wɔn honhom akyire na wɔnhunu hwee no.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Israel, w’adiyifoɔ ayɛ sɛ akurofo mu nsakraman.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Momforo nkɔgyinaa ntokuro no mu, na monnyee Israel fie ho ban, sɛ mobɛgyina akono, AWURADE da no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ahuhudeɛ ne atorɔ nkɔmhyɛ na wɔn a wɔka sɛ: AWURADE asɛm nie, no hunu, nso na AWURADE nsomaa wɔn, nanso wɔtwɛn sɛ ɔbɛma wɔn asɛm no aba mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnyɛ ahuhudeɛ na mohunu na atorɔ nkɔm na mohyɛ, sɛ moka sɛ: AWURADE asɛm nie, wɔ berɛ a menkasaeɛ?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛno nti, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛnam sɛ moka ahuhusɛm na mohunu atorɔ anisoadeɛ yi nti, hwɛ, me ne mo anya, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na me nsa bɛba adiyifoɔ a wɔhunu ahuhudeɛ na wɔhyɛ nkɔntorɔ no so: Wɔrentena me man badwa no mu, na wɔrentwerɛ wɔn din Israel fie edintwerɛ no mu, na wɔremma Israel asase so, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE Nyankopɔn.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ, aane ɛfiri sɛ wɔsisi me man ka sɛ: Asomdwoeɛ, na asomdwoeɛ nni hɔ, na ɔman no to fasuo bi, na hwɛ, wɔn deɛ, wɔde hyire sra ho nti,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ka kyerɛ wɔn a wɔde hyire sra ho no sɛ: Ɛbɛhwe ase! Osuo a ɛsram soɔ bɛba, na asukɔtweaa bɛtotɔ, na kyinhyia mframa bɛbɔ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na hwɛ, ɔfasuo no bɛhwe ase. Wɔrenka nkyerɛ mo sɛ: Ɛhe na sra a mosraa ho no wɔ?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ɛno nti, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mɛma kyinhyia mframa abɔ wɔ m’abufuhyeɛ mu, na osuo a ɛsram soɔ aba wɔ m’abufuo mu, na asukɔtweaa aba anibereɛ mu abɛwie.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mɛdwiri fasuo a mode akaadoo kaa ho no agu ama no aka fam, na ne nnyinasoɔ ada adi, na ahwe ase, na moadwerɛ wɔ mu, na moahunu sɛ, mene AWURADE.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na mɛwie m’abufuhyeɛ, ɔfasuo ne wɔn a wɔde hyire sraa ho no so, na maka akyerɛ mo sɛ: Ɔfasuo no nni hɔ bio, na wɔn a wɔsraa ho no nso nni hɔ bio,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Israel adiyifoɔ a wɔkaa Yerusalem ho adiyisɛm, sɛ wɔhunuu asomdwoeɛ adeɛ maa no, nanso asomdwoeɛ biara nni hɔ no, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wo, onipa ba yi w’ani sa wo man mmaa a wɔfiri wɔn adwene mu hyehyɛ nkɔm no, na hyɛ wɔn ho nkɔm sɛ:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Monnue, mo mmaa a mopempam nkataho ma nsa akwaa nyinaa, na mopam nnuku ma etire ahodoɔ nyinaa, sɛ mode reyi akra. Moyi me man akra, na mo ara mo kra deɛ, mogye no nkwa?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mogu me ho fi, me man mu, atokoɔ nsa ma ma ne paanoo afono ma bi nti, sɛ mode atorɔ a modi kyerɛ me man a wɔtie atorɔ no rekum akra a ɛnni kum, na moregye akra a wɔnnsɛ nkwa no nkwa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛno nti, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne nkaberɛ a mode reyi akra sɛ nnomaa no anya, na mɛtete afiri mo basa ho, na magyaa akra no, akra a moyi wɔn no, ama wɔatutu akɔ sɛ nnomaa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na mɛtete mo nnuku, na mayi me man afiri mo nsa mu, na wɔantena mo nsa mu sɛ ahayɛdeɛ bio, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ mode atorɔ ma ɔteneneeni a, me deɛ, menhyɛ no awerɛhoɔ no akoma tutuo, na mohyɛ ɔbɔnefoɔ nsa mu den, sɛdeɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wansane amfiri ne kwammɔne so na wannnya nkwa nti,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> morenhunu anisoadeɛ huhuo bio, na nkɔm nso morenhyɛ bio; na mɛyi me man afiri mo nsa mu, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na Israel mpanimfoɔ mu bi baa me nkyɛn bɛtenaa m’anim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Onipa ba, mmarima yi de wɔn abosonhunu ahyɛ wɔn akomam, na wɔde wɔn amumuyɛ suntidua asisi wɔn anim. Memma wommisa me hɔ biribi mma wɔn?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Enti kasa kyerɛ wɔn na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Obiara a ɔfiri Israel fie a ɔde n’abosonhunu hyɛ n’akomam na ɔde n’amumuyɛ suntidua si n’ani soɔ, na ɔba odiyifoɔ nkyɛn no, me, AWURADE, mɛbua no ho bi, n’abosonhunu no dodoɔ so,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na masɔ Israel fie no mu, wɔn akoma mu, sɛ wɔde wɔn abosonhunu no nyinaa ate wɔn ho afiri me ho no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Enti ka kyerɛ Israel fie sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Monsane na monnane mo ho mfiri mo abosonhunu no ho, na monnane mo ani mfiri mo akyiwadeɛ no nyinaa ho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na obiara a ɔfiri Israel fie, anaa ɔhɔhoɔ a wabɛyɛ Israel mu ɔhɔhoɔ no mu, na wawae afiri me ho, na ɔde n’abosonhunu hyɛ n’akoma mu, na ɔde n’amumuyɛ suntidua si n’ani soɔ, na ɔba odiyifoɔ nkyɛn bɛbisa no me hɔ adeɛ no, me AWURADE, me ara na mɛbua no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mɛma m’ani asa onipa no, na mɛdwiri no ama no ayɛ nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ ne akasabebuo, na matwa no afiri me man mu, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na sɛ odiyifoɔ no ma wɔdaadaa no na ɔka asɛm bi a, ɛnneɛ me, AWURADE, na madaadaa odiyifoɔ ko no, na mɛtene me nsa wɔ ne so asɛe no afiri me man Israel mu,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na wɔasoa wɔn amumuyɛ no; sɛdeɛ ɔdebisani no amumuyɛ teɛ no, sɛ odiyifoɔ no amumuyɛ bɛyɛ ne no,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na Israel fie amfom kwan amfiri m’akyiri bio, na wɔamfa wɔn mmarato nyinaa angu wɔn ho fi bio, na wɔayɛ me ɔman, na me nso mayɛ wɔn Onyankopɔn, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Onipa ba, sɛ asase bi yɛ me bɔne di afomfonsɛm bi, na metene me nsa wɔ so, na mebu ne paanoo dua mu, na mema ɛkɔm ba so, na metwa nnipa ne mmoa firi so,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na sɛ mmarima baasa yi, Noa, Daniel ne Hiob wɔ hɔ a, wɔn deɛ, wɔn tenenee ho na wɔbɛgye wɔn kra, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛ mema mmoa bɔne kyini asase no so, na wɔdwerɛ ɛsofoɔ, na ɛdane afo a mmoa no nti obiara ntwam mfa so a,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> sɛ mmarima baasa yi wɔ so a, sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa, mmabanin ne mmammaa mpo, wɔrennye wɔn; wɔn ara nko na wɔbɛgye wɔn, na asase no deɛ, ɛbɛdane afo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Anaasɛ mede nkrantɛ meba asase no so, na mese: Nkrantɛ, fa asase no so, na metwa nnipa ne mmoa firi so a,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na mmarima baasa yi wɔ so a, sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, mmabanin ne mmammaa mpo, wɔrennye wɔn, na wɔn ara nko na wɔbɛgye wɔn.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Anaasɛ mema owuyadeɛ ba asase no so, na mehwie m’abufuhyeɛ gu so, mogya mu, sɛ meretwa nnipa ne mmoa afiri so,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na Noa, Daniel ne Hiob wɔ so a, sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa, wɔrennye ɔbabanin ne ɔbabaa; na wɔn deɛ, wɔn tenenee so na wɔbɛgye wɔn kra.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Na nkantom sɛ mɛma m’atemmudeɛ bɔne nnan, nkrantɛ ne ɛkɔm ne mmoa bɔne ne owuyadeɛ, aba Yerusalem so de atwa nnipa ne mmoa afiri so!",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nanso, hwɛ, nnipa a wɔbɛfiri mu afire bɛka wɔn mu, mmammarima ne mmammaa, wɔde wɔn bɛfiri adi; hwɛ, wɔbɛfiri adi aba mo nkyɛn, na moahunu wɔn abrabɔ ne wɔn nneyɛɛ, na moakyekyere mo werɛ, bɔne a mede baa Yerusalem soɔ, adeɛ a mede baa soɔ no nyinaa ho.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na sɛ mohunu wɔn abrabɔ ne wɔn nneyɛɛ a, wɔbɛkyekyere mo werɛ, na moahunu sɛ ɛnyɛ ɔkwa na meyɛɛ adeɛ a meyɛɛ no wɔ wɔn mu no nyinaa, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, ɛdeɛn na bobe dua de sene nnua nyinaa, bobe homa a ɛwɔ wira mu nnua mu no?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Wɔfa mu dua de yɛ adwuma bi, anaasɛ wɔfa mu bi yɛ pɛɛwa, sɛ wɔde adeɛ biara bɛsɛne soɔ?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hwɛ, wɔde gu ogya mu, na ahye: Sɛ ogya ahye ano mmienu, na mfimfini ahye a, ɛfata adwuma bi yɛ anaa?",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hwɛ, ɛda so di mu no, wɔamfa anyɛ hwee, na nkantom sɛ ogya ahye no dwɛɛ yi, na wɔde bɛyɛ biribi bio anaa?",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Enti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Sɛdeɛ bobe dua teɛ wɔ kwaeɛ mu nnua mu, a mede mema ogya ma no hyeɛ no, saa na mede Yerusalemfoɔ bɛma,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na mɛyi m’ani masa wɔn; wɔfiri ogya mu, na ogya ara na ɛbɛhye wɔn, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE, m’ani a meyi mesa wɔn no mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mɛma asase no adane afo, ɛfiri sɛ wɔadi afomfonsɛm, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, ma Yerusalem nhunu n’akyiwadeɛ no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn ka kyerɛ Yerusalem nie: W’ase ne w’awoɔ asase ne Kanafoɔ asase so, w’agya yɛ Amorini, na wo na yɛ Hetini.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na w’awoɔ mu deɛ, da a wɔwoo woɔ no, wɔantwa wo funuma, na wɔamfa nsuo annware wo amma wo ho amfi, nkyene nso wɔamfa ansra wo, na wɔamfa ntoma ankyekyere wo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Obiara yam anhyehye no amma wo anyɛ wo yeinom mu biara amfa anhu wo mmɔbɔ, na wɔtoo wo twenee ɛserɛ so, too wo kra ho pe, da a wɔwoo woɔ no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna mebɛsianee wo ho na mehunuu woɔ, sɛ wɔabɔ wo adapaa, wo mogya mu, na meka mekyerɛɛ wo, wo mogya no mu, sɛ: Nya nkwa!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Meyɛɛ wo dodoɔ pɛnhunuano sɛ wiram mfefɛeɛ, na wodɔre yɛɛ kɛseɛ, na w’ahoɔfɛ boroo so, wo mpokua bobɔe na wo nwi fui; nanso na woda adagya, nam kwaterekwa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mebɛsianee wo ho na mehunuu wo, na hwɛ, ɛyɛ wo berɛ, ɔdɔ berɛ; na mede me ntaban metrɛɛ wo so, na mekataa w’adagya so, na mekaa wo ntam, na me ne wo yɛɛ apam, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, na woyɛɛ me deɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mede nsuo dwaree wo, na mehohoroo wo ho mogya no, na mesraa wo ngo;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na mede atadeɛ a wɔadi mu adwini hyɛɛ wo, na mede sukraman nwoma mpaboa hyɛɛ wo, na mede nwera pa kyekyeree wo, na mede serekye ntoma kataa wo ho;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na mede ahyehyɛdeɛ hyehyɛɛ wo, na mede nkapo hyehyɛɛ wo nsa, na mede nkɔnmuadeɛ guu wo kɔn mu,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na mede adwinneɛ hyɛɛ wo hwene mu, na mede asomuadeɛ hyehyɛɛ wo, na mede abotire fɛfɛ bɔɔ wo.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔde sika ne dwetɛ hyehyɛɛ wo ho, na wo ntadeɛ yɛ nwera pa ne serekye ne nkyeremu; esiam ne ɛwoɔ ne ngo na wodiiɛ, na wo ho yɛɛ fɛ pa ara, na wodii yie kɔduruu ahennie mu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na w’ahoɔfɛ nti wo din trɛtrɛ kɔɔ amanaman mu, ɛfiri sɛ m’animuonyam a mede hyɛɛ woɔ no maa no wiee fɛyɛ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nanso wode wo ho too w’ahoɔfɛ so, na wobɔɔ adwaman guu wo din so, na wohwiee w’adwamammɔ guu obiara a ɔretwam so; ne no daeɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wofaa wo ntadeɛ no bi de yɛɛ nsaasaawa wɔ sorɔnsorɔmmea hɔ fae, na wobɔɔ so adwaman, nnoɔma a ɛte saa bi mmaa da, ɛrenyɛ saa nso.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wofaa wo nnwinneɛ fɛfɛ no, me sika ne me dwetɛ a memaa woɔ no bi, na wode yɛɛ mmarima ahoni fae, na wode bɔɔ adwaman;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> na wode wo nkyeremu ntadeɛ kataa wɔn ho, na wode me ngo ne m’aduhwam sisii wɔn anim.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na m’aduane a memaa woɔ, esiam ne ngo ne ɛwoɔ a mede meyɛnee woɔ no, wode sisii wɔn anim sɛ ɛnyi hwa hwamhwam. Deɛ ɛyɛeɛ nie, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wofaa wo mmabanin ne wo mmammaa a wowo maa me no de wɔn bobɔɔ afɔdeɛ maa wɔn sɛ wɔnni. W’adwamammɔ yɛ ade ketewa,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> sɛ wokunkumm me mma na woyii wɔn maeɛ maa wɔfaa ogya mu maa wɔn no?",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na w’akyiwadeɛ ne w’adwamanneɛ nyinaa mu no, woankae wo mmabaaberɛ nna no a na woda adagya na wonnam kwaterekwa bɔ wo ho adapaa, wo mogya mu no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wo nnebɔne nyinaa akyiri no, wo ara, (due, due! AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie),",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> wotoo dampan faeɛ na woyɛɛ pampa faeɛ, mmɔntene nyinaa soɔ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nkwantia nyinaa wotoo wo pampa, na woguu w’ahoɔfɛ no ho fi, na wobaee w’ananmu maa obiara a ɔsene, na womaa w’adwamammɔ dɔɔso.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na wo ne Misraim mma a wɔte wo ho a wɔn honam soso no bɔɔ adwaman, na womaa w’adwamammɔ dɔɔso de huruu me bo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na hwɛ, wo so na metenee me nsa, na metee w’aduane a mehyɛeɛ soɔ, na meyii wo mae sɛ w’atamfo, Filistifoɔ mmammaa a wɔn ani wuu w’ahohwibɔ ho no pɛ no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Nso wo ne Asiria mma bɔɔ adwaman, ɛfiri sɛ na wommee. Na wo ne wɔn bɔɔ adwaman, nanso woammee.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nso womaa w’adwamammɔ dɔɔso kɔduruu Kanaan asase a ɛne Kaldea, na yei nso ammee wo.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Sɛdeɛ w’akoma asi ahodwo afa, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, sɛ wɔyɛɛ yeinom a ɛyɛ ɔbaa dwamamfoɔ a ɔso ne tire no nneyɛɛ no nyinaa!",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Wotoo wo dampan, akwan nyinaa tia, na woyɛɛ pampa, mmɔntene nyinaa soɔ no, woanyɛ sɛ odwamamfoɔ mpo, ɛne sɛ wopoo apɛdeɛ.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ɛyerɛ a ɔsɛe awadeɛ, ɔfa ananafoɔ si ne kunu ananmu.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Nnwamamfoɔ nyinaa, wɔma wɔn akyɛdeɛ, na wo deɛ, wode w’akyɛdeɛ kyekyɛ w’adɔfoɔ nyinaa, na woma wɔn adanmudeɛ, sɛ wɔmfiri mmaa nyinaa mmra wo nkyɛn adwamammɔ.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Enti wo deɛ, woyɛ sononko wɔ mmaa a aka no wɔ adwamammɔ mu: Sɛ obi nhyɛ da mmɛpɛ wo ne wo mmɔ adwaman, na wo na woma apɛdeɛ; na wo deɛ, obi mma wo apɛdeɛ, enti na woyɛ sononko no.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ɛno nti, odwamamfoɔ, tie AWURADE asɛm!",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ wɔhwiee wo ho fi guiɛ, na wɔayi w’adagya soɔ, w’adwamammɔ mu, ama w’akyiwadeɛ abosonhunu no nyinaa ne wo mma a wode wɔn maa wɔn no mogya nti,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> hwɛ, merehyiahyia w’adɔfo a woafam wɔn ho no nyinaa ne wɔn a woadɔ wɔn nyinaa mabɔ wɔn a woatane wɔn no nyinaa so. Ɛfiri afa nyinaa na maboaboa wɔn ano atia wo, na mayi w’adagya adi akyerɛ wɔn, na wɔahunu w’adagya nyinaa.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na mede mmaa awaresɛefoɔ ne mogyakagufoɔ atemmudeɛ bɛbu wo atɛn, na mayɛ wo abufuhyeɛ ne ninkuntwe mogya,",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> na mede wo ahyɛ wɔn nsa, na wɔadwiri wo dampan, na wɔaburi wo mpampa, na wɔaworɔ wo ho ntadeɛ, na wɔafa wo nnwinneɛ fɛfɛ no, na wɔagya wo adagya ne kwaterekwa mu,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> na wɔama wɔabɛbɔ wo so dwa, na wɔasi wo aboɔ, na wɔde wɔn nkrantɛ atwitwa wo mu,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> na wɔde ogya ahye w’adan, na wɔde w’atemmuo mu adeɛ ayɛ wo, mmaa bebree ani so, na mama woagyae adwamammɔ; na akyɛdeɛ nso, worenkyɛ bio.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na mɛma m’abufuhyeɛ no adwo wɔ wo ho, na me ninkuntwe afiri wo so, na mɛyɛ komm a me bo renhuru bio.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ wonkaee wo mmabaaberɛ mu nna no, na wode yeinom ha me nti, na me nso, hwɛ, mede w’abrabɔ bua w’atifi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, na mammɔ w’akyiwadeɛ nyinaa so mmusuo.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Hwɛ, obiara a ɔbubu mmɛ no bɛbu wo ho bɛ yi sɛ: Sɛdeɛ ɛna teɛ na ne ba teɛ.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Wo ne wo na a ɔpo ne kunu ne ne mma no ba, na wo ne nuammaanom a wɔpo wɔn kununom ne wɔn mma no nuabaa; mo na yɛ Hetini, na mo agya yɛ Amorini.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Na wo nuabaa panin ne Samaria, ɔno ne ne mmammaa a wɔte wo benkum soɔ no, na wo nuabaa kumaa a ɔte wo nifa soɔ ne Sodom ne ne mmammaa.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Nso woamfa wɔn akwan so na wɔyɛɛ wɔn akyiwadeɛ no nko, na mmom ɛyɛɛ kakraa bi pɛ, na wosɛe senee wɔn, w’akwan nyinaa so.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa, wo nuabaa Sodom ne ne mmammaa anyɛ sɛdeɛ wo ne wo mmammaa ayɛ yi.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Hwɛ, yei ne wo nuabaa Sodom amumuyɛ no: Ahantan, adidimeeɛ ne yiedie dwoodwoo mu na ɔno ne ne mmammaa tenaeɛ, na mmɔborɔni ne ohiani nsa deɛ, wansɔ mu;",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> na wɔyɛɛ ahantan yɛɛ akyiwadeɛ wɔ m’anim, na meyii wɔn hɔ sɛdeɛ me ara mepɛ.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Na Samaria anyɛ wo bɔne no mu fa, na womaa w’akyiwadeɛ dɔɔso senee wɔn, na wode w’akyiwadeɛ a woyɛeɛ no nyinaa buu wo nuammaanom bem.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Wo nso, soa w’ahohora a wobu maa atɛn maa wo nuammaanom no. Wo bɔne a woama no ayɛ akyiwadeɛ asene wɔn no nti, wɔtene sene wo, na wo nso, ma w’ani nwu na soa w’ahohora, sɛ woabu wo nuammaanom bem.",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> Na mede wɔn nnommum, Sodom ne ne mma nnommum, ne Samaria ne ne mmammaa nnommum, ne wo nnommumfa mu nnommum a ɛwɔ wɔn mu no bɛsane aba,",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na woasoa w’ahohora, adeɛ a woayɛ nyinaa ho de akyekyere wɔn werɛ.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Na wo nuammaanom, Sodom ne ne mmammaa bɛsane aba wɔn kane dibea mu, na Samaria ne ne mmammaa bɛsane aba wɔn kane dibea mu, na wo nso wo ne wo mmammaa bɛsane aba mo kane dibea mu.",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> Na wo nuabaa Sodom anyɛ w’anomu asɛnka, w’ahantan nna no mu,",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> ansa na wɔreyi wo bɔne adie, sɛ ɛberɛ a Siria mmammaa ne wɔn a wɔtwa ne ho hyia nyinaa, Filistifoɔ mmammaa a wɔyi wo ahi no sopaa wo, afa nyinaa no.",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> W’abusudeɛ ne w’akyiwadeɛ no, wo ara na woso, AWURADE asɛm nie.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Meyɛ wo sɛdeɛ woyɛeɛ no ara a, wobuu ntanka animtia sɛ worebu apam soɔ no.",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Na me deɛ, mɛkae m’apam a me ne wo pamm no wo mmabaaberɛ mu no, na mɛma daa apam atim hɔ ama wo.",
			"61": "<sup>61</sup> Na sɛ mede wo nuammaanom a wɔsene wo panin ka wo nuammaanom a wɔyɛ w’akyiri mma no ho de wɔn meyɛ wo mmammaa a ɛnnyina m’apam no so a, ɛno na wobɛkae w’akwan na w’ani awu.",
			"62": "<sup>62</sup> Na me na mɛma me ne wo apam no agyina, na woahunu sɛ, me ne AWURADE,",
			"63": "<sup>63</sup> deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na woakaeɛ, na w’ani awuo, na w’aniwuo nti woammue w’ano bio, sɛ makata deɛ woyɛeɛ no nyinaa so mama woɔ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, to aborɔme no ka mfatohosɛm yi kyerɛ Israel fie,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɔkɔdeɛ kɛseɛ bi, a ɔwɔ ntaban akɛseakɛse, ne ntakra atenteneatentene, ntakra nworanworan ayɛ ne ho ma, baa Lebanon bɛbuu tweneduro nkona.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ne nkɔnmu mu ban na ɔpaneeɛ, na ɔde kɔɔ adwadie asase bi so, ɔkɔtɛɛ no adwadifoɔ kuro bi mu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔfaa asase no so aba bi de kɔduaa asase pa bi mu, ɔde sii nsuo bebree ano, ɔtɛɛ no sɛ nsunoa dua.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɛfifirii yɛɛ bobe a ɛdennaneeɛ a ɛhwihwa fam ma ne mman tenetene baa ne ho, na ne nhini wɔ n’ase; na ɛyɛɛ bobe na ɛyiyii mman na ahahan baa so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Nso na ɔkɔdeɛ kɛseɛ foforɔ bi wɔ hɔ, ne ntaban akɛseakɛse, na ne ntakra bebree. Na hwɛ, bobe no firi n’akofie a wɔtɛɛ no wɔ mu no mu tentene, ne nhini kɔɔ ne fam, na ɛyiyii ne mman kɔɔ ne so, sɛ ɔmma no nsuo.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Afu pa so ne nsuo bebree ho na ɔtɛeɛ, sɛ ɛnyiyi mman, na ɛnso aba, na ɛnyɛ bobe fɛfɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛbɛyɛ yie? Ɔrentutu ne nhini, na ɔntwitwa n’aba na atwintwam? Ahahan a ɛfefɛeɛ no nyinaa bɛtwintwam, na ɛnyɛ basa kɛseɛ anaa ɛdɔm bebree na wɔde bɛsɔ ne nhini mu atu no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na hwɛ, wɔatɛ no yi, ɛbɛkye? Berɛ a apueeɛ mframa bɛka no no, ɛnyɛ kusa na ɛbɛkusa anaa? Akofie a ɛfifirii soɔ no so na ɛbɛtwintwam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ka kyerɛ asowuiɛ fie no sɛ: Monhunu adekodeɛ a yei yɛ? Ka sɛ: Hwɛ, Babel hene baa Yerusalem, na ɔbɛfaa emu hene ne emu asafohene, na ɔde wɔn kɔɔ ne nkyɛn Babel.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔfaa ahennie asefoɔ no mu obi, na ɔne no pamee, na ɔmaa no kaa no ntam, (na asase no so atumfoɔ no deɛ, ɔfaa wɔn kɔe),",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> sɛ ɛnyɛ ahennie a wɔabrɛ no aseɛ, na amma ne ho so bio, na ɔnni apam no so na ɛnnyina.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nanso ɔtee n’anim atua somaa n’abɔfoɔ maa wɔkɔɔ Misraim, sɛ wɔmma no apɔnkɔ ne ɛdɔm bebree. Ɛbɛsi no yie anaa? Deɛ ɔyɛ yeinom bɛfiri mu afi anaa? Ɔbɛsɛe apam no na wafa ne ho adi anaa?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa ara, ɔhene a ɔsii no hene a wammu ne nseɛ no, na wabu n’apam soɔ no tenabea, ne nkyɛn hɔ wɔ Babel, na ɔbɛwuo.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɛnyɛ ɛdɔm kɛseɛ ne asafo bebree na Farao de bɛdi ama no. Ɛsa mu wɔbɛto epie na wɔasisi aban atentene de atwa nnipa pii agu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛfiri sɛ, wammu ntam no na ɔbuu apam so; na hwɛ, wadi nse, nanso wayɛ yeinom nyinaa. Ɔremfiri mu mfi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Enti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, ampa ara, me ntam a wammuo ne m’apam a wabu soɔ no na mede bɛbua n’atifi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na mɛtrɛ m’asau ne so, na wɔayi no me fidie mu, na mede no akɔ Babel, na fom a ɔfom me no, me ne no bɛdi wɔ hɔ;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na n’adwanefoɔ a ɛwɔ n’asafo nyinaa, nkrantɛ ano na wɔbɛtotɔ, na wɔn a wɔaka no, wɔbɛbɔ wɔn apete mframa nyinaa mu, na moahunu sɛ me, AWURADE, na maka.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Me nso mɛbu tweneduro a ɛkorɔn no nkona mu bi akɔtɛ, ne mfefɛeɛ mu tire bɛtɛbɛtɛ no bi na mɛpan makɔdua no bepɔ a ɛkorɔn na ɛwareɛ bi so;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Israel bepɔ sorɔnsorɔn so na mɛdua no, na ɛbɛyiyi mman aso aba, na ayɛ tweneduro kunini, na nnomaa nyinaa, ntakraboa nyinaa abɛsisi aseɛ; ne mman nwunu mu na wɔbɛsisie.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na wiram nnua nyinaa ahunu sɛ me, AWURADE, na mabrɛ dua bantenn no aseɛ, na mama dua a ɛhwihwa fam akorɔn, mama duamono adwan na mama duawuiɛ afefɛ. Me, AWURADE, na maka, na mayɛ."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Mokyerɛ sɛn, sɛ mobu bɛ yi Israel asase so sɛ: Agyanom twɛre abunu, na mma se fem, a?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa ara, moremmu bɛ yi Israel mu bio.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hwɛ, akra nyinaa wɔ me. Sɛ agya kra wɔ me no, sɛ ɔba nso kra wɔ me ne no; ɔkra a ɔyɛ bɔne no, ɔno ara na ɔbɛwuo.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na sɛ onipa yɛ ɔteneneeni, na ɔyɛ atemmudeɛ ne ateneneedeɛ,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ɔnni afɔreduane mmepɔ no so, na ɔmma n’ani so nhwɛ Israel fie ahoni huhuo no, na ɔngu ne yɔnko yere ho fi na ɔnkɔ ɔbaa a wayɛ bra ho,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na ɔnhom obi so, na ɔde ɔkafoni awowasideɛ sane ma, ɔnyɛ ɔpempensini, ɔde n’aduane ma deɛ ɔdi kɔm na ɔfira ɔdagyani ntoma,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ɔmmɔ bosea na ɔnnye nsiho, na ɔtwe ne nsa firi abusudeɛ ho, na ɔbu onipa ne onipa ntam atɛntenenee,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na ɔnam m’ahyɛdeɛ mu, na ɔdi m’atemmudeɛ so di nokwasɛm a, ɔno na ɔteneneeni ne no; nkwa na ɔbɛnya, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na sɛ ɔwɔ ɔba korɔmfoɔ a ɔka mogya guo, na ɔyɛ yeinom mu baako pɛ,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na ɔno ara deɛ ɔnnyɛ nnoɔma yeinom biara, (wanyɛ yeinom mu biara), na sɛ nso ɔdi afɔreduane mmepɔ no so, na ɔgu ne yɔnko yere ho fi,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na ɔhom mmɔborɔni ne ohiani so, ɔyɛ ɔpempensideɛ nso ɔnnane mma, na ɔma n’ani so hwɛ ohoni huhuo yɛ akyiwadeɛ,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na ɔbɔ bosea na ɔgye nsiho a, ɔbɛnya nkwa anaa? Aane, ɔrennya nkwa! Wayɛ akyiwadeɛ yi nyinaa, wuo na ɔbɛwuo, ne mogya bɛbua n’atifi.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na hwɛ ɔwo ɔba, na ɔno deɛ, ɔhunu n’agya bɔne a ɔyɛ nyinaa, na ɔsuro, na ɔnyɛ saa bi,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na ɔnni afɔreduane mmepɔ no so, na ɔmma n’ani so nhwɛ Israel fie ahoni huhuo, na ɔngu ne yɔnko yere ho fi,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na ɔnhom obi so, na ɔnnye awowasideɛ nsie, na ɔnyɛ ɔpempensini, na ɔde n’aduane ma deɛ ɛkɔm de no, ɔfira ɔdagyani ntoma,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> na ɔsianka ne nsa firi mmɔborɔni ho, na ɔnnye mfɛntomu ne nsiho, na ɔyɛ m’atemmudeɛ nam m’ahyɛdeɛ mu a, ɔno deɛ, ɔrenwu n’agya amumuyɛ mu; nkwa na ɔbɛnya.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> N’agya no, ɛnam sɛ wadi amim, asi ne nua apempem, na wayɛ deɛ ɛnyɛ, ne man mu nti hwɛ, ɔbɛwu n’amumuyɛ mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na moka sɛ: Adɛn nti na ɔba nsoa n’agya amumuyɛ bie? Na sɛ ɔba no ayɛ atemmudeɛ ne ateneneedeɛ adi m’ahyɛdeɛ nyinaa so ayɛ a, nkwa na ɔbɛnya.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɔkra a ɔyɛ bɔne no, ɔno na ɔbɛwuo; ɔba rensoa n’agya amumuyɛ bi, na agya nso rensoa ne ba amumuyɛ bi; ɔteneneeni tenenee bɛtena ne so, na ɔbɔnefoɔ abɔnefosɛm bɛtena ne so.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ɔbɔnefoɔ nso, sɛ ɔsane firi ne bɔne a wayɛ nyinaa ho, na ɔdi m’ahyɛdeɛ nyinaa so, yɛ atemmudeɛ a, nkwa na ɔbɛnya, ɔrenwu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ne mmarato adeɛ a ɔyɛeɛ nyinaa, wɔrenkae mma no bio; ne tenenee a wayɛ no mu na ɔbɛnya nkwa.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Pɛ na mepɛ ɔbɔnefoɔ wuo anaa? AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie; ɛnyɛ sɛ ɔsane firi ne kwan soɔ na ɔnya nkwa na mepɛ anaa?",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Nanso sɛ ɔteneneeni sane firi ne tenenee ho kɔyɛ abusudeɛ ne akyiwadeɛ nyinaa a ɔbɔnefoɔ yɛ a, ɔbɛnya nkwa anaa? Ne tenenee a ɔyɛeɛ nyinaa, wɔrenkae; ne fom a wafom ne ne bɔne a wayɛ no mu na ɔbɛwuo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nanso moka sɛ AWURADE kwan ntene. Montie ɛ, Israel fie, me kwan ntene anaa? Ɛnyɛ mo akwan na ɛntene?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Sɛ ɔteneneeni sane firi ne tenenee ho kɔyɛ abusudeɛ, na ɔwu wɔ mu a, n’abusudeɛ a ɔyɛeɛ no mu na ɔwuiɛ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Nso sɛ ɔbɔnefoɔ sane firi n’abɔnefosɛm a wadie no ho bɛyɛ atemmudeɛ ne ateneneedeɛ a, ɔno deɛ, wagye ne kra nkwa.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na sɛ wahunu, na wasane afiri ne mmarato a ɔdiiɛ no nyinaa ho nti, nkwa na ɔbɛnya, ɔrenwu.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nanso Israel fie ka sɛ AWURADE kwan ntene. M’akwan ntene, Israel fie? Ɛnyɛ mo akwan na ɛntene?",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ɛno nti Israel fie, mɛbu mo mo akwan ho atɛn mmaako mmaako, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie. Monsane na monnane mo ho mfiri mo mmaratodeɛ nyinaa ho, na mmusuo anyɛ suntidua amma mo.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Montoto mo mmaratodeɛ a mode too mmara no nyinaa mfiri mo so ngu, na monyɛ akoma foforɔ ne honhom foforɔ mfa. Na adɛn nti na ɛsɛ sɛ mowuo yi, Israel fie?",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na menni deɛ ɔrewuo no wuo ho anigyeɛ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie. Enti monsane, na mommɛnya nkwa."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wo deɛ, twa Israel aberempɔn ho kwadwom",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> na ka sɛ: Adɛn na wo na, gyatabereɛ no butu agyatanini ntam yɛne ne mma gyataburuwa mu?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔyɛnee ne mma mu baako, ɔyɛɛ gyataburuwa na ɔsuaa ahayɔ; ɔdii nnipa nam,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na amanaman tee ne nka, na wɔkyeree no wɔn amena mu, na wɔde hwene mu kaa twee no kɔɔ Misraim asase so.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ne na hunuu sɛ watwɛn, nanso n’anidasoɔ ayera no, ɔfaa ne mma mu bi de no yɛɛ gyataburuwa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔnenam agyata mu no, ɔyɛɛ gyataburuwa, na ɔsuaa ahayɔ; ɔdii nnipa nam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔhunuu wɔn akunafoɔ, na ɔbobɔɔ wɔn nkuro, na ne mmobomu gyegyeegye nti, asase no ne ne mayɛ sɛee.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛnna amanaman a wɔfiri nsase soɔ no ba bɛtwaa ne ho hyiaeɛ, na wɔde wɔn asau trɛɛ ne so, wɔkyeree no wɔ wɔn amena mu,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na wɔde hwene mu kaa hyɛɛ no de no hyɛɛ ebuo mu, na wɔde no kɔmaa Babel hene, na wɔde no siee abankɛseɛ mu, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔnte ne nne bio wɔ Israel mmepɔ soɔ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Anka wo na te sɛ bobeturo mu bobe a wɔatɛ no nsuo ho, nsuo pii nti n’aba ne ne mman baa yie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔnyaa mpoma a na ɛyɛ den na ɛyɛɛ ahemfo mpoma, na ne kɛseyɛ korɔn kɔduruu mununkum kusuu ntam, na wɔhunuu no ne korɔn mu, ne ne mman dodoɔ mu.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔtuu no anibereɛ so too no hwee fam, na apueeɛ mframa kusaa n’aba no; ne mpoma a na ɛyɛ den no bubui na ɛtwintwamee, na ogya hyee.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na afei wɔatɛ no ɛserɛ so, asase pɛsɛɛ a ɛdi sukɔm so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ogya afiri ne mman mpoma bi mu ahye n’aba, na poma a ɛyɛ den a ɛbɛyɛ ahennie poma biara nni hɔ bio. Kwadwom nie, na abɛyɛ kwadwom."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so nson, bosome a ɛtɔ so nnum da a ɛtɔ so du no, Israel mpanimfoɔ no mu binom ba bɛbisaa AWURADE hɔ adeɛ, na wɔbɛtenaa m’anim.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Ɛnna AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Onipa ba, kasa kyerɛ Israel mpanimfoɔ no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Me hɔ adebisa na mobaeɛ yi? Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, ampa ara, meremma wɔmmisa me hɔ adeɛ mma mo, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wobɛbu wɔn atɛn, onipa ba? Wobɛbu wɔn atɛn? Ɛnneɛ ma wɔnhunu wɔn agyanom akyiwadeɛ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛda a mefaa Israel na memaa me nsa so kyerɛɛ Yakob fie asefoɔ, na memaa wɔhunuu me Misraim asase soɔ na memaa me nsa so kyerɛɛ wɔn kaa sɛ: Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn, no.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛda no na memaa me nsa so kyerɛɛ wɔn, sɛ merebɛyi wɔn afiri Misraim asase so de wɔn akɔ asase a mepɛ maa wɔn, a ɛsene nufosuo ne ɛwoɔ, a ɛyɛ nsase nyinaa ahyehyɛdeɛ no so,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na meka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Mo nyinaa montoto mo ani so akyiwadeɛ no ngu, na mommfa Misraim abosonhuhuo nngu mo ho fi; mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na wɔtee me so atua, na wɔampene sɛ wɔtie me; wɔn mu obiara biara anto n’ani so akyiwadeɛ no antwene, na wannya Misraim abosonhuhuo no. Ɛnna mese: Mɛhwie m’anibereɛ agu wɔn so, de awie m’abufuo no wɔ wɔn so, Misraim asase so.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nanso me din nti, meyɛe na ɛho angu fi amanaman a wɔte wɔn mu no anim, wɔn a memaa wɔhunuu me wɔn ani so, sɛ mereyi wɔn afiri Misraim asase so.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna meyii wɔn firii Misraim asase soɔ, na mede wɔn baa ɛserɛ so,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na mede m’ahyɛdeɛ maa wɔn, na memaa wɔhunuu m’atemmudeɛ a sɛ onipa yɛ a, ɔnya mu nkwa no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nanso mede me home nna maa wɔn, sɛ ɛnyɛ me ne wɔn ntam nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ, na wɔnhunu sɛ mene AWURADE a metee wɔn ho no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Israel fie tee m’anim atua ɛserɛ so; wɔanni m’ahyɛdeɛ so na wɔpoo m’atemmudeɛ a sɛ onipa yɛ a, ɔbɛnya mu nkwa no, na me home nna nso, wɔguu ho fi bebree. Ɛnna mese: Merehwie m’anibereɛ agu wɔn so, ɛserɛ so, na madwerɛ wɔn.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nanso me din nti meyɛe na ɛho angu fi, amanaman a meyii wɔn, wɔn anim no anim.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nanso memaa me nsa so kyerɛɛ wɔn, ɛserɛ so sɛ, meremfa wɔn nkɔ asase a memaeɛ a ɛsene nufosuo ne ɛwoɔ a ɛyɛ nsase nyinaa ahyehyɛdeɛ no so,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ɛsiane sɛ, wɔpoo m’atemmudeɛ na wɔannante m’ahyɛdeɛ mu, na wɔguu me home nna ho fi nti; na na wɔn abosonhuhuo no akyi na wɔn akoma die.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nanso mehunuu wɔn mmɔbɔ, na mansɛe wɔn, na manyɛ wɔn pasaa, ɛserɛ no so.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na meka kyerɛɛ wɔn mma, ɛserɛ no so sɛ: Monnnante mo agyanom ahyɛdeɛ no mu, na monnni wɔn atemmudeɛ no so, na mommfa wɔn abosonhuhuo nngu mo ho fi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn, m’ahyɛdeɛ mu na monnanteɛ, na m’atemmudeɛ na monni soɔ na monyɛ,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na monyɛ me home nna no kronkron, na ɛnyɛ me ne mo ntam nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ, na monhunu sɛ mene AWURADE mo Nyankopɔn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na mma no nso tee me so atua, wɔannante m’ahyɛdeɛ no mu, na wɔanni m’atemmudeɛ so anyɛ deɛ onipa yɛ a, ɔbɛnya mu nkwa no; me home nna nso, wɔguu ho fi. Ɛnna mese: Merehwie m’anibereɛ agu wɔn so, na mawie m’abufuo wɔn mu ɛserɛ no so.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nanso mesiankaa me nsa, na me din nti, meyɛe, na ɛho angu fi amanaman a meyii wɔn firii wɔn anim no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Nso mekaa wɔn ntam ɛserɛ no so, sɛ mɛbɔ wɔn apete amanaman mu, na mapansam wɔn agu nsase so,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ɛsiane sɛ wɔanyɛ m’atemmudeɛ na wɔapo m’ahyɛdeɛ, na wɔagu me home nna ho fi, na wɔn ani di wɔn agyanom abosonhuhuo akyiri nti.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na me nso memaa wɔn ahyɛdeɛ a ɛnyɛ ne atemmudeɛ a wɔnnya mu nkwa ho kwan,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na meguu wɔn ho fi, wɔn ayɛyɛdeɛ mu, ne bɔ a wɔde wɔn abakan bɔɔ afɔdeɛ no mu, na masɛe wɔn, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Enti, onipa ba, kasa kyerɛ Israel fie, na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Yei mu nso, mo agyanom kaa abususɛm tiaa me, na wɔfomm me,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ɛfiri sɛ mede wɔn baa asase a mekaa ntam sɛ mede bɛma wɔn no soɔ no, sɛ wɔhunu kokoɔ a ɛkorɔn biara ne dua kusuu biara, na wɔrebɔ wɔn afɔdeɛ wɔ hɔ, na wɔde wɔn ayɛyɛdeɛ a ɛhuru me boɔ no kyɛ wɔ hɔ, na wɔde wɔn hwa hwamhwam ma wɔ hɔ, na wɔhwie wɔn ahwiesa wɔ hɔ.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> (Na meka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: Ɛdeɛn ne sorɔnsorɔnbea a mokɔ hɔ no? Na wɔtoo hɔ din sɛ sorɔnsorɔnbea de bɛsi nnɛ da yi.)",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Enti ka kyerɛ Israel fie sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mo agyanom kwan so na mogu mo ho fi, na wɔn atantanneɛ akyi na mobɔ adwaman die,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> na mode mo ayɛyɛdeɛ ba, na moma mo mma fa ogya mu yi, mogu mo ho fi mo abosonhuhuo nyinaa fam de bɛsi nnɛ yi, na me na wɔmmisa me hɔ adeɛ mma mo anaa? Israel fie! Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa ara, meremma wɔmmisa me hɔ adeɛ mma mo.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na deɛ ɛba mo adwene mo no, ɛrenyɛ hɔ oo! Deɛ moka sɛ: Yɛbɛyɛ sɛ amanaman no, sɛ nsase so mmusua no, na yɛasom dua ne ɔboɔ no.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa ara, mede nsa a ɛyɛ den ne basa a emu atene ne anibereɛ a wɔahwie aguo na ɛbɛdi mo so hene.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na mɛyi mo afiri aman mu, na maboa mo ano afiri nsase a wɔabɔ mo apete hɔ no so, nsa a ɛyɛ den ne basa a emu atene ne anibereɛ a wɔahwie aguo so,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> na mede mo aba aman no serɛ so na mabɛbu mo atɛn wɔ hɔ, anim ne anim.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Sɛdeɛ mebuu mo agyanom atɛn ɛserɛ so wɔ Misraim asase soɔ no, saa ara na mɛbu mo atɛn, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Na mɛma moafa abaa no ase, na mede mo aba apam no nkyehoma mu.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na mɛyiyi mo mu atuatefoɔ ne wɔn a wɔto me mmara no, wɔn ahɔhobea asase no so na mɛyi wɔn, nanso wɔremma Israel asase so, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na mo, Israel fie, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Monkɔ nkɔsom mo abosonhuhuo ɛ, seesei ne daakye, sɛ moantie me a, ɛnneɛ na mommfa mo ayɛyɛdeɛ ne mo abosonhuhuo no ngu me din kronkron no ho fi bio.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na bepɔ kronkron, Israel bepɔ a ɛkorɔn no so, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ɛhɔ na Israel fie nyinaa, wɔn dodoɔ a ɛwɔ asase no soɔ nyinaa bɛsom me; ɛhɔ na wɔbɛsɔ m’ani, na ɛhɔ nso na mɛbisa mo mmasoɔ adeɛ ne mo ayɛyɛdeɛ mu adikanneɛ, mo akronkronneɛ nyinaa mu.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Mobɛsɔ m’ani sɛ ehwa hwamhwam, ɛberɛ a mɛyi mo afiri aman mu no, na maboa mo ano afiri nsase a wɔabɔ mo apete soɔ no, mo mu na mɛma wɔayɛ me kronkron, amanaman no anim.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na mobɛhunu sɛ mene AWURADE, berɛ a mede mo bɛba Israel asase, asase a mekaa ntam sɛ mede bɛma mo agyanom no soɔ no,",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> na ɛhɔ na mobɛkae mo akwan ne mo nneyɛɛ a mode guu me ho fi no nyinaa, na mo ho ayɛ mo nwunu, mo ani so, mo bɔne a moyɛeɛ no nyinaa nti.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na mobɛhunu sɛ mene AWURADE. Me din nti na me ne mo bɛdie, ɛnyɛ mo akwammɔne no so, ne mo nneyɛɛ a asɛeɛ no so, Israel fie, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Onipa ba, fa w’ani kyerɛ anafoɔ fam, ka asɛm kyerɛ anafoɔ fam, na ka adiyisɛm kyerɛ Negeb petee mu kwaeɛ,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> na ka kyerɛ Negeb kwaeɛ no sɛ: Tie, AWURADE asɛm nie: Hwɛ, meresɔ wo mu gya, na ahye wo mu nnua mono nyinaa ne nnua wuiɛ nyinaa. Ogyaframa a ɛdɛre framframfram no rennum, na ahye asase ani nyinaa afiri anafoɔ fam akɔsi atifi fam.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Na honam nyinaa bɛhunu sɛ me AWURADE na mesɔeɛ, ɛrennum.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ɛnna mekaa sɛ: Ao, AWURADE Nyankopɔn, wɔn deɛ, wɔka no ne me ho sɛ: Ɛnyɛ mmɛ na ɔrebubuo yi?"
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, fa w’ani kyerɛ Yerusalem, na ma w’asɛm nsosɔ ngu kronkronbea hɔ na hyɛ nkɔm tia Israel asase no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ka kyerɛ Israel asase no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne wo anya, na mɛtwe me nkrantɛ afiri ne bɔha mu, na matwitwa wo mu ateneneefoɔ ne abɔnefoɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ mɛtwa wo mu ateneneefoɔ ne abɔnefoɔ nti, me nkrantɛ bɛfiri ne bɔha mu atia honam nyinaa, afiri anafoɔ fam akɔsi atifi fam,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na honam nyinaa ahunu sɛ me, AWURADE, matwe me nkrantɛ afiri ne bɔha mu, na ɛrensane nkɔ mu bio.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, fa akoma a abubuo si apini, na gu ahome yaya wɔ wɔn anim.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ wɔbisa wo sɛ: Ɛdeɛn ho na woresi apini a? Ka sɛ: Akwansosɛm ntira, ɛfiri sɛ ɛreba, na akoma nyinaa bɛnane, na nsa nyinaa mu agogo, na honhom nyinaa ano akum, na anankoroma nyinaa adanedane nsuo. Hwɛ, ɛreba na abɛyɛ hɔ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Onipa ba, hyɛ nkɔm, na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Ka sɛ: Nkrantɛ a wɔase ano na wɔapɔ ho nso,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> wɔase ano sɛ ɛnkum, wɔapɔ ho sɛ ɛntwa nyinamnyinam. Ɛbɛyɛ dɛn na yɛama yɛn ho asɛpɛ yɛn? Me ba woabu abaa, ne atenetene nyinaa animtia?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔde maa sɛ wɔmpɔ ho sɛ wɔde nsa rekura, wɔase nkrantɛ no na wɔapɔ ho nso, sɛ wɔde rehyɛ okumfoɔ nsa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Onipa ba, su na twa adwo, sɛ ɛno bɛba me man so, ɛno bɛba Israel aberempɔn nyinaa so; wɔde wɔn ne me man ato hɔ ama nkrantɛ, enti hwe wo srɛ mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na wɔasɔ ahwɛ; na sɛ poma a ɛbu animtia no mpo nyɛ hwee a, ɛdeɛn na ɛbɛyɛ? AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, hyɛ nkɔm na bɔ nsam, na nkrantɛ no bɛba mprenu ne mprɛnsa, atɔfoɔ nkrantɛ no; ɛyɛ ɔtɔfoɔ kɛseɛ nkrantɛ na atwa wɔn ho ahyia no.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na akoma atuo, na suntidua adɔɔso nti, mede nkrantɛ hyerɛn asisi wɔn kuro apono nyinaa ho. Aa! Wɔayɛ no sɛ ɛnyɛ sɛ anyinam, wɔase ano de rebɛkum.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Dane wo ho koraa kɔ nifa, dane w’ano kɔ benkum, baabiara a wɔahyɛ sɛ w’ani nkyerɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na me nso mɛbɔ me nsam, na mama m’anibereɛ ano adwo. Me, AWURADE, na maka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, sensan akwan mmienu fa, na Babel hene nkrantɛ mfa so mmra. Ma ne mmienu nyinaa mfiri asase korɔ so, na kurukyire akyerɛkyerɛkwan bi, nkuro nkwanta na kurukyire no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Siesie ɔkwan a nkrantɛ no mfa so mmra Amonfoɔ kuro Raba ne Yuda kuro a ɛwɔ Yerusalem a ɛyɛ den no mu.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na Babel hene gyina tempɔn nkwanta so, akwan mmienu no ti, sɛ wɔnhyɛ nkɔm mma no, ɔwoso agyan, bisa abusua honi adeɛ, hwɛ mmerɛboɔ mu;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> nkɔmhyɛ a ɛba ne nifa mu ne Yerusalem, sɛ wɔnsisi adwennini a ɛdwiri ɔfasuo, mmue ano okum mu, sɛ wɔnsisi adwennini a wɔde bɛdwiri aponkɛseɛ, ngu epie nsisi ntua aban.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na ɛbɛyɛ wɔn sɛ nkɔntorɔ wɔ wɔn ani so; wɔanka ntankɛseɛ; nanso ɔno deɛ, ɔkae wɔn amumuyɛ, sɛ wɔnkyere wɔn.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛno nti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ momma wɔkae mo amumuyɛ ma mo mmarato da adie na wɔhunu mo bɔne, mo nneyɛɛ nyinaa mu nti, na ɛsiane sɛ wɔkae mo nti, wɔde nsa bɛkyere mo.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wo, ɔbɔnefoɔ a woatɔ, Israel berempɔn a ne da aduro, awieeɛ amumuyɛ berɛ mu no,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Yi abotire no, na tu ahemmotire no; nnoɔma nnkɔ so ara nyɛ saa ara daa. Ma deɛ abrɛ ase so, na brɛ deɛ ama ne ho soɔ no ase.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Nnaneani, nnaneani, nnaneani na mɛdane no. Na yei nso rentena hɔ, de bɛkɔ akɔsi sɛ deɛ atemmuo wɔ no no, ɛbɛba ama no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, hyɛ nkɔm sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn se Amonfoɔ ne wɔn ahohorabɔ no ho nie, na ka sɛ: Nkrantɛ, nkrantɛ a wɔtwe rebɛkum, wɔapɔ ho sɛ ɛnni nam, sɛ ɛnyɛ nyinamnyinam.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ɛberɛ a wɔhunu adehuhuo ma woɔ na wɔrehyɛ wo nkɔntorɔ no, wɔde wo bɛto abɔnefoɔ atɔfoɔ a wɔn da aduro, awieeɛ amumuyɛ berɛ mu no kɔn ho.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Fa wo nkrantɛ sane hyɛ ne bɔha mu, faako a wɔbɔɔ woɔ no, w’awoɔ asase so na mɛbu wo atɛn,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> na mɛhwie m’abufuhyeɛ agu wo so, mɛfite m’anibereɛ gya no mu atia wo, na mɛyi wo ahyɛ mmarima atirimuɔdenfoɔ a wɔnim sɛeɛ ho nyansa no nsa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Wobɛdane ogya mmabowa ama wo mogya agu asase no mfimfini; wɔrenkae wo bio, na me, AWURADE na maka."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, wobɛbu kuro a mogya ayɛ mu ma no atɛn? Ɛnneɛ ma no nhunu n’akyiwadeɛ nyinaa,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Kuro a ɛhwie mogya gu wɔ mu, sɛ ne berɛ mmra, na ɛyɛ abosonhuhuo fa de gu ne ho fi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wo mogya a wohwie guiɛ no mu na wodi so, na w’abosonhuhuo a woyɛeɛ no, na wode agu wo ho fi, na woama wo nna abɛn, na woaduru wo mfeɛ awieeɛ; ɛno nti, mede wo ayɛ ahohoradeɛ ama amanaman, ne fɛdie ama nsase nyinaa;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> wɔn a wɔbɛn woɔ ne wɔn a wɔwɔ akyiri di wo ho fɛw sɛ deɛ ne din ho agu fi, na ne sakasakayɛ dɔɔso.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hwɛ Israel aberempɔn a wɔwɔ mo mu no, wɔn mu biara pɛ sɛ ɔhwie mogya gu sɛdeɛ ne tumi teɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Wo mu na wɔbɔ agya ne ɛna adapaa, wo mu na wɔdi ahɔhoɔ amim, wɔhom wo mu agyanka ne okunafoɔ soɔ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wobu m’akronkronneɛ animtia, na wogu me home nna ho fi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nkontompofoɔ wɔ wo mu, sɛ wɔbɛhwie mogya aguo, na mmepɔ so na wɔbɛhwie mogya aguo, na mmepɔ so na wɔdidie wɔ wo mu, na ahohoradeɛ na wɔyɛ no wo mfimfini.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wo mu na wɔyi agya adagya so; wo mu na wɔkɔ deɛ asakyima ama ne ho akum no ho.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na obi ne ne yɔnko yere yɛ akyiwadeɛ, na obi gu n’ase baa ho fi aniwudeɛ mu, wo mu na obi to ne nuabaa, n’agya ba, mmɔnaa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Wo mu na wɔgyegye adanmudeɛ, sɛ wɔbɛhwie mogya aguo. Wogyegye mfɛmtomu ne nsiho, na wode apempensie fa wo yɔnko so, na me deɛ, wo werɛ afiri me, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na hwɛ, mebɔ me nsamu, w’aniberebereɛ mfasoɔ a wonya, ne wo mogya a ɛwɔ wo mu no ho.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> W’akoma bɛtumi adi anaasɛ wo nsam bɛyɛ den nna a me ne wo bɛdie no? Me, AWURADE, na maka, na mɛyɛ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na mɛbɔ wo apete amanaman mu, na mapansam wo, nsase so, na mɛhye wo fi no koraa afiri wo ho.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wo ho bɛgu fi amanaman anim, na woahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Onipa ba, Israel fie ayɛ me dwetɛ fi. Wɔn nyinaa yɛ me fononoo mu kɔbere mfrafraeɛ ne sanya ne dadeɛ ne sumpii; wɔayɛ dwetɛ bini.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ɛno nti sei na AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ: Ɛsiane sɛ mo nyinaa adanedane dwetɛ fi nti, hwɛ, mereboa mo ano ahyia Yerusalem.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Sɛdeɛ wɔboa dwetɛ, kɔbere mfrafraeɛ, dadeɛ, sumpii ne sanya ano fononoo mu, fite ɛho gya mu ma no nane no, saa ara na mɛboa mo ano, m’abufuo ne m’anibereɛ mu, na mede mo ahyɛ mu anane mo,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> na maka mo abom na masɔ mo ho gya m’anibereɛ mu, na moanane wɔ mu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Sɛ dwetɛ nane fononoo mu no, saa ara na mobɛnane mu, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE a mahwie m’abufuhyeɛ agu mo soɔ no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Onipa ba, ka kyerɛ no sɛ: Woyɛ asase a wɔntee ho, na wɔmmma osuo ntɔ so abohuro da mu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> N’adiyifoɔ atirisopam wɔ so, wɔte sɛ gyata a ɔbobom tete ne hanam, wɔdi onipa nam, wɔfa ahonyadeɛ ne aboɔdenneɛ, wɔma emu akunafoɔ dɔɔso.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> N’asɔfoɔ bu me mmara so, na wɔgu m’akronkronneɛ ho fi; wɔmma no nsono akronkronneɛ ne adeɛ a ɛnyɛ akronkronneɛ, na wɔnkyerɛ adeɛ a ɛho nteɛ ne deɛ ɛho teɛ no ntam nsonsonoeɛ, na wɔbu wɔn ani gu me home nna so, na wɔgu me ho fi wɔ wɔn mu.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ne mmapɔmma a wɔwɔ soɔ no te sɛ mpataku a wɔtete hanam, sɛ wɔbɛhwie mogya aguo, na wɔasɛe akra, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔanya mfasoɔ bɔne adie.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na n’adiyifoɔ sra hyire ma wɔn, wɔhunu adehuhuo na wɔhyɛ wɔn nkɔntorɔ; wɔka sɛ: Sei na AWURADE seɛ, nanso na AWURADE nkasae.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Asase no so nkurɔfoɔ di amim na wɔsi apempem, na wɔhom mmɔborɔni ne ohiani so, na wɔsi ɔhɔhoɔ apempem a ɛntene koraa.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na mehwehwɛɛ wɔn mu bi a ɔbɛgye ban anaasɛ ɔbɛgyina tokuro mu, m’anim ama asase no na mansɛe no, nanso manhunu obiara.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Enti mɛhwie m’abufuhyeɛ agu wɔn so, na madwerɛ wɔn anibereɛ gya no mu, na mede wɔn abrabɔ abua wɔn atifi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, mmaa baanu, ɛna baako mmammaa wɔ hɔ,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na wɔbobɔɔ adwaman Misraim, wɔn mmabaaberɛ mu na wɔbobɔɔ adwaman no; ɛhɔ na wɔmiaa wɔn nufo, na ɛhɔ na wɔkekaa wɔn mmabaaberɛ mu mpokua.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔpanin no ne Ohola, ɔne ne nuabaa Oholiba. Wɔbɛyɛɛ me dea, na wɔwowoo mmammarima ne mmammaa. Ohola din no gyina hɔ ma Samaria, na Oholiba din no gyina hɔ ma Yerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na m’akyi Ohola bɔɔ adwaman na n’ani beree n’adɔfoɔ, Asiriafoɔ a wɔba bɛpinkyɛɛ no no ho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Wɔhyehyɛ bibitoma ntadeɛ, amradofoɔ ne mmakoma, mmeranteɛ a wɔn ho yɛ fɛ nko ara, wɔtete nteaseɛnam mu ne apɔnkɔ so.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔde n’adwamammɔ kɔɔ wɔn so, Asiriafoɔ a wɔasa mu ayi wɔn no nyinaa, na ɔde wɔn a ne kɔn dɔ wɔn nyinaa, wɔn abosom nyinaa guu ne ho fi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nanso n’adwamammɔ a ɔde firi Misraim no, wannyae, ɛfiri sɛ wɔne no dae ne mmabaaberɛ mu, na wɔkekaa ne mmabaaberɛ mu mpokua, na wɔhwiee wɔn adwamammɔ guu ne so.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛno nti mayi no ahyɛ n’adɔfo nsa, Asiriafoɔ a n’ani beree wɔn no nsa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wɔn na wɔyii n’adagya soɔ, wɔfaa ne mmabanin ne ne mmammaa, na ɔno ara nso, wɔde nkrantɛ kumm no, na ɔyɛɛ ɔnokwa maa mmaa, na wɔyɛɛ no n’atemmudeɛ.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ne nua Oholiba hunui, nanso ɔmaa n’ani beree bere bɔne senee ɔno, na ɔmaa n’adwamammɔ senee ne nua no deɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> N’ani beree Asiriafoɔ, amradofoɔ ne mmakoma a wɔba bɛpinkyɛɛ no no, wɔhyehyɛ ntadeɛ twom, wɔtete nteaseɛnam mu ne apɔnkɔ so, mmeranteɛ a wɔn ho yɛ fɛ ara nko.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na mehunuu sɛ wagu ne ho fi; wɔn baanu no nam ɔkwan korɔ so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔmaa n’adwamammɔ kɔɔ so; na ɔhunuu mmarima a wɔakurukyire wɔn ɔfasuo ho, Kaldeafoɔ mfonini a wɔde adukɔkɔɔ akurukyire,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> wɔde abɔsoɔ abobɔ wɔn asene de abotire atentene abobɔ wɔn ti, sɛ Babelfoɔ a wɔn awoɔ asase ne Kaldea no teɛ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ɛnna ɔde n’ani hwɛeɛ no, n’ani beree wɔn, na ɔsomaa abɔfoɔ maa wɔkɔɔ wɔn nkyɛn Kaldea.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na Babelfoɔ baa ne nkyɛn ne no bɛdae ɔdɔ mpa so, na wɔde wɔn adwamammɔ guu ne ho fi; na ɔde wɔn guu ne ho fi no, ɔtee ne kra firii wɔn ho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔyii n’adwamammɔ adie na ɔyii n’adagya soɔ no, ɛnna me kra tee ne ho firii ne ho, sɛdeɛ me kra tee ne ho firii ne nua no ho no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔmaa n’adwamammɔ no dɔɔso ara de kaee ne mmabaaberɛ mu nna a ɔbɔɔ adwaman, Misraim asase soɔ no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na n’ani beree wɔn mpenafoɔ a wɔn mmarima te sɛ mfunumu deɛ, na wɔn ahobaa te sɛ apɔnkɔ deɛ no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na wo kɔn dɔɔ wo mmabaaberɛ mu aniwudeɛ berɛ a wo mpokua nti Misraim miamiaa wo nufo no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛno nti, Oholiba, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, merehwanyan w’adɔfo atia wo, wɔn a wo kra ate ne ho afiri wɔn ho no, na mahyia wɔn afiri mmaa nyinaa aba wo so.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Babelfoɔ ne Kaldeafoɔ nyinaa, Pekodfoɔ, Soafoɔ ne Kaldeafoɔ ne Asiriafoɔ a wɔka wɔn ho nyinaa, mmeranteɛ a wɔn ho yɛ fɛ, amradofoɔ ne mmakoma nyinaa, nnɔmkunini ne wɔn a wɔwɔ din, apɔnkɔsotefoɔ ara nko,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na wɔde akodeɛ ne nteaseɛnam ne nkyimiiɛ ne aman asafo bɛba wo so; ahokatadeɛ ne ɛkyɛm ne dadeɛ kyɛ na wɔde bɛka wo ahyɛ mu ahyia; na mede atemmuo bɛsi wɔn anim, na wɔabu wo atɛn wɔn atemmuo so.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na mede me ninkuntwe bɛsa wo, na wɔne wo adi no anibereɛ so, wɔbɛtwitwa wo hwene ne w’aso, na wo mu nkaeɛ bɛtotɔ nkrantɛ ano; wɔn na wɔbɛfa wo mmabanin ne wo mmammaa akorɔ, na wɔde ogya ahye w’adeɛ a ɛbɛka akyire,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na wɔbɛworɔ wo ho ntadeɛ, na wɔatase wo nnwinneɛ afɛfɛ no.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na mɛma wo aniwudeɛ to atwa afiri wo ho, ne w’adwamammɔ a ɛfiri Misraim asase soɔ no, na woamma w’ani so ankyerɛ wɔn, na woankae Misraim bio.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na sei na AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ: Hwɛ, mede wo bɛhyɛ wɔn a wotane wɔn no nsa, ne wɔn a wo kra ate ne ho afiri wɔn ho no nsa,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> na wɔne wo adi no wɔ ɔtane so, na wɔafa deɛ wobrɛ nyaeɛ no, na wɔagya wo, adagya ne kwaterekwa mu, na wɔayi w’adwamammɔ adagya so ne w’aniwudeɛ ne w’adwamammɔ deɛ nyinaa so.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Wɔbɛyɛ wo yei, w’adwamammɔ a wode dii amanaman no akyire no nti, sɛ wode wɔn abosonhuhuo agu wo ho fi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Wo nuabaa no kwan so na wonam, enti mede ne kuruwa bɛhyɛ wo nsa.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Wo nuabaa kuruwa a emu dɔ na emu trɛ no na wobɛnom mu, dodoɔ a ɛbɛtumi afa no bɛdane asereseredeɛ ne fɛdie;",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> nsaborɔ ne awerɛhoɔ, ahodwire ne ahoyera kuruwa, wo nuabaa Samaria kuruwa no bɛyɛ wo ma.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na wobɛnom, na wobɛfefe mu, na wobɛwe ne ferɛ, na wobɛsunsuane wo nufo mu, na me na maka, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ɛno nti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ wo werɛ afiri me, na woato me atwene w’akyire nti, wo nso soa w’aniwudeɛ ne w’adwamammɔdeɛ no.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, wobɛbu Ohola ne Oholiba atɛn? Ɛnneɛ kyerɛ wɔn wɔn akyiwadeɛ,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> sɛ wɔasɛe awadeɛ, na mogya wɔ wɔn nsamu. Na wɔn abosonhuhuo na wɔde asɛe awadeɛ, na wɔn mma a wɔwo maa me no nso, wɔama wɔafa ogya mu ama wɔn abosom ama wɔadi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Bio yei na wɔayɛ me, wɔagu me kronkronbea ho fi da no ara, na me home nna nso, wɔagu ho fi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na wɔkunkum wɔn mma ma wɔn abosonhuhuo a, wɔba me kronkronbea da no ara bɛgu ho fi, na hwɛ, saa na wɔayɛ no me fie no mu.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na mpo wɔsoma maa wɔkɔhyiaa mmarima a wɔfiri akyirikyiri bae, na wɔsomaa abɔfoɔ maa wɔkɔɔ wɔn nkyɛn, na hwɛ, wɔbae; wɔn na wodwaree wo ho maa wɔn, de adubire kekaa w’ani, na wode ahyehyɛdeɛ hyehyɛɛ wo ho,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> na wɔtenaa nnaeɛ a anim yɛ duro so, na ɛpono a wɔatoɔ si w’anim, na wode m’aduhwan ne me ngo sisii so.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na asafo yuu a wɔato wɔn ho mpan wɔ mu, na wɔde nsabofoɔ kaa nnipa dodoɔ no ho firi ɛserɛ so baeɛ, na wɔde nkapo hyehyɛɛ wɔn nsa, na wɔde abotire afɛfɛ bobɔɔ wɔn.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ɛnna mekaa sɛ: Mmarima mmɔ adwaman sɛ ɔno ara, sɛ wɔkɔ ne ho a!",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na wɔkɔɔ ne ho sɛdeɛ wɔkɔ ɔbaa dwamamfoɔ ho, na saa na wɔkɔɔ Ohola ne Oholiba, mmaa ahohorafoɔ no ho.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na mmarima ateneneefoɔ na wɔde awaresɛefoɔ atemmuo ne mogyakagufoɔ atemmuo bɛbu wɔn atɛn, ɛfiri sɛ wɔyɛ awaresɛefoɔ, na mogya wɔ wɔn nsamu.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mɛma asafo bi atu aba wɔn so, na mayi wɔn ama ahodwan ne ɔfom,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> na asafo no asi wɔn aboɔ, na wɔde wɔn nkrantɛ awowɔ wɔn; wɔbɛkunkum wɔn mmabanin ne wɔn mmammaa, na wɔde ogya ahye wɔn afie.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Na mɛtwa aniwudeyɛ afiri asase no so, na wɔde abɔ mmaa nyinaa kɔkɔ, na wɔanyɛ mo ahohoradeɛ no bi.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Na wɔde mo ahohoradeɛ bɛgu mo so, na moasoa mo abosonhuhuo no ho bɔne, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE Nyankopɔn."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn afe a ɛtɔ so nkron, bosome a ɛtɔ so du no da a ɛtɔ so du no sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, twerɛ da yi din, da yi ara. Babel hene atua Yerusalem da yi ara.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na bu asowuiɛ fie no bɛ ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Fa ɛsɛn no si so, na hwie nsuo nso gu mu.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Fa ne nankum nso gu mu, nankum pa nyinaa, srɛ ne basa, nnompe a ɛyɛ nyinaa, na fa hyɛ mu ma;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> fa nnwan no mu deɛ ɔyɛ no, na fa nnyina hyehyɛ nnompe no ase ma no nhuru yie, na ne nnompe nso mmen wɔ mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛno nti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Due, mogya kuro! Ɛsɛn a emu awe nnaakyen a ne nnaakyen mfiri ne mu. Yiyi mu adeɛ, nankum, nankum. Wɔnnyiyi mu.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ne mogya wɔ ne mu; waka agu ɔbotan kwawee so, wanhwie angu fam, na wɔde dɔteɛ akata so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na ahwanyan anibereɛ na ama aweredie aba nti, na memaa ne mogya guu ɔbotan pataa soɔ, a wɔankata soɔ yi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Saa nti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Due, mogyahwiegu kuro! Me nso mɛma aseɛ mmaboa adɔɔso.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ma nnyina nnɔɔso, ma ogya no nnɛre, ma nam no nhono, nu mu ma no mpi na nnompe no nhye.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na fa ɛsɛn no mpan si nsramma no so, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na ne kɔbere adɔ ayɛ kɔɔ, na emu fi no anane na ne nnaakyen asa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Brɛ ara na mabrɛ agu, ɛfiri sɛ ogya rentumi nhye ne nnaakyen pii no mfiri ne ho nkɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Wo fi mu wɔ abusudeɛ; sɛ matwi wo ho na amfire nti, wo ho rente mfiri wo fi no mu bio, de bɛkɔ akɔsi sɛ mɛma m’abufuhyeɛ ano adwo wo soɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Me, AWURADE, na maka. Ɛbɛba na mɛyɛ. Merennyae na merennodo ho, na merennu me ho; sɛdeɛ w’akwan teɛ ne sɛdeɛ wo nneyɛɛ teɛ no, saa ara na wɔbɛbu wo atɛn, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Onipa ba, hwɛ, merebɛbɔ wo de ayi w’ani adeɛ a ɛpɛ no afiri wo ho. Na ntwa adwo, nsu, na mma wo nisuo nkyi.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Gu ahome komm, nni owufoɔ ho abooboo, fa w’abɔtire bɔ wo ti, na fa wo mpaboa hyɛ wo nan, na nkata w’ano, na nni nnipa aduane.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na mekasa kyerɛɛ ɔman no anɔpa, na me yere wuu anwummerɛ, na anɔpa meyɛɛ sɛdeɛ ɔhyɛɛ me no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na nkurɔfoɔ no ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Worenkyerɛ yɛn adekodeɛ a yeinom a woreyɛ yi kyerɛ wɔ yɛn ho anaa?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na meka kyerɛɛ wɔn sɛ: AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kasa kyerɛ Israel fie sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, meregu me kronkronbea ho fi, mo ahoɔden ahokyerɛ no, mo ani adeɛ a ɛpɛ ne mo kra adeɛ a ɛdɔ no; na mo mmabanin ne mo mmammaa nkaeɛ no bɛtotɔ nkrantɛ ano.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na mobɛyɛ sɛdeɛ mayɛ yi, morenkata mo ano na morenni nnipa aduane,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na mo abotire bɛbobɔ mo ti, na mo mpaboa ahyehyɛ mo nan. Morentwa adwo na morensu, na mode awerɛhoɔ bɛhunu amane wɔ mo amumuyɛ mu, na moasisi apini akyerɛkyerɛ mo ho.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na Hesekiel ayɛ mo nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ; sɛdeɛ wayɛ yi nyinaa, mobɛyɛ no berɛ a ɛbɛba mu no, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE Nyankopɔn.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, ɛda no ara a mɛgye wɔn nsam ahoɔden, wɔn ahyehyɛdeɛ ho ahosɛpɛ, wɔn ani adeɛ a ɛpɛ ne wɔn kra adeɛ a ɛpɛ, wɔn mmabanin ne wɔn mmammaa no,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> da no ara na deɛ wafiri mu afire bi bɛba wo nkyɛn abɛma w’aso ateɛ.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ɛda no ara na wo ne deɛ wafiri mu afire no ano bɛbue, na wobɛkasa na worentɔre mum bio, na wobɛyɛ wɔn nsɛnkyerɛnneɛ na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, yi w’ani kyerɛ Amonfoɔ, na hyɛ nkɔm tia wɔn.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ka kyerɛ Amonfoɔ no sɛ: Montie AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ moka sɛ: Wiɛ, sɛ me kronkronbea ho agu fi, ne Israel asase ho, sɛ ayɛ afo, ne Yuda fie ho nso, sɛ wɔkɔ tukorɔ mu nti,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> hwɛ, mereyi wo ama apueeɛfoɔ sɛ wɔmfa wo nni, na wɔnkyere wɔn nsraban wo mu, na wɔnsisi wɔn tenabea wo mu; wɔn na wɔbɛdi w’aba, na wɔn ara anom wo nufosuo;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na mede Raba bɛyɛ yoma adan, na Amonfoɔ asase ayɛ nnwan butubea, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ woabɔ wo nsamu na wode wo nan apempem fam na w’ahantan nyinaa mu woama w’akoma atɔ wo yam atia Israel asase nti,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> hwɛ, meretene me nsa atia wo, na mede wo ayɛ amanaman asadeɛ, na matwa wo afiri aman mu, na asɛe wo afiri aman mu, na madwerɛ wo, na woahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ Moab ne Seir ka sɛ: Hwɛ, Yuda fie ayɛ sɛ amanaman nyinaa nti,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> hwɛ, merebue Moab nkyɛn mu afiri nkuro no so, nkuro a ɛdeda n’ahyeɛ so ho, asase a ɛyɛ no, Bet-yesimot, Baal-meon de kɔka Kiriataim,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> mede mama apueeɛ mma apae Amonfoɔ deɛ no so, na mama wɔafa adi wɔn so, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔankae Amonfoɔ bio aman mu,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na mɛyɛ Moab mu atemmudeɛ, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ Edom atɔ Yuda fie so were na wɔadi so pa ara, na wanhunu wɔn mmɔbɔ nti,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mɛtene me nsa atia Edom, na matwitwa emu nnipa ne afieboa, na mayɛ no afo afiri Teman, na wɔatotɔ nkrantɛ ano akɔduru Dedan.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mede me man Israel nsa bɛwie m’aweretɔ Edom so, na wɔne Edom adi no m’abufuo ne m’anibereɛ so, na wɔahunu m’aweretɔ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ Filistifoɔ atɔ ne so were, na wɔde abufuo kɛseɛ atɔ wɔn so were sɛ wɔde daa ɔtane bɛsɛe wɔn no nti,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, meretene me nsa atia Filistifoɔ, na matwa Keretifoɔ no, na masɛe deɛ aka mpoano no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na mede abufuhyeɛ kɛse bɛtɔ wɔn so were, na me were a mɛtɔ wɔn soɔ no mu wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so dubaako, bosome no da a ɛdi kan no, AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, ɛsiane sɛ Tiro ka wɔ Yerusalem ho sɛ: Wiɛ, wɔabubu aman no pono no, ɛbɛdane aba me nkyɛn; mɛyɛ ma, ɛno ayɛ amamfo nti,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, mene wo anya, Tiro, na mede amanaman bebree bɛba wo so, sɛdeɛ ɛpo de n’asorɔkyeɛ ba no,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na wɔabɛsɛe Tiro afasuo, na wɔabubu n’aban atentene no; na mɛpra ne dɔteɛ afiri mu, na mayɛ no ɔbotan kwawee;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ɛbɛyɛ asau hatabea wɔ ɛpo mu. Na me na maka, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, na ɛbɛyɛ amanaman asadeɛ,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na ne mmammaa a wɔwɔ asase soɔ no, wɔde nkrantɛ bɛkunkum wɔn. Na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, mede Babelhene Nebukadnessar, ahene mu hene no, mefiri atifi fam ne apɔnkɔ ne nteaseɛnam ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ ne asafo ne dɔm bebree mereba Tiro so.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Wo mmammaa a ɛdeda asase soɔ no, ɔde nkrantɛ bɛkum wɔn. Na wasi wo ho aban, na wato wo ho pie, na wama ɛkyɛm so ahyia wo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔde ne dwirie adeɛ asisi w’afasuo ho, na ɔde n’akodeɛ adwiri w’aban atentene.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> N’apɔnkɔ dodoɔ nan ase mfuturo bɛkata wo so, apɔnkɔsotefoɔ, nkyimiiɛ ne nteaseɛnam gyegyeegye nti, w’afasuo bɛwosowosoɔ, berɛ a ɔrefa w’aponkɛseɛ mu aba mu sɛ wɔreba kuro a wɔabu mu afa no mu.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɔde n’apɔnkɔ ntɔte bɛtiatia wo mmorɔno nyinaa so, ɔde nkrantɛ bɛkunkum wo nkurɔfoɔ, na ɔbɛsum w’ahoɔden adum no agu fam.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔde w’ahonyadeɛ bɛyɛ asadeɛ, na wɔafomfom w’adwadeɛ, na wɔadwiri w’afasuo, na wɔasɛe w’anigyeɛ afie. Na wɔatoto w’aboɔ ne wo nnua ne wo dɔteɛ agu nsuo mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na mɛma wo dwontoɔ hooyɛ agyae, na w’asankuo nne nso, wɔrente bio.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mɛyɛ wo ɔbotan kwawee, wobɛdane asau hatabea. Wɔrenkyekyere wo bio, na me, AWURADE, na maka, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn ka kyerɛɛ Tiro nie: Ɛnyɛ w’ahweaseɛ huuyɛ, w’atɔfoɔ apenepene, kum a wɔkunkumm wɔ wo mu nti na nsupɔ bɛwosowosoɔ?",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ɛpo so aberempɔn nyinaa refiri wɔn adwa so asianesiane, na wɔayiyi wɔn ngusoɔ, na wɔaworɔworɔ wɔn nkyeremu atadeɛ, na wɔafira ahopopoɔ atenatena fam, na wɔn ho apopo berɛ nyinaa mu, na wo nti wɔn ho adwiri wɔn.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wɔbɛtwa wo ho kwadwom aka akyerɛ wo sɛ: Ei, sɛdeɛ woasɛe nie, wo a ɛpo mufoɔ bɛtenaa wo mu, kuro a wɔkamfo a ɛyɛ den wɔ po mu, ɛno ne emufoɔ a wɔma wɔn ho hu ba emufoɔ nyinaa soɔ no!",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Afei nsupɔ ho bɛpopo w’ahweaseɛ da no; na nsupɔ a ɛwɔ po mu no akoma atu w’awieeɛ ho.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Sɛ meyɛ wo nkurofo sɛ nkuro a wɔntena mu bio, sɛ mede ebunu meba wo so ma nsuo kɛseɛ bebree wo so a,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> mede wo bɛsiane aka wɔn a ɛfiri tete nteredee wɔasiane kɔ Amena mu no ho, akɔ nkurɔfoɔ no nkyɛn, na mama woatena famfam asase so, deɛ ɛhɔ yɛ amamfo firi tete nteredee no, wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ Amena mu no nkyɛn, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔrentena wo mu bio, na mɛyɛ animuonyanneɛ ateasefoɔ asase so.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Adeɛ a ɛyɛ hu na mede wo bɛyɛ, na worentena hɔ bio, na wɔbisa w’akyiri kwan a, wɔrenhu wo da biara da bio, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Afei wo, onipa ba, twa Tiro ho kwadwom,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ka kyerɛ Tiro sɛ: Wo a wote ɛpo aboboano, aman batani a wokɔ nsupɔ bebree soɔ, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Tiro, wo deɛ, woka sɛ: Me na me ho wie fɛ yɛ!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> W’ahyeɛ wɔ po mfimfini, w’abantofoɔ awie wo fɛ yɛ,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Senir pepeaa na wɔde pempam w’ahyɛn afasuo, Lebanon ntweneduro na wɔfa de yɛɛ w’ahyɛn mu nnua;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Basan adum na wɔde yɛɛ w’atabono, wɔyɛɛ no asonse mango a ɛhyehyɛ kwabɔhorɔ nnua a ɛfiri Kipro mpoano mu mu;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> nwera a wɔakyere mu a ɛfiri Misraim yɛ wo mframatoma a ɛyɛɛ wo frankaa; bibitoma ne ntoma a ɛberedum a ɛfiri Elisa mpoano mu yɛ wo nkatasoɔ;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sidonfoɔ ne Arwadfoɔ yɛɛ w’aharefoɔ; w’anyansafoɔ wɔ wo Tiro no ara mu, wɔne w’ahyɛn kwankyerɛfoɔ;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Gebal mpanimfoɔ ne emu anyansafoɔ nso wɔ wo mu repempam w’agoago; ɛpo so ahyɛn nyinaa ne wɔn hyɛn mufoɔ wɔ wo mu di w’adwadeɛ ho nsesadwa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Persia ne Lidia ne Put wɔ wo dɔm mu, yɛ w’akofoɔ, wɔde kyɛm ne dadeɛ kyɛ sensɛne wo mu, wɔn na wɔmaa w’anim baa nyam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Arwadfoɔ ne wo dɔm wɔ w’afasuo so hyia, na Gamadfoɔ wɔ w’aban atentene mu, wɔde wɔn akyɛm sensɛne w’afasuo ho hyia, wɔn na wɔmaa w’ahoɔfɛ wiee yie yɛ.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Tarsis ne w’adamfo, w’adeɛ nyinaa dodoɔ nti; dwetɛ, dadeɛ, sanya, ne sumpii na wɔde bɛsesa wo hɔ adeɛ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Yawan, Tubal ne Mesek ne wo di dwa, nnipa ne kɔbere mfrafraeɛ adeɛ na wɔde gye w’adwadeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Bet-togarma fie na wɔfiri de apɔnkɔ ne ɔko mu apɔnkɔ ne mfunumupɔnkɔ ba de bɛsesa wo hɔ adeɛ;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Dedan mma ne wo di dwa; mpoano aman bebree so na wo nsa ano adwadeɛ korɔ; asonse amuamu ne duaboɔ nnua na wɔde bɛtua wo ka;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Siria ne wo di dwa, w’adeɛ a woyɛeɛ no dodoɔ nti. Nsrammaboɔ, ntoma a ɛberedum ne nkyeremu ne nwera pa ne bota ne nnenkyenema na wɔde bɛsesa wo hɔ adeɛ.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Yuda ne Israel asase ne wo di dwa; Minit ayuo, atokoɔ, ɛwoɔ, ngo ne aneneduhwam na wɔde gye w’adwadeɛ,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Damasko ne wo di dwa, w’adeɛ a woyɛeɛ no dodoɔ so, ahodeɛ nyinaa dodoɔ nti; wɔde Helbon bobesa ne nnwan nwi fitaa ba.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Wedan ne Yewan firi Usal bɛne wo di nsesadwa; dadeɛ a wɔabɔ, bɛwewonua ne mmetire yɛ wo nsesa adeɛ.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Dedan de apɔnkɔtoma a wɔtena soɔ ne wo di dwa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Arabia ne Kedar aberempɔn nyinaa yɛ wo nsa ano adwadifoɔ: Nnwammaa ne adwennini ne mpapo dwa na wɔne wo die;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Seba ne Rama abatafoɔ ne wo di dwa, wɔde nnuhwam nyinaa mu titire ne aboɔden aboɔ nyinaa mu sika ne wo bɛdi nsesadwa;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Haran ne Kane ne Eden, Seba abatafoɔ, Asur, Kilmad ne wo di dwa;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> wɔn na wɔyɛ w’abatafoɔ, ntoma afɛfɛ mu, bibitoma ne nkyeremu ngusoɔ mu ne asaawa a wɔafira ademudeɛ, nhoma a wɔafira na wɔakyinkyim, wɔde gye wo adwadeɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Tarsis ahyɛn no ne w’akwantufoɔ di w’adwadie mu akɔneaba, na woayɛ ma, na wɔsoaa wo nnesoa pii wɔ ɛpo ahodoɔ no mfimfini.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> W’aharefoɔ no de wo kɔ nsuo bebree so, apueeɛ mframa bobɔ wo wɔ ɛpo ahodoɔ no mfimfini.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> W’adeɛ dodoɔ ne w’adetɔnneɛ, wo nsesa adwadeɛ, w’ahyɛn mufoɔ ne w’ahyɛn kwankyerɛfoɔ, wo mu agoago pempamfoɔ ne w’adwadeɛ sesafoɔ ne wo mu akofoɔ nyinaa ne w’asafo a wɔwɔ wo mu nyinaa, bɛmem ɛpo mu, w’ahweaseɛ da no mu.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> W’ahyɛn kwankyerɛfoɔ nteamu nne ma mpoano asase wosowoso,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> na wɔn a wɔkurakura atabono nyinaa, ahyɛn mufoɔ, po ani kwankyerɛfoɔ nyinaa fifiri wɔn ahyɛn mu sianesiane bɛgyinagyina fam,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> na wo so na wɔmema wɔn nne soɔ, na wɔteam yayaaya de dɔteɛ gugu wɔn atifi yantamyantam nso mu,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> na wɔbobɔ tikwa ma wo, firafira ayitoma na wɔde ɔkra awerɛhoɔ ne agyaadwotwirɛ yaya su ma wo,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> na wɔbɛtwa wo ho kwadwom, wɔn adwotwa no mu ato wo ho dwom sɛ: Hwan na ɔte sɛ Tiro a wɔama n’asase ayɛ dinn, ɛpo mu yi?",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> W’adwadeɛ firi po nyinaa mu baeɛ no, wode maa aman bebree mee, w’ahonyadeɛ ne w’adwadeɛ dodoɔ na wode maa asase so ahemfo nyaa wɔn ho.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Afei a wɔabobɔ wo afiri ɛpo ani de wo ahyɛ nsu donkodonko mu yi, w’adwadeɛ ne w’asafo a ɛwɔ wo mu no nyinaa atotɔ.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Nsuano aman nyinaa, wo nti wɔn ho dwiri wɔn, na awɔse gu wɔn ahemfo so, wɔn anim akusa.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Aman mu adwadifoɔ bɔ wo so hwerɛma hwee hwee. Woapatu asɛe, na wonni hɔ bio de kɔsi daa."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, ka kyerɛ Tiro man panin sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ woama wo ho soɔ, na wose: Meyɛ onyame, anyamedwa so na meteɛ, ɛpo mfimfini, nanso woyɛ onipa, na wonyɛ onyame, na wobu wo ho sɛ onyame.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hwɛ, woyɛ onyansafoɔ sene Daniel anaa, ahuntasɛm biara anhunta wo,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> wo nyansa ne wo nhunumu so na woanya adeɛ afa, na woanya sika ne dwetɛ agu w’akoradeɛ mu,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> wo nyansa dodoɔ ne w’adwadie na wode ama w’ahodeɛ adɔɔso, na w’adeɛ no nti w’akoma ahuhuru,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> enti, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ woyɛ wo ho sɛ onyame nti,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> hwɛ, mede ananafoɔ mereba wo so, amanaman mu aniɛdenfoɔ, na wɔabɛtwetwe wɔn nkrantɛ atia wo nyansa ahoɔfɛ no, na wɔagu wo hyerɛn ho fi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Amena mu na wɔde wo bɛsiane akorɔ, na woawu atɔfoɔ wuo, ɛpo mfimfini.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ka na wobɛka sɛ: Onyame ne me, wɔn a wɔkum woɔ no anim? Na wo deɛ, woyɛ onipa na wonyɛ onyame, deɛ ɔhwire wo mu no nsam.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Momonotofoɔ wuo na wobɛwuo ananafoɔ nsam, na me na maka, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Onipa ba, twa Tiro hene ho kwadwom, na ka kyerɛ no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Wo deɛ, wone abɔdeɛ afɛfɛ mu deɛ ɔyɛ, nyansa ahyɛ wo ma, w’ahoɔfɛ di mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nyankopɔn turo Eden mu na woteɛ, aboɔden aboɔ nyinaa yɛ wo nkataho, bogyanamboɔ, akarateboɔ ne bɔwerɛboɔ, sikabereɛboɔ, apopobibireboɔ ne ahwehwɛboɔ, hoaboɔ, nsrammaboɔ ne ahahammonoboɔ ne sika; wo mpintin ne bɔmmaa som w’anim, ɛda a wɔbɔɔ woɔ no na wɔsiesieeɛ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Wo ne kerub a wɔasra no a ɔkata soɔ, na mede wo mesii hɔ, Nyankopɔn bepɔ kronkron no so na wowɔ, ogya aboɔ ntam na na wonenam.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na mfomsoɔ biara nni wo ho, firi da a wɔbɔɔ woɔ ara de kɔsii da a wɔhunuu wo mu abusudeɛ no.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> W’adwadie dodoɔ nti na wɔde amimdie hyɛɛ wo mu ma, na woyɛɛ bɔne, na metoo wo firi Nyankopɔn bepɔ so sɛ afideɛ, na kerub a ɔbɔ wo ho ban no, pamm wo firi ogya aboɔ no ntam.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> W’ahoɔfɛ nti w’akoma ahuhuru, woasɛe wo nyansa ne wo hyerɛn, mato wo atwene fam, mede wo ato ahemfo anim sɛ wɔnhwɛ wo.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> W’amumuyɛ dodoɔ so, w’adwadie abusudeɛ mu woagu w’akronkronneɛ ho fi, enti mama ogya afiri wo mu, na ahye wo, na madane wo nso, asase so, wɔn a wɔhwɛ woɔ nyinaa anim.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Wɔn a wɔnim woɔ, aman nyinaa mu, wo ho bɛyɛ wɔn ahodwiri; woapatu asɛe, na wonni hɔ bio de kɔsi daa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Onipa ba, dane w’ani kyerɛ Sidon, na hyɛ ne ho nkɔm,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne wo anya, O Sidon, na mɛnya wo mu animuonyam, na sɛ meyɛ ne mu atemmudeɛ na meyi ne mu kronkronyɛ adi a, wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na merema owuyadeɛ aba ne mu na mogya agu ne mmorɔno so, na apirafoɔ atotɔ ne mu, nkrantɛ a ɛfiri mmaa nyinaa bɛba ne soɔ no ano, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na kasɛɛ a ɛwɔ onipa ne hwerɛmo a ɛyɛ ya renka hɔ mma Israel fie bio, mfiri wɔn a wɔatwa wɔn ho ahyia a wɔbu wɔn animtia no nyinaa mu, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE Nyankopɔn.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Sɛ menya boa Israel fie ano firi aman a wɔapete wɔn mu no mu a, mɛyi me kronkronyɛ adi wɔ wɔn mu amanaman no ani so, na wɔbɛtena wɔn asase a mede maa m’akoa Yakob no so.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na wɔbɛtena so dwoodwoo, asi adan, ayeyɛ bobe nturo, na wɔatena ase dwoodwoo, ɛfiri sɛ mɛyɛ atemmudeɛ, wɔn a wɔatwa wɔn ho ahyia bu wɔn animtia no nyinaa mu, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE wɔn Nyankopɔn."
		},
		"29": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Afe a ɛtɔ so du no, bosome a ɛtɔ so du no da a ɛtɔ so dummienu no, AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, dane w’ani kyerɛ Misraimhene Farao, na hyɛ nkɔm tia no ne Misraim nyinaa;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> kasa na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne wo anya, Misraimhene Farao, asuboa kɛseɛ a ɔda n’asubɔnten mu a ɔka sɛ: M’Asubɔnten Nil wɔ me, me ara na meyɛ mefaeɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na mede nkɔtɔkorɔ bɛwura w’afono mu, na mama w’asubɔnten mu mpataa afemfam w’abena ho, na matwe wo afiri w’asubɔnten mu aba, wo ne w’asubɔnten mu mpataa a ɛfemfam w’abena ho no nyinaa.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na mɛto wo atwene ɛserɛ so, wo ne w’asubɔnten mu mpataa nyinaa. Ɛserɛ petee so na wobɛtɔ, wɔrentase wo, na wɔremmoa wo ano; asase so mmoa ne ewiem nnomaa na mede wo bɛyɛ wɔn aduane.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na Misraimfoɔ nyinaa bɛhunu sɛ mene AWURADE. Ɛsiane sɛ wɔyɛ nkyɛnkyɛmma poma ma Israel fie,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> wɔsɔ wo nsa mu a, wobuka suane wɔn mmati nyinaa, na wɔtwere wo a, wobu ma wɔn sisi nyinaa hinhim.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ɛno nti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, mede nkrantɛ mereba wo so, na matwitwa wo mu nnipa ne mmoa,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na Misraim asase adane afo, na ɛso ada mpan, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE. Ɛsiane sɛ woka sɛ: Asubɔntene Nil no wɔ me, na me ara na meyɛeɛ.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Enti, hwɛ, me ne wo ne w’asutene ahodoɔ no anya, na mɛyɛ Misraim asase no afoafo, amamfo ne ahodwirideɛ, afiri Siene abantenten ho akɔsi Etiopia hyeɛ so tɔnn.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Onipa nan remfa so na aboa nan rensi so, na wɔrentena so mfirinhyia aduanan.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mɛyɛ Misraim asase pasaa, nsase a ayɛ pasaa mu, na ne nkuro ada mpan wɔ nkuro afoafo mu, mfirinhyia aduanan, na mɛbɔ Misraim apete amanaman mu, na mapansam wɔn agu nsase so.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mfirinhyia aduanan akyiri no, mɛboa Misraim ano afiri aman a mabɔ wɔn apete hɔ no mu,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na mede Misraim nnommum no asane aba, na mede wɔn aba Patros asase so bio, wɔn asase a wɔfiri soɔ no so, na wɔayɛ ahennie a abrɛ aseɛ wɔ hɔ.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ɛbɛyɛ ahennie mu deɛ abrɛ aseɛ, na ɛremma ne ho so bio wɔ amanaman so. Na mɛma wɔasua, na wɔanni amanaman so bio.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na Israel fie remfa wɔn ho nto wɔn so bio, sɛ wɔkae wɔn bɔne a ɛne sɛ wɔhwehwɛɛ mmoa firii wɔn hɔ no. Na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE Nyankopɔn.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so aduonu nson no, bosome a ɛdi kan no da a ɛdi kan no, AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Onipa ba, Babelhene Nebukadnessar maa ne dɔm ko tiaa Tiro. Ɛyɛɛ ɔko kɛseɛ a na ɔhaw ne brɛ pii wɔ mu, nanso akatua biara amfiri Tiro ammɛka ɔno ne ne dɔm nsa, som a ɔsomeeɛ no ho.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Enti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, mede Misraim asase merema Babelhene Nebukadnessar, na wasoa n’asafo yuu akɔ, na wafa n’asadeɛ, na wafom n’afomfadeɛ afa, na ayɛ ne dɔm no akatua;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> n’apaadeɛ a ɔsom ho no ano na mede Misraim asase bɛma no, sɛ n’apaadeɛ a ɔsomm ho, ɛfiri sɛ wɔyɛ maa me, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ɛda no na mɛma abɛn bi afifiri ama Israel fie, na wo na mɛma wo kwan na woabue w’ano wɔ wɔn mu, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"30": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, hyɛ nkɔm na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Montwa agyaadwoɔ! Ao, ɛda no!",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɛda no abɛn, ɛda no abɛn ama AWURADE, mununkum da, ɛbɛyɛ amanaman berɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na nkrantɛ bɛba Misraim so, na nketenkete akuta Etiopia, ɛberɛ a apirafoɔ retotɔ Misraim na wɔrefa emu asafo yuu akorɔ na wɔredwiri ne nnyinasoɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Etiopia, Put, Lidia ne afrafrafoɔ dɔm nyinaa ne Kub a wɔne wɔn wɔ apam no nyinaa bɛtotɔ nkrantɛ ano.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Sɛ AWURADE seɛ nie: Wɔn a wɔboa Misraim bɛtotɔ, na n’ahoɔden ahantan no abrɛ ase. Ɛfiri Migdol kɔsi Siene wɔbɛtotɔ nkrantɛ ano, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na wɔayɛ pasaa, nsase a ayɛ pasaa mu, na ne nkuro afra nkuro afoafo mu,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE, berɛ a mɛsɔ ogya Misraim na wɔasɛe n’aboafoɔ nyinaa no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛda no, abɔfoɔ bɛfiri m’anim afiri adi, ahyɛne mu, akɔma Etiopiafoɔ wɔn a wɔwɔ hɔ anibiannasoɔ mu no abɔ binim, na ehu bɛba wɔn mu sɛ Misraim da no, na hwɛ, ɛreba.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mede Babelhene Nebukadnessar nsa bɛtwa Misraim asafo yuu no so.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɔno ne ne man a ɛka ne ho no, amanaman aniɛdenfoɔ no, wɔde wɔn reba abɛsɛe asase no, na wɔatwetwe wɔn nkrantɛ atia Misraim, na wɔde atɔfoɔ ahyɛ asase no ma.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mɛma Nil ne nsubɔntene no awewe, na matɔn asase no ahyɛ abɔnefoɔ nsa, na mede ananafoɔ nsa mayɛ asase no ne ne mayɛ pasaa; me AWURADE, na maka.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mɛsɛe ahoni huhuo no na matwa abosonhuhuo no so afiri Memfis, na ɔberempɔn renka Misraim asase so mma wɔn bio, na mɛma ehu aba Misraim asase so.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mɛyɛ Patros pasaa, na masɔ ogya Soan, na mayɛ atemmudeɛ wɔ Tebes,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na mahwie m’abufuhyeɛ agu Pelusium, ne Misraim aban a ɛyɛ den no so, na Tebes asafo yuu no matwa so.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na mɛto Misraim mu gya. Pelusium bɛhunu ayayadeɛ, na wɔde Tebes bɛma wɔabu n’afasuo afa mu, na Memfis bɛhunu ahohiahiafoɔ awia,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> On ne Pi-beset mmeranteɛ bɛtotɔ nkrantɛ ano, na mmaa no akɔ nnommumfa mu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Tehafnehes nso, ɛda no bɛduru sum, sɛ merebubu Misraim kɔnnua wɔ hɔ, na n’ahoɔden ahantan to bɛtwa wɔ ne mu, na mununkum bɛkata ne so, na ne mmammaa akɔ nnommumfa mu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Sei na mɛyɛ atemmudeɛ wɔ Misraim, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so dubaako, bosome a ɛdi kan no da a ɛtɔ so nson no, AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Onipa ba, Misraimhene Farao basa no, mabu, na hwɛ, wɔnkyekyeree sɛ wɔresa, sɛ wɔde ntomaban rekyekyere so, sɛ wɔde rema emu ayɛ den na atumi asɔ nkrantɛ mu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛno nti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne Misraimhene Farao anya, na merebɛbu n’abasa no, deɛ ɛyɛ den ne deɛ abuo no, na mama nkrantɛ no afiri ne nsa atɔ fam;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na mɛbɔ Misraimfoɔ apete amanaman mu, na mapansam wɔn agu nsase so.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na mɛhyɛ Babel hene abasa mu den, na mede ne nkrantɛ ahyɛ ne nsa, na mabubu Farao abasa, na wapenepene ɔtofoɔ pene n’anim.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na mɛma Babel hene abasa ayɛ den, na Farao abasa mu ago, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE. Na mede me nkrantɛ merehyɛ Babel hene nsa, na watene no Misraim asase so;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na mɛbɔ Misraim apete amanaman mu, na mapansam wɔn agu so, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"31": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so dubaako no, bosome a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa no da a ɛdi kan no, AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, ka kyerɛ Misraimhene Farao ne n’asafo yuu no sɛ: Wote sɛ hwan, wo kɛseyɛ mu?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hwɛ, Asiria te sɛ Lebanon so tweneduro, ne mman fɛfɛ, n’ahahan kusuu a ɛma enwunu, na ɛkorɔn sorɔnsorɔn a ne ntɛntɛnoa wɔ mununkum ntam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Nsuo maa no yɛɛ kɛse, ebunu maa no korɔnn. Ne nsutene sene twaa ne mfuo ho hyiae, na ɛde ne nsuka kɔɔ wiram nnua nyinaa ho.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Enti ɛkorɔn sorɔnsorɔn sene wiram nnua nyinaa, ne dubaa ayeyɛ akɛseɛ na ne mman ayeyɛ atentene, nsuo dodoɔ a ɛnyaeɛ a ɛpaepae nkorabata no nti.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ne mman frɔmfrɔm no mu na ewiem nnomaa nyinaa yeyɛɛ apirebuo, na ne mman akɛseɛ no ase na wiram mmoa nyinaa wowoo wɔn mma, na n’ase nwunu mu na amanaman akɛseɛ nyinaa tenaeɛ.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ne ho yɛ fɛ, ne kɛseyɛ mu, ne mman tentenyɛ mu, ɛfiri sɛ na ne nhini kɔ nsuo bebree ho;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> ntweneduro a ɛwɔ Nyankopɔn turo mu nto no, na pepeaa nnua nte sɛ ne mman frɔmfrɔm no, na kyɛnkyɛn nte sɛ ne mman akɛseɛ; dua biara nni Nyankopɔn turo mu a na ɛsɛ no n’ahoɔfɛ mu;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> mede ne mman dodoɔ maa ɛyɛɛ fɛ maa nnua a ɛwɔ Nyankopɔn Eden turo mu no nyinaa ani beree no.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Enti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ ɛwaree ne korɔn mu na ɔyii ne ntɛntɛnoa kɔɔ mununkum mu, na n’akoma huhuruiɛ n’ahantan mu nti,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> mede no hyɛɛ amanaman tumfoɔ no nsa; die na ɔne no diiɛ, n’abɔnefosɛm nti na metuu no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ananafoɔ, amanaman mu aniɛdenfoɔ too no gui na wɔgyaa no hɔ; mmepɔ so ne mmonhwa nyinaa mu na na ne mman guguo, na ne mman akɛseɛ no bubui wɔ asase so nsubɔnhwa nyinaa mu, na asase so aman nyinaa firii ne nwunu no mu sane kɔe, gyaa no hɔ.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na dutan a ɛda fam no so na na ewiem nnomaa nyinaa sisie, na ne mman akɛseɛ no so na na wiram mmoa nyinaa wɔ.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛyɛɛ saa na nsuo ho nnua nyinaa mu biara amma ne ho so, ne korɔn nti, na anyiyi ne ntɛntɛnoa wɔ mununkum mu, na wɔn atumfoɔ amma wɔn ho so annyina wɔn ahantan mu, wɔn a wɔnom nsuo nyinaa. Ɛfiri sɛ, na wɔde wɔn nyinaa ama owuo, akɔ asase ase tɔnn, nnipa mma mu, akɔ wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ Asamando no nkyɛn.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Da a ɔsiane kɔɔ Asamando no, memaa abooboodie bae, ne nti memaa ebunu so katae, na mesii ne nsubɔntene ano, na wɔsiankaa nsuo bebree no; na memaa Lebanon firaa ne so birisi tumm, na ne nti ewiem nnua nyinaa botoe.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> N’ahweaseɛ gyegyeegye so memaa amanaman wosoe, berɛ a mereto no akɔ Asamando aka wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ Amena mu no ho no; na Eden nnua nyinaa, Lebanon adeɛ a wɔayi a ɛyɛ no, wɔn a wɔnom nsuo nyinaa bo tɔe, asase so.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Wɔn nso a wɔyɛ ne basa a wɔte n’ase nwunu mu, amanaman mu no, wɔne no siane kɔɔ Asamando, kɔɔ nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ nkyɛn.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hwan na wosɛ no saa, animuonyam ne kɛseyɛ mu, Eden nnua mu? Nanso wɔde wo ne Eden nnua no bɛsiane akɔ asase ase, momonotofoɔ mu na wobɛda, nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ nkyɛn. Farao ne n’asafo yuu nyinaa nie, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"32": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so dummienu no, bosome a ɛtɔ so dummienu no, da a ɛdi kan no, AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, twa kwadwom ma Misraimhene Farao, na ka kyerɛ no sɛ: Amanaman mu gyataburuwa ho na wɔde wo toeɛ, nso wo deɛ, wotee sɛ ɛpo mu asuboa, na wohuri firii wo nsubɔntene no mu, na wode wo nan nuu nsuo no mu honoo wɔn nsubɔntene.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Mɛto m’asau agu wo so, aman bebree asafo mu, na wɔde me boa ayi wo aforo aba,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na mɛto wo atwene fam, na mato wo atwene ɛserɛ so, na mama ewiem nnomaa nyinaa abɛsisi wo so, na mama asase nyinaa so mmoadoma adi wo nam amee.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na mede wo nam bɛto mmepɔ so, na mede wo funu ahyɛ mmonhwa ma,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na mama asase no anom wo mogya sɛ nsuo akɔduru mmepɔ ho, na woahyɛ nsubɔnhwa no mama.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na sɛ medum wo sɛ kanea a, mɛkata ɔsoro, na mama ne nsoromma abiri tumm; mede mununkum bɛkata owia ani, na ɔsrane renharan.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Mɛma ɔsoro nkanea a ɛhyerɛn abiri wo so, na mama esum aduru w’asase so, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na mɛteetee aman bebree akoma, berɛ a mɛfa wo dommum akɔ amanaman mu, nsase a wonnim soɔ no soɔ;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na mɛma wo ho ayɛ aman bebree ahodwiri, na wo ho ama awɔse agu wɔn ahemfo so, berɛ a mehwinhwim m’afena wɔn anim no, na wɔn ho bɛpopo berɛ nyinaa mu, wɔn nyinaa nkwa nti, w’ahweaseɛ da no so.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Babel hene nkrantɛ bɛba wo so.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Nnɔmmarima nkrantɛ na mede bɛma w’asafo yuu no atotɔ, amanaman mu aniɛdenfoɔ ne wɔn nyinaa, na wɔbɛsɛe Misraim ahantan, na wɔadwerɛ n’asafo yuu no nyinaa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na mɛdwerɛ n’afiemmoa nyinaa afiri nsuo akɛseɛ no ho, na onipa nan remma no nhono bio, na afieboa ntɔte remma no nhono bio.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Ɛno na mɛma wɔn nsuo ani agyene, na mama wɔn nsubɔntene asene sɛ ngo, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ɛberɛ a mɛma Misraim asase ayɛ afo na asase no ada ne mayɛ ho mpan no, ɛberɛ a mɛkum wɔn a wɔte soɔ no nyinaa no, na wɔbɛhunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Kwadwom a wɔde bɛsu no nie. Amanaman mmammaa de bɛsu no, wɔde bɛsu Misraim ne n’asafo yuu nyinaa, AWURADE asɛm nie.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na afe a ɛtɔ so dummienu no, bosome a ɛdi kan no ara da a ɛtɔ so dunum no, AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Onipa ba, twa Misraim asafo yuu so adwo, na ma wɔne amanaman atumfoɔ mmammaa nsiane nkɔ famfam asase so nka wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ Amena mu no ho.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hwan na wosene no ahoɔfɛ? Siane na da momonotofoɔ nkyɛn!",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ mu na wɔbɛtotɔ; wɔde no ama nkrantɛ; montwe ɔno ne n’asafo yuu nyinaa nkɔ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Nnɔmmarima mu atumfoɔ ne wɔn aboafoɔ firi Asamando ka kyerɛ no sɛ: Momonotofoɔ a wɔde nkrantɛ akunkum wɔn no asiane deda hɔ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛhɔ na Asiria ne n’asafo nyinaa wɔ, wɔn adamena atwa ne ho ahyia, wɔahwire wɔn nyinaa mu, wɔatotɔ nkrantɛ ano.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Wɔabɔ ne da wɔ Amena mu tɔnn, na n’asafo atwa ne damena ho ahyia. Wɔahwire wɔn nyinaa mu, wɔatotɔ nkrantɛ ano, wɔn a wɔyii nnipa hu, ateasefoɔ asase soɔ no.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛhɔ na Elam ne n’asafo yuu nyinaa wɔ, wɔn adamena atwa ne ho ahyia; wɔahwire wɔn nyinaa mu, wɔatotɔ nkrantɛ ano. Momonotofoɔ a wɔsiane kɔɔ asase ase tɔnn a wɔyii nnipa hu, ateasefoɔ asase soɔ no, na wɔne wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ Amena mu no asoa wɔn ahohora.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Atɔfoɔ mu na wɔato no mpa, n’asafo yuu no nyinaa mu, wɔn adamena atwa ne ho ahyia; wɔn nyinaa yɛ momonotofoɔ, na wɔakunkum wɔn nkrantɛ ano. Wɔn ho hu kaa nnipa ateasefoɔ asase soɔ nti, wɔne wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ Amena mu no asoa wɔn ahohora; wɔde no ato atɔfoɔ mu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ɛhɔ na Mesek, Tubal ne wɔn asafo yuu no nyinaa wɔ; wɔn adamena atwa ne ho ahyia; wɔn nyinaa yɛ momonotofoɔ, wɔakunkum wɔn nkrantɛ ano, ɛfiri sɛ wɔmaa wɔn ho hu kaa nnipa, ateasefoɔ asase so;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> na wɔrenneda momonotofoɔ mu nnɔmmarima a wɔatotɔ na wɔde wɔn akodeɛ asiane kɔ Asamando, na wɔdeda wɔn nkrantɛ soɔ; na wɔn amumuyɛdeɛ aba wɔn nnompe so, ɛfiri sɛ wɔn ho yɛɛ nnɔmmarima hu, ateasefoɔ asase so.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wo nso wɔbɛbubu wo momonotofoɔ mu, na wo ne nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ adeda.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Ɛhɔ na Edom wɔ, n’ahemfo ne n’aberempɔn nyinaa, wɔde wɔn guu nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ nkyɛn, wɔn mmaninyɛ mu. Wɔn nso wɔne momonotofoɔ ne wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ Amena mu no deda hɔ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Ɛhɔ na atifi fam mmapɔmma nyinaa wɔ, ne Sidonfoɔ a wɔne atɔfoɔ asiane korɔ no nyinaa; wɔn ho hu a wɔde wɔn mmaninyɛ yiiɛ no mu, wɔn ani awu, na wɔdeda hɔ, wɔyɛ momonotofoɔ; wɔne nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ no, na wɔne wɔn a wɔsiane kɔ Amena mu soa wɔn ahohora.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Farao bɛhu wɔn, na wakyekye ne werɛ, n’asafo yuu no nyinaa ho; nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ ne Farao ne ne dɔm nyinaa ho, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na memaa no yii hu, ateasefoɔ asase so, enti na wɔde no ato momonotofoɔ mu aka nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ ho, Farao ne n’asafo yuu nyinaa, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"33": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, kasa kyerɛ wo man mma, na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ mede nkrantɛ ba asase bi so, na asase no so man no yi wɔn mu barima bi, na wɔyɛ no ɔwɛmfoɔ,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ɔhunu nkrantɛ sɛ ɛreba asase no so, na ɔhyɛne totorobɛnto de bɔ ɔman no kɔkɔ,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na ɔtefoɔ te totorobɛnto no hyɛn, na wantie kɔkɔbɔ no, na nkrantɛ no ba bɛfa no kɔ a, ne mogya bɛbua n’atifi.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɔtee totorobɛntohyɛn no, na wantie kɔkɔbɔ no; ne mogya ngu ne so! Na sɛ ɔtiee kɔkɔbɔ no a, anka ɔgyee ne kra nkwa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na sɛ ɔwɛmfoɔ no hunu nkrantɛ sɛ ɛreba, na wanhyɛne abɛn no ammɔ ɔmanfoɔ kɔkɔ na nkrantɛ no ba bɛkum wɔn mu bi a, ɔno deɛ, n’amumuyɛ mu na wɔafa no korɔ, na ne mogya deɛ, mɛbisa no ɔwɛmfoɔ no nsam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, mede wo asi ɔwɛmfoɔ ama Israel fie, na tie m’anomu asɛm, na fa bɔ wɔn kɔkɔ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sɛ meka kyerɛ ɔbɔnefoɔ sɛ: Ɔbɔnefoɔ, wuo na wobɛwuo, na sɛ woanka ammɔ ɔbɔnefoɔ no kɔkɔ ne kwan ho a, ɔno ɔbɔnefoɔ no bɛwu n’amumuyɛ mu, na ne mogya deɛ, wo nsam na mɛbisa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wo, sɛ wobɔ ɔbɔnefoɔ no kɔkɔ ne kwan ho, sɛ ɔnsane mfiri so, na wansane amfiri ne kwan no so a, ɔno deɛ, ɔbɛwu n’amumuyɛ mu, na wo nso woagye wo kra nkwa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Enti wo, onipa ba, ka kyerɛ Israel fie sɛ: Moka sɛ: Yɛn mmarato ne yɛn bɔne gu yɛn so, na ɛnonom mu na yɛredwerɛ yi, na ɛbɛyɛ dɛn na yɛbɛnya nkwa?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa ara, ɔbɔnefoɔ wuo nyɛ me fɛ, na mmom sɛ ɔbɔnefoɔ bɛsane afiri ne kwan soɔ na wanya nkwa! Monsane, monsane mfiri mo akwammɔne so! Adɛn nti na morewuwuo yi, Israel fie?",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, ka kyerɛ wo man mma no sɛ: Ɔteneneeni tenenee rennye no ne mmarato da no, na ɔbɔnefoɔ abɔnefosɛm nso renhwe no ase, ɛda a ɔbɛsane afiri n’abɔnefosɛm mu no ho, na ɔteneneeni nso rentumi nnye ne ho nkwa wɔ mu, ɛda a ɔyɛ bɔne no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sɛ meka kyerɛ ɔteneneeni sɛ: Wobɛnya nkwa, na ɔde no ho to ne tenenee so na ɔyɛ amumuyɛdeɛ a, wɔrenkae ne tenenee no biara, na n’amumuyɛdeɛ a wayɛ no mu ara na ɔbɛwuo.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na meka kyerɛ ɔbɔnefoɔ sɛ: Wuo na wobɛwuo, na ɔsane firi ne bɔne mu bɛyɛ atemmudeɛ ne ateneneedeɛ,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na sɛ ɔbɔnefoɔ dane awowasideɛ kɔma, ɔhyɛ deɛ ɔfomeeɛ no ananmu, ɔnante nkwa ahyɛdeɛ mu sɛ ɔrenyɛ amumuyɛdeɛ a, nya na ɔbɛnya nkwa, ɔrenwu;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ne bɔne a ɔyɛeɛ no nyinaa, wɔrenkae mma no; wayɛ atemmudeɛ ne ateneneedeɛ, nkwa ara na ɔbɛnya.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Nanso wo man mma ka sɛ: AWURADE kwan ntene! berɛ a wɔn mmom na wɔn kwan ntene.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Sɛ ɔteneneeni sane firi ne tenenee ho na ɔyɛ amumuyɛdeɛ a, emu na ɔbɛwuo;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na sɛ ɔbɔnefoɔ sane firi n’abɔnefosɛm ho na ɔyɛ atemmudeɛ ne ateneneedeɛ a, ɛno ara so na ɔbɛnya nkwa;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> nanso moka sɛ: AWURADE kwan ntene! Sɛdeɛ obiara kwan teɛ no, saa na mɛbu mo atɛn, o Israel fie.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na yɛn tukorɔ afe a ɛtɔ so dummienu no, bosome a ɛtɔ so du no da a ɛtɔ so nnum no, odwanefoɔ bi firii Yerusalem baa me nkyɛn sɛ: Wɔabɔ kuro no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nso na AWURADE nsa aba me so anwummerɛ no, ansa na odwanefoɔ no reba. Ɔbaa me nkyɛn anɔpa no, na wabue m’ano, na mantɔre mum bio.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Onipa ba, wɔn a wɔte Israel asase so akurofo no soɔ no ka sɛ: Abraham yɛ ɔbaakofoɔ, na ɔfaa asase no diiɛ, na yɛn deɛ, yɛdɔɔso, yɛn mmom na wɔde asase no ama yɛn sɛ yɛmfa nnie.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Enti ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Modi aboa a wɔantwa ne tiri nam, na momma mo ani so kyerɛ mo abosonhuhuo, na moka mogya gu, na mobɛfa asase no adi so anaa?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Mogyinagyina mo nkrantɛ so, moyɛ akyiwadeɛ, na obi gu ne yɔnko yere ho fi, na mobɛfa asase no adi so anaa?",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Sɛ ka kyerɛ wɔn nie: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, ampa ara wɔn a wɔwɔ akurofo no soɔ no, nkrantɛ ano na wɔbɛtotɔ; na deɛ ɔwɔ wiram no, mmoadoma na mede no bɛma mmoa ma wɔadie; na wɔn a wɔwɔ aban ne abodan mu no, owuyadeɛ na ɛbɛkunkum wɔn.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na mɛyɛ asase no afo ne pasaa, na n’ahoɔden ahantan no to bɛtwa, na Israel mmepɔ adanedane afo a obiara biara remfa soɔ;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> na wɔn akyiwadeɛ a wɔyɛeɛ no nyinaa nti, mɛyɛ asase no afo ne ahodwirideɛ, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, wo man mma keka wo ho nsɛm afasuo ho ne adan no apono ano, na obi ne obi, obi ne ne nua, kasa sɛ: Mommra mmɛtie asɛm ko a ɛfiri AWURADE nkyɛn ba no ɛ!",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na wɔbɛba wo nkyɛn sɛdeɛ ɔman bi ba, na wɔatenatena ase w’anim sɛ me man, na wɔatie wo nsɛm, nso wɔrenni so, na wɔn anomu adɔkɔdɔkɔsɛm na wɔredie; wɔn akoma di wɔn mfasoɔ akyi.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na hwɛ, woyɛ wɔn sɛ dwom dɛdɛ, sɛ obi a ne nne yɛ dɛ, na ɔnim sankuo bɔ yie; na wɔte wo nsɛm deɛ, nanso wɔnni so.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na ɛnya ba a, hwɛ ɛbɛba, na wɔbɛhunu sɛ odiyifoɔ bi atena wɔn mu pɛn."
		},
		"34": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, hyɛ nkɔm tia Israel nnwanhwɛfoɔ, hyɛ nkɔm na ka kyerɛ wɔn, nnwanhwɛfoɔ no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Monnue, Israel nnwanhwɛfoɔ a wɔyɛne wɔn ho no; ɛnyɛ nnwan na nnwanhwɛfoɔ yɛne wɔn?",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Modi sradeɛ no, na mofira nnwan no ho nwi; deɛ wadorɔ no, mokum no; na nnwankuo no deɛ, monyɛne wɔn.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Wɔn a wɔahodwo no, monhyɛ wɔn den, na ayarefoɔ nso, monsa wɔn yadeɛ; deɛ wabubuo no, monkyekyere no, deɛ wɔapam no no, monkɔfa no mma, na deɛ wayera no, monhwehwɛ no, na mmom ɔhyɛ ne atirimuɔden na mode di wɔn soɔ.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna wɔbɔɔ wɔn pansameeɛ, ɛfiri sɛ wɔnni hwɛfoɔ, na wɔdanedanee wiram mmoa nyinaa aduane, na wɔbɔɔ wɔn petee koraa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Me nnwan wɔ mmepɔ nyinaa ne nkokoɔ a ɛkorɔn nyinaa so ntwɛtwɛdɛ, na me man abɔ apete asase nyinaa ani, na obiara nni hɔ a ɔbisa, na obiara nni hɔ a ɔhwehwɛ wɔn.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Enti, mo nnwanhwɛfoɔ, montie AWURADE asɛm!",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ampa ara, ɛsiane sɛ me nnwan adane fomfa adeɛ, na me nnwan adane wiram mmoa nyinaa aduane, ɛnam sɛ wɔnni hwɛfoɔ nti, na me nnwanhwɛfoɔ mmisaa me nnwan akyiri kwan, na mmom nnwanhwɛfoɔ no yɛne wɔn ho, na me nnwan no deɛ, wɔanhwɛ wɔn nti,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> mo nnwanhwɛfoɔ, montie AWURADE asɛm:",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne nnwanhwɛfoɔ no anya, na mɛbisa me nnwan no wɔn nsam, na mama wɔagyae nnwanhwɛ adwuma no yɛ, na nnwanhwɛfoɔ no anyɛne wɔn ho bio, na magye me nnwan afiri wɔn anomu, na wɔanyɛ wɔn aduane bio.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ara mɛhwehwɛ me nnwan, na mahwehwɛ wɔn akyiri kwan.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Sɛdeɛ odwanhwɛfoɔ hwehwɛ ne nnwankuo akyiri kwan da a ɔwɔ ne nnwan a wɔabɔ apete no mu no, saa ara na mɛhwehwɛ me nnwan akyiri kwan, na mɛyi wɔn afiri deɛ wɔapansam wɔn korɔ nyinaa, mununkum ne sum kabii da no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na mɛyi wɔn afiri aman mu, na maboa wɔn ano afiri nsase so na mede wɔn aba wɔn asase so, na mayɛne wɔn, Israel mmepɔ so, nsubɔnhwa mu ne asase no so tenabea nyinaa;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> adidibea pa na mɛyɛne wɔn, na Israel mmepɔ atenten so bɛyɛ wɔn yɛmmea; ɛhɔ na wɔde wɔn bɛkɔ yɛmmea pa, na wɔawe ɛserɛ pa, Israel mmepɔ so.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Me ara na mɛyɛne me nnwan, na me ara mɛma wɔabutubutu, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Deɛ wayera no, mɛhwehwɛ no, na deɛ wɔapam no no, mɛkɔ akɔfa no aba, na deɛ wabubuo no, mɛkyekyere no, na deɛ ɔyareɛ no, mɛhyɛ no den; na deɛ wadɔre sradeɛ ne deɛ ne ho yɛ den no, mɛhwɛ no so; mɛhwɛ wɔn tenenee mu.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na mo, me nnwan, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, merebu odwan ne odwan, odwennini ne mpapo ntam atɛn.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛyɛ mo adewa sɛ modidi adidibea pa, na mo adidibea nkaeɛ no, mode mo nan tiatia soɔ? Na monom nsuo a agyene, na mode mo nan hono nkaeɛ no?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na me nnwan no deɛ, wɔnni deɛ mode mo nan atiatia soɔ na wɔnnom deɛ mode mo nan ahono no anaa?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Enti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn ka kyerɛ wɔn nie: Hwɛ, me ara mɛbu nnwan a wɔadɔre sradeɛ ne nnwan a wɔafɔn no ntam atɛn.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ mode mfemu ne mmatire sunsum na mode mo mmɛn pempem ayarefoɔ nyinaa kɔsi sɛ mopansam wɔn kɔ akyiri nti,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> mɛgye me nnwan nkwa na wɔrenyɛ fomfa adeɛ bio, na mɛbu odwan ne odwan ntam atɛn.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na mede odwanhwɛfoɔ baako bɛsi wɔn so na wayɛne wɔn, ɔno ne m’akoa Dawid; ɔno na ɔbɛyɛne wɔn, na ɔno na ɔbɛyɛ wɔn ɔhwɛfoɔ;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na me AWURADE, mɛyɛ wɔn Onyankopɔn, na m’akoa Dawid ayɛ wɔn mu berempɔn; me, AWURADE, na maka.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na me ne wɔn bɛpam asomdwoeɛ apam, na mahye mmoa bɔne ase, asase no so, na wɔatena ɛserɛ so dwoodwoodwoo, na wɔadeda kwaeɛ mu.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na mɛma wɔn ne nsase a ɛdeda me kokoɔ ho hyia no ayɛ nhyira, na mɛma osuo atɔ ne berɛ mu; ɛbɛyɛ nhyira nsuo.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na petee mu nnua bɛso n’aba, na asase ama ne nnɔbaeɛ, na wɔn ho adwo wɔn, wɔn asase so, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE, sɛ mabubu wɔn kɔnnua na mayi wɔn afiri wɔn a wɔdi wɔn nya nsam.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔrenyɛ amanaman fomfa adeɛ bio, na asase so mmoa renni wɔn nam bio, na wɔbɛtena ase dwoodwoo a obiara biara renyi wɔn hu.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na mɛsiesie afuo a ɛyɛ krabɛhwɛ mama wɔn, na ɛkɔm rempra wɔn bio asase no so, na wɔrensoa amanaman ahohora bio.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na wɔbɛhunu sɛ me, AWURADE, wɔn Nyankopɔn na me ne wɔn teɛ, na wɔn, Israel fie ne me man, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na mone me nnwan, me yɛmmea nnwan, moyɛ nnipa, mene mo Nyankopɔn, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"35": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, dane w’ani kyerɛ Seir bepɔ na hyɛ nkɔm tia no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ka kyerɛ no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne wo anya, Seir bepɔ, na mɛtene me nsa atia wo, na mede wo ayɛ afo ne ahodwirideɛ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Mɛma wo nkuro adeda mpan, na adane afo, na woahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ wokuraa daa nitan, na woyii Israel mma hyɛɛ nkrantɛ nsa, wɔn amaneɛ berɛ mu, wɔn asotwe a ɛdi akyire no mu nti,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, mede wo bɛyɛ mogya, na mogya ati wo; sɛ woantane mogya nti, mogya ara na ɛbɛdi w’akyi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mɛyɛ Seir bepɔ ahodwirideɛ ne afo, na matwa deɛ ɔresene ne deɛ ɔresane afiri mu,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na mede atɔfoɔ ahyɛ ne mmepɔ ma ma; wo nkokoɔ so ne wo mmonhwa mu ne wo nsubɔnhwa nyinaa mu na nkrantɛ ano atɔfoɔ bɛguguo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mɛyɛ wo daa afoafo, na wo nkuro no, obiara rentena mu, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ wokaa sɛ: Aman mmienu yi ne nsase mmienu yi, bɛyɛ me deɛ na yɛafa adi so, nso AWURADE wɔ hɔ,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> enti, sɛ mete aseɛ yi, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, mene wo bɛdi no sɛdeɛ w’abufuo ne wo ninkunu a wotane wɔn no nti wotweeɛ no teɛ, na mɛma wɔahu me wɔ wɔn mu, berɛ a mɛbu wɔn atɛn no.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na wɔbɛhunu sɛ me, AWURADE, mate w’abususɛm a woka tiaa Israel mmepɔ no sɛ: Ayɛ afo, yɛn na wɔde ama yɛn sɛ yɛnnie so no nyinaa.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Mode mo ano adi me so akokurokosɛm, na moama me ho nsɛm a moka no adɔɔso; me ara mate.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛberɛ a asase nyinaa ani bɛgyeɛ no, wo deɛ, mɛyɛ wo afo.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Sɛ w’ani gyee Israel fie agyapadeɛ ho sɛ ayɛ afo no, saa ara na mɛyɛ woɔ, afo ara na Seir bepɔ ne Edom mu nyinaa bɛyɛ, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"36": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, hyɛ nkɔm kyerɛ Israel mmepɔ, na ka sɛ: Mo, Israel mmepɔ, montie AWURADE asɛm:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ ɔtamfoɔ ka mo ho asɛm sɛ: Wiɛ, tete sorɔnsorɔmmea no abɛyɛ yɛn deɛ! nti,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> hyɛ nkɔm, na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ wɔayɛ mo afo amene mo, afa nyinaa, ama moadanedane agyapadeɛ ama amanaman no nkaeɛ, na ɔkasafoɔ tɛkyerɛma da mo soɔ, na nkurɔfoɔ sopa mo nti,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> mo, Israel mmepɔ, montie AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn ka kyerɛ mmepɔ ne nkokoɔ ne nsubɔnhwa no, akurofo a ɛdeda mpan ne nkuro a wɔagya a adanedane fomfa adeɛ ne fɛdie ama amanaman nkaeɛ a ɛwowɔ ho hyia no,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> enti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ampa ara, me ninkuntwe gya mu na mɛkasa atia amanaman nkaeɛ no, ne Edom nyinaa a wɔafa m’asase ayɛ wɔn apɛgyadeɛ, wɔn akoma nyinaa anigyeɛ mu, ne ɔkra ho ɛpetoɔ mu, sɛ wɔbɛfa de ayɛ fomfa adeɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛno nti hyɛ Israel asase ho nkɔm, na ka kyerɛ mmepɔ ne nkokoɔ ne nsubɔnhwa ne mmonhwa no sɛ: Hwɛ, me ninkuntwe ne m’anibereɛ mu na mekasa, ɛfiri sɛ moasoa amanaman ahohora;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> enti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Me na mama me nsa soɔ; ampa ara, amanaman a atwa mo ho ahyia no, wɔn ara na wɔbɛsoa wɔn ahohora.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mo Israel mmepɔ, mobɛdennan mo mman mu na moaso mo aba ama me man Israel, ɛrenkyɛre na wɔaba fie.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na hwɛ, meredi mama mo, na madane aba mo nkyɛn, na wɔbɛdɔ mo, na wɔadua mo so aduane.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na mɛma nnipa adɔɔso mo so, Israel fie nyinaa, na wɔbɛtenatena nkuro no mu, na wɔakyekyere afoafo no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na mɛma nnipa ne afieboa adɔɔso mo so, na wɔadɔre awowo bebree, na mama wɔatena mo so sɛ akane berɛ no, na mayɛ mo yie asene mo mfitiaseɛ, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mɛma nnipa anante mo so, me man Israel so, na wɔafa wo ayɛ wɔn deɛ, na woayɛ wɔn agyapadeɛ, na worenkɔ so mma wɔnni mmasugya bio.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛsiane sɛ wɔka kyerɛ wo sɛ: Woyɛ nnipadifoɔ, na woma wo man di mmasugya nti,",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> worenni nnipa nam bio, na woremma wo manfoɔ nni mmasugya bio, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na meremma wonte amanaman ahohorabɔ bio, na worensoa aman nsopa bio, na woremma wo man nni mmasugya bio, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Onipa ba, Israel fie tenaa wɔn asase soɔ no, wɔde abrabɔ ne wɔn nneyɛɛ guu ho fi; na wɔn bra no te sɛ ɔbaa a wayɛ bra fi wɔ m’anim.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɛnna mehwiee m’abufuhyeɛ guu wɔn soɔ, mogya a wɔhwiee guu asase no soɔ no nti, ne wɔn abosom a wɔde guu ho fi no nti.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mepansamm wɔn guu amanaman mu, na mehwetee wɔn mu guu nsase so. Wɔn bra ne wɔn nneyɛɛ so na mebuu wɔn atɛn.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔduruu amanaman a wɔkɔɔ hɔ no mu no, wɔguu me din kronkron no ho fi, sɛ wɔkaa no wɔ wɔn ho sɛ: AWURADE man ne yeinom, nanso wɔafiri n’asase so kɔ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ɛnna menyaa tema maa me din kronkron a Israel fie guu no fi, amanaman a wɔkɔɔ hɔ no mu.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ɛno nti ka kyerɛ Israel fie sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Israel fie, ɛnyɛ mo nti na mereyɛ, na mmom me din kronkron a moguu ho fi, amanaman a mokɔɔ hɔ no mu ntira.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na mɛyɛ me din kɛseɛ a wɔagu ho fi, amanaman a moagu ho fi wɔ wɔn mu no kronkron, na amanaman ahunu sɛ mene AWURADE, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, sɛ mereyi me kronkronyɛ adi, mo mu, wɔn ani so.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na mɛfa mo afiri amanaman no mu, na maboaboa mo ano afiri nsase no nyinaa so, na mede mo asane aba mo asase so.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na mede nsu korɔgyenn bɛpete mo so na mo ho ate; mo ho fi nyinaa ne mo abosonhuhuo nyinaa mu na mɛte mo ho afire,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na mɛma mo akoma foforɔ, na mede honhom foforɔ mahyɛ mo mu, na mɛyi ɔboɔ akoma no afiri mo honam mu, na mama mo honam akoma.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na mede me honhom bɛhyɛ mo mu, na mama moanante m’ahyɛdeɛ so, na moahwɛ m’atemmudeɛ ayɛ.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na mobɛtena asase a mede memaa mo agyanom no so, na moayɛ me ɔman, na me nso, mayɛ mo Onyankopɔn.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na mɛgye mo afiri mo fi nyinaa mu, na mɛfrɛ aduane ama no adɔɔso, na meremma ɛkɔm biara mma mo so.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na mɛma nnua aba, ne mfuo mu nnɔbaeɛ adɔɔso, na moansoa ɛkɔm no nsopa, amanaman mu bio.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ɛno na mobɛkae mo akwammɔne ne mo nneyɛɛ a ɛnyɛ no, na mo amumuyɛ ne mo akyiwadeɛ no nti, mo ho ayɛ mo nwunu, mo anim.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ɛnyɛ mo nti na mereyɛ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, monhu no saa. Momma mo ani nwu na momfɛre wɔ mo akwan ho, Israel fie.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Da a mɛte mo ho afiri mo amumuyɛdeɛ nyinaa mu no, mɛma wɔatenatena nkuro no so, na wɔakyekyere amamfo no,",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> na wɔadɔ asase a na ɛda hɔ hunu no ama aduane aba so no, wɔn a wɔtwam nyinaa anim no.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Na wɔbɛka sɛ: Asase yi a na ɛda hɔ hunu no na adane sɛ Eden turo yi, na nkuro afoafo a ɛdedaa mpan a adwiridwirie no na wɔatoto ho afasuo tete mu yi.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ɛnna amanaman a atwa mo ho ahyia no bɛhunu sɛ, me, AWURADE, na masisi deɛ adwiridwirie no, na matɛ deɛ ɛda hɔ hunu no; me, AWURADE, na maka, na mɛyɛ.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Yei bio na Israel fie bɛbisa no me hɔ, na mɛyɛ mama wɔn. Mɛma wɔadɔɔso ayɛ nnipa pii, sɛ Yerusalem nnwankuo.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Sɛ nnwankuo kronkron, sɛ Yerusalem nnwankuo teɛ n’afahyɛ aseɛ no, saa na nnipa akuakuo bɛyeyɛ nkuro afoafo no ma ma, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"37": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> AWURADE nsa baa me so, na ɔde me firii adi wɔ AWURADE honhom mu, na ɔde me kɔsii bonhwakɛseɛ a nnompe ara nko ayɛ mu ma mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔma me faa so kyini hyiae, na hwɛ, na ɛdɔɔso pa ara wɔ bonhwa no ani, na hwɛ, ɛho akokwa sɛ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔbisaa me sɛ: Onipa ba, nnompe yi bɛnya nkwa anaa? Na mese: AWURADE Nyankopɔn, wo na wonim.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Hyɛ nnompe yi ho nkɔm, na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Mo nnompe a mo ho akokwa, montie AWURADE.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn ka kyerɛ nnompe yi nie: Hwɛ, mɛma ahome aba mo mu, na moanya nkwa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na mede ntini bɛsosɔ mo mu, na mede nam agu mo so, na mede wedeɛ akata mo ho, na mede ahome ahyɛ mo mu, na moanya nkwa, na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ɛnna mehyɛɛ nkɔm sɛdeɛ wɔhyɛɛ me no; na mehyɛɛ nkɔm no, ɛnne bi bae, na hwɛ, awosoɔ bi nie, na nnompe no hyiahyiae, dompe bɛkaa ne dompe ho.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mehwɛe, na hwɛ, ntini baa so, na ɛnam baa ho, na wedeɛ bɛkataa so, nanso na ahome biara nni mu.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnna ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Hyɛ nkɔm kyerɛ mframa no, hyɛ nkɔm, onipa ba, na ka kyerɛ aframa no sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ahome e, firi mframa nnan no mu bra, na bɛhome gu nnipa a wɔakunkum wɔn yi so, na wɔnnya nkwa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ɛnna mehyɛɛ nkɔm sɛdeɛ wɔhyɛɛ me no; na ahome no baa wɔn mu, na wɔnyinyaa nkwa, na wɔsɔre gyinagyinaa wɔn nan so, dɔm kɛseɛ pa ara.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnna ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, nnompe yi yɛ Israel fie no nyinaa. Hwɛ, wɔka sɛ: Yɛn nnompe ho akokwa, na yɛn anidasoɔ ayera; wɔatwa yɛn korakora!",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Enti hyɛ nkɔm, na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, merebuebue mo adamena ano na mayi mo, me man, afiri mo adamena mu, na mede mo akɔ Israel asase so,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na moahunu sɛ mene AWURADE, sɛ mebuebue mo adamena ano, me man, na mema mo firi adamena no mu ba a.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na mede me honhom bɛhyɛ mo mu, na moanya nkwa, na mede mo adua mo asase so, na moahunu sɛ me, AWURADE, na maka na mayɛ, AWURADE asɛm nie.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, fa dua baako na twerɛ so sɛ: Yuda ne Israelfoɔ a wɔka ne ho no deɛ; na fa dua baako nso, na twerɛ so sɛ: Yosef a ɔne Efraim, ne Israel fie a wɔka ne ho no nyinaa dua.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ka ne mmienu bɔ mu yɛ no dua koro, na ɛnyɛ baako wɔ wo nsam.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na sɛ wo man mma bisa wo sɛ: Worenkyerɛ yɛn deɛ wode yeinom reyɛ anaa?",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, merefa Yosef dua (a ɛwɔ Efraim nsam) no ne Israel mmusuakuo a wɔka ne ho no, mede wɔn aka Yuda dua no ho, na mayɛ wɔn dua koro, na wɔayɛ baako, me nsam.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na nnua a woatwerɛtwerɛ soɔ no ntena wo nsam, wɔn anim.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na ka kyerɛ wɔn sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, merekɔfa Israel mma afiri amanaman a wɔakɔ hɔ no mu, na maboa wɔn ano afiri mmaa nyinaa ahyia, na mede wɔn akɔ wɔn asase so,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na mayɛ wɔn ɔman koro, asase no so, Israel mmepɔ no so, na ɔhene baako adi wɔn nyinaa so hene, na wɔrenyɛ aman mmienu bio, na wɔrempae wɔn mu bio nyɛ ahennie mmienu bio,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na wɔremfa wɔn abosonhuhuo ne wɔn atantanneɛ ne wɔn mmaratodeɛ nyinaa ngu wɔn ho fi bio, na mɛgye wɔn nkwa, wɔn tenabea nyinaa a wɔayɛ hɔ bɔne no, na mate wɔn ho, na wɔayɛ me ɔman, na me nso mayɛ wɔn Onyankopɔn.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na m’akoa Dawid bɛdi wɔn so hene, na odwanhwɛfoɔ koro adi wɔn nyinaa so, na wɔanante m’atemmudeɛ mu, na wɔahwɛ m’ahyɛdeɛ ayɛ,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> na wɔatena asase a mede memaa m’akoa Yakob a mo agyanom tenaa soɔ no so, wɔne wɔn mma ne wɔn mma mma akɔsi daa, na m’akoa Dawid bɛyɛ wɔn ɔberempɔn akɔsi daa.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na me ne wɔn bɛpam asomdwoeɛ apam, ɛbɛyɛ wɔn daa apam, na wɔatim na mama wɔakyene, na mede me kronkronbea bɛsi wɔn mu akɔsi daa.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na me tenabea bɛsi wɔn mu, na mayɛ wɔn Onyankopɔn, na wɔn nso wɔayɛ me ɔman,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> na amanaman no ahunu sɛ mene AWURADE a mete Israel ho, berɛ a me kronkronbea si wɔn mu kɔsi daa no."
		},
		"38": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na AWURADE asɛm baa me nkyɛn sɛ:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Onipa ba, fa w’ani si Gog so, Magog asase so, Mesek ne Tubal berempɔn no, na hyɛ nkɔm tia no,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne wo anya, Gog, Mesek ne Tubal berempɔn!",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na mɛgyegye wo, na mede nnarewa mawurawura w’afono mu, na mayi wo ne wo dɔm nyinaa, apɔnkɔ ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ a wɔn nyinaa hyehyɛ ntadeɛ akɛseɛ ne nkumaa na wɔn nyinaa kurakura nkrantɛ no aba;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Persia, Etiopia ne Put ka wɔn ho, wɔn nyinaa wowɔ ɛkyɛm ne dadeɛ kyɛ;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Gomer ne n’asafotoɔ nyinaa, Togarma fie a ɛwɔ atifi fam tɔnn ne n’asafotoɔ nyinaa; aman bebree ka wo ho.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Mia na siesie wo ho, wo ne w’asafo ahodoɔ a wɔaboaboa wɔn ano aba wo nkyɛn nyinaa, na yɛ wɔn ɔhwɛfoɔ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nna pii akyiri no, wɔbɛba abɛhwɛ wo; mfeɛ a ɛdi akyire no mu no, wobɛba asase a wɔadane ɛsofoɔ afiri nkrantɛ ano de wɔn abɛsi hɔ na wɔaboa wɔn ano afiri aman bebree mu no so, Israel mmepɔ a ɛdedaa mpan daa no so; na afei wɔayi ɔman no afiri aman no mu, na wɔn nyinaa te hɔ dwoodwoo.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na wobɛba sɛ ahum, wobɛba sɛ mununkum abɛkata asase no so, wo ne w’asafotoɔ no nyinaa ne aman pii a ɛkeka wo ho.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Na ɛda no, nsɛm bi bɛsɔre w’akomam na woadwene adwemmɔne,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na woaka sɛ: Mɛforo makɔ asase a ano da hɔ no, akɔtua wɔn a wɔwɔ hɔ komm a wɔte hɔ dwoodwoo no, wɔn nyinaa tete hɔ a wɔnni ɔfasuo, na wɔnni aponkɛseɛ ne akyire adaban,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> sɛ worekɔfa asadeɛ na woafom adeɛ afa, na woadane wo nsa nifa atia amamfo a afei wɔtete mu ne ɔman a wɔaboaboa ano afiri amanaman mu na wɔdanedane wɔn ho nya mmoa ne nnoɔma na wɔte asase mfimfini no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Seba ne Dedan ne Tarsis adwadifoɔ ne wɔn a wɔwɔ nkuraase no nyinaa bɛka akyerɛ wo sɛ: Asadeɛ na worebɛfa yi? Fomfa nti na woahyia w’asafo, sɛ worebɛsoa dwetɛ ne sika na woafa mmoa ne nnoɔma na woafom asadeɛ bebree yi?",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Enti, onipa ba, hyɛ nkɔm na ka kyerɛ Gog sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɛnyɛ da a me man Israel bɛtena ase dwoodwoo no na wɔbɛhunu,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na wobɛfiri wo tenabea atifi fam ano nohoa tɔnn aba, wo ne aman bebree a wɔka wo ho a wɔn nyinaa tete apɔnkɔ soɔ, asafo kɛseɛ ne dɔm a ɛso,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> na wobɛtu aba me man Israel so sɛ mununkum abɛkata asase no so. Nna a ɛdi akyire no, mede wo bɛba m’asase so, na amanaman ahu me, berɛ a meyi me kronkronyɛ adi wɔ wo ho, wɔn anim, O Gog!",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Wone deɛ mekaa ne ho asɛm tete nna no mu a menam me nkoa, Israel adiyifoɔ a wɔkaa adiyisɛm nna no mu, mfeɛ pii no so mekaa sɛ mede wo bɛba wɔn soɔ no?",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɛda no, ɛda a Gog bɛba Israel soɔ no, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, m’abufuhyeɛ bɛdɛre,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na me ninkuntwe mu, m’anibereɛ gya no mu, maka sɛ: Ampa ara, ɛda no awosoɔ kɛseɛ bɛba Israel asase so,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na ɛpo mu mpataa ne ewiem nnomaa bɛwoso m’anim. Wiram mmoa ne wɔn a wɔwea asase soɔ nyinaa, ne nnipa a wɔwɔ asase so nyinaa, na mmepɔ bɛdwiri agu, na abotan korɔnkorɔn ahwehwe ase, na afasuo nyinaa ahwehwe ase.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na mɛfrɛ nkrantɛ atia no, me mmepɔ nyinaa so, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, wɔn nyinaa kurakura nkrantɛ, obi de bɛka ne nua;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na mede owuyadeɛ ne mogya ne no bɛdi, na mɛtɔ osuo a ɛhwie na ɛsram soɔ ne asukɔtweaa, ogya ne sɔfe agu ɔno ne n’asafotoɔ ne aman bebree a wɔkeka ne ho no so;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na mɛyɛ me ho kɛse na mayɛ me ho kronkron, na mama wɔahu me, amanaman bebree anim, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE."
		},
		"39": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na wo onipa ba, hyɛ Gog ho nkɔm na ka sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Hwɛ, me ne wo anya, Gog, Mesek ne Tubal berempɔn!",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na mɛdanedane wo na mama woatu afiri atifi fam nohoa tɔnn aba, na mede wo aba Israel mmepɔ so;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na mɛbɔ wo tadua afiri wo nsa benkum mu, na mama w’agyan afiri wo nsa nifa mu atotɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Israel mmepɔ so na wobɛtɔ, wo ne w’asafotoɔ nyinaa ne aman a wɔka wo ho no; nnomaa a ɛdi nam, ntakraboa nyinaa ne wiram mmoa na mede wo bɛyɛ wɔn aduane.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Mpaperɛ so na wobɛtɔ, na me na maka, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na mɛsoma ogya akɔ Magog ne wɔn a wɔtete nsuano aman mu dwoodwoo no mu, na wɔahunu sɛ mene AWURADE.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na mɛma wɔahunu me din kronkron me man Israel mu, na meremma wɔngu me din kronkron no ho fi bio, na amanaman ahunu sɛ mene AWURADE, Israel mu kronkronni no.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hwɛ, ɛreba na wɔbɛyɛ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ɛno ara ne da a maka ho asɛm no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ɛnna Israel nkuro mufoɔ bɛfiri adi akɔto akodeɛ no mu gya ahyeɛ, akyɛm nkumaa ne akyɛm akɛseɛ, tadua ne agyan ne mporibaa ne mpea, na wɔde ayɛ nnyina asɔ mfeɛ nson;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na wɔrenkɔ wiram anyina, na wɔrentwa bi mfiri kwaeɛ mu, na akodeɛ no na wɔbɛsɔ; na wɔbɛfom wɔn a wɔfomm wɔn, na wɔafom afa wɔn a wɔfomm wɔn faeɛ no, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɛda no, mɛma Gog baabi wɔ Israel a ɛbɛyɛ n’asieeɛ. Ɛwɔ akwantemfoɔ bonhwa a ɛwɔ ɛpo no anim fam, na ɛbɛsi akwantemfoɔ kwan, na ɛhɔ na wɔbɛsie Gog ne n’asafo yuu no nyinaa, na wɔafrɛ hɔ sɛ: Gog asafo yuu no bonhwa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na Israel fie bɛsie wɔn sɛ wɔde redwira asase no abosome nson.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na asase no so aman no nyinaa bɛsie wɔn, na ayɛ wɔn din, da a mɛnya animuonyam no, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔbɛyiyi mmarima ama wɔakyinkyini asase no so asie wɔn a wɔaka asase no soɔ no de adwira ho; abosome nson akyiri no, wɔbɛtwee ahwehwɛ sɛ funu bi nni hɔ bio.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na anantefoɔ no kyini asase no so, na wɔn mu bi hunu onipa dompe a, ɔbɛhyɛ hɔ agyiraeɛ de akɔsi sɛ asiefoɔ no bɛba abɛsie no, Gog asafo yuu bonhwa no mu.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> (Na kuro Hamona bi nso wɔ hɔ). Sei na wɔbɛdwira asase no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na wo, onipa ba, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ka kyerɛ nnomaa, ntakraboa nyinaa ne wiram mmoa nyinaa sɛ: Monhyia mmra, mommoa mo ano mfiri mmaa nyinaa mmra me kum afɔdeɛ a makum ama mo no ho, Israel mmepɔ so kum afɔdeɛ kɛseɛ, na mommɛdi nam na monnom mogya.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nnɔmmarima nam na mobɛdie, na asase so aberempɔn mogya na mobɛnom, adwennini, nnwanten mma ne mpapo ne anantwinini, Basan ayɛmmoa ara nko.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na mobɛdi sradeɛ amee, na moanom mogya abo, me kum afɔdeɛ a mekum maa mo no mu,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na apɔnkɔ ne apɔnkɔsotefoɔ, nnɔmmarima ne akofoɔ nyinaa bɛmee mo, me pono so, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na mede m’animuonyam bɛsi amanaman nyinaa mu na wɔahunu m’atɛn a mabuo ne me nsa a mede ato wɔn soɔ;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> na Israel fie bɛhunu sɛ me, AWURADE, mene wɔn Nyankopɔn ɛfiri da no de rekorɔ,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na amanaman bɛhunu sɛ Israel fie amumuyɛ nti na wɔtuu wɔn kɔeɛ; ɛsiane sɛ wɔyɛɛ me bɔne nti na meyii m’ani huntaa wɔn, na mede wɔn hyɛɛ wɔn ahohiahiafoɔ nsa, na wɔn nyinaa totɔɔ nkrantɛ ano.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Wɔn fi ne wɔn mmaratodeɛ so na me ne wɔn diiɛ, na meyii m’ani huntaa wɔn.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ɛno nti sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Afei mede Yakob nnommum no bɛsane aba, na mahunu Israel fie nyinaa mmɔbɔ, na matwe me din kronkron no ho ninkunu,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na wɔbɛsoa wɔn ahohora ne wɔn bɔne a wɔyɛɛ me no nyinaa, berɛ a wɔte wɔn asase so dwoodwoo na obiara nni hɔ a ɔyi wɔn hu no,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> berɛ a makɔfa wɔn afiri aman mu asane aba, na makɔboaboa wɔn ano afiri wɔn atamfoɔ nsase so, na mayi me kronkronyɛ adi wɔ wɔn mu, amanaman bebree anim no.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na wɔbɛhunu sɛ mene AWURADE wɔn Nyankopɔn, sɛ memaa wɔtuu wɔn kɔɔ amanaman mu, na mekɔtasee wɔn baa wɔn asase so bio, na mannya wɔn mu biara wɔ hɔ bio.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Na merenyi m’ani nhunta wɔn bio, ɛfiri sɛ mahwie me honhom agu Israel fie so, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"40": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Yɛn tukorɔ afe a ɛtɔ so aduonunum no afe no ahyɛaseɛ bosome no da a ɛtɔ so du no, kuro no bɔ akyiri afe a ɛtɔ so dunan mu no, ɛda no ara no AWURADE nsa baa me so, na ɔde me baa hɔ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Nyankopɔn anisoadehunu mu na ɔde me baa Israel asase soɔ, na ɔde me kɔgyinaa bepɔ a ɛkorɔn papaapa so, na ɛso te sɛ kuro bi a wɔakyekyere no anafoɔ fam.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na ɔde me baa hɔ no, na hwɛ, ɔbarima bi a ne su te sɛ kɔbere mfrafraeɛ nie, na siwabire homa ne susuo demmire kura ne nsamu, na ɔgyina ɛpono kɛseɛ no ano.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔbarima no kasa kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, fa w’ani hwɛ, na fa w’aso tie, na fa w’adwene to deɛ merema woahunu no nyinaa so. Na sɛdeɛ ɛbɛyɛ na mɛma woahunu nti na wɔde wo baa ha. Ka deɛ wohunu yi nyinaa kyerɛ Israel fie.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na hwɛ, na ɔfasuo atwa efie no ho ahyia, na ɔbarima no kura demmire a ne tentene yɛ basafa mmiɛnsa wɔ ne nsamu, nsamu trɛ da anammɔn baako ne fa biara so, na ɔsusuu ɔfasuo no trɛ, demmire no baako, na ne korɔn nso demmire baako tentene.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ɛnna ɔbaa ɛpono kɛseɛ a ani kyerɛ apueeɛ fam kwan soɔ no ho, na ɔforoo ne ntwedeɛ no, na ɔsusuu ɛpono kɛseɛ no ano, ɛpono ase a ne trɛ yɛ demmire baako, ɛne ɛpono ase baako a ne trɛ yɛ demmire baako.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ne pia no ntam, basafa mmienu ne fa, mmienu ne fa; ne ɛpono kɛseɛ no pono ase a ɛwɔ ntwonoo a ɛkyerɛ efie no ho no, demmire baako;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na ɔsusuu ɛpono kɛseɛ no ntwonoo a ɛkyerɛ efie no, demmire baako;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na ɔsusuu ntwonoo no basafa nnan ne n’adum no, basafa baako, na ntwonoo no kyerɛ efie no mu.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na apueeɛ fam ponkɛseɛ no mpia no, mmiɛnsa wɔ ha na mmiɛnsa wɔ ha, ne mmiɛnsa no nyinaa nsusuiɛ yɛ baako, na ɛha ne ɛha adum no nsusuiɛ yɛ baako.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na ɔsusuu ɛpono kɛseɛ no ano trɛ basafa nnum, na ɛpono kɛseɛ no ntwemu yɛ basafa nsia ne fa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na mpia no anim hyekwan anammɔn baako ne fa wɔ ha ne ɛha, na pia baako yɛ basafa mmiɛnsa wɔ ha ne basafa mmiɛnsa wɔ ha.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔsusuu ɛpono kɛseɛ no firii pia baako atifi de kɔsii baako atifi, ne trɛ yɛ basafa dummienu ne fa, ɛpono ne ɛpono ntam.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɔyɛɛ adum no basafa du, na adum no ho wɔ abannwa a ɛtwa ɛpono kɛseɛ no ho hyiahyia.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɛfiri ɛpono kɛseɛ a wɔfa mu hyɛne mu no anim kɔsi emu fam ponkɛseɛ no ntwonoo anim yɛ basafa aduonu nnum.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na mpomma aniahunuankansa wowɔ mpia no ne n’adum no ho, kɔ ponkɛseɛ no mu fam, de twa ho hyiahyia, ne ntam fasuo no ho saa ara, na mpomma wɔ mu hyia, na mmɛ wowɔ adum no ho.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me kɔɔ abannwa a ɛwɔ akyire no soɔ, na hwɛ, na adammoa wowɔ hɔ, ne aboɔ nsɛeɛ a wɔayɛ no abannwa so hɔ atwa ahyia. Adammoa aduasa na na ɛwɔ aboɔ nsɛeɛ no ho.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na aboɔ nsɛeɛ no wɔ aponkɛseɛ no nkyɛn mu ma no ne aponkɛseɛ no ntwemu sɛ; ɛne aboɔ nsɛeɛ no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔsusuu akyire abannwa no, ne trɛ firi ɛpono kɛseɛ no anim de kɔsi emu fam abannwa no anim, basafa aduonum, apueeɛ fam ne atifi fam.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɛpokɛseɛ a ani hwɛ atifi fam, ɛho fam abannwa no ho no, ɔsusuu ne ntwemu ne ne trɛ",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ne ne mpia, mmiɛnsa wɔ ha na mmiɛnsa wɔ ha, ne n’adum ne ne ntam fasuo. Ne nsusuiɛ te sɛ akane ponkɛseɛ no deɛ no, ne tentene yɛ basafa aduonu nnum, na ne ntwemu basafa dummienu ne fa.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ne mpomma ne ntam afasuo, ne mmɛ no nsusuiɛ te sɛ ɛpono kɛseɛ a ani hwɛ apueeɛ fam no deɛ no. Na ntwedeɛ nson na wɔforo kɔ mu, na ne ntam fasuo no sisi anim.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na emu fam abannwa no ponkɛseɛ si ɛpono kɛseɛ a ɛhwɛ atifi fam, ne deɛ ɛhwɛ apueeɛ fam no ntentensoɔ, na ɔsusu firii ɛpono kɛseɛ ano kɔsii ɛpono kɛseɛ ano, basafa aduonum.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me kɔɔ anafoɔ fam, na hwɛ, na ɛpono kɛseɛ wɔ anafoɔ fam nso, na ɔsusuu n’adum ne ne ntam fasuo sɛdeɛ saa nsusuiɛ no teɛ;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> na mpomma twa ɛno ne ne ntam fasuo ho hyia sɛdeɛ saa mpomma no teɛ; ne ntwemu yɛ basafa aduonu nnum, na ne trɛ yɛ basafa dummienu ne fa,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na n’aforoeɛ yɛ ntwedeɛ nson, na ne ntam fasuo sisi anim, na mmɛ wowɔ ho, baako wɔ ha na baako wɔ ha, n’adum ho.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na abannwa a ɛwɔ mu no ponkɛseɛ wɔ anafoɔ fam, na ɔsusu firii ɛpono kɛseɛ ano de kɔsii ɛpono kɛseɛ ano, anafoɔ fam, basafa aduonum.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me faa anafoɔ fam ponkɛseɛ no mu kɔɔ abannwa a ɛwɔ mu no soɔ; na ɔsusuu anafoɔ fam ponkɛseɛ no, sɛdeɛ saa nsusuiɛ no teɛ;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ne ne mpia ne n’adum ne ne ntam fasuo, sɛdeɛ saa nsusuiɛ no teɛ, na mpomma wowɔ ho ne ne ntam fasuo ho hyia; ne ntwemu yɛ basafa aduonu nnum, na ne trɛ yɛ basafa dummienu ne fa.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na ntam fasuo twa ho hyia, ne ntwemu yɛ basafa dummienu ne fa, na ne trɛ basafa mmienu ne fa.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Na ne ntam fasuo no hwɛ ɛho fam abannwa so, na mmɛ wowɔ n’adum ho, na aforoeɛ no yɛ ntwedeɛ nwɔtwe.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me kɔɔ abannwa a ɛwɔ mu no soɔ apueeɛ fam. Na ɔsusuu ɛpokɛseɛ no sɛdeɛ saa nsusuiɛ no teɛ,",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> na ne mpia ne n’adum ne ne ntam fasuo te sɛdeɛ saa nsusuiɛ no teɛ, na mpomma twa ɛno ne ne ntam fasuo ho hyia, ne ntwemu yɛ basafa aduonu nnum, na ne trɛ yɛ basafa dummienu ne fa.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Na ne ntam fasuo no hwɛ ɛho fam abannwa so, na mmɛ wowɔ n’adum ho ɛha ne ɛha, na n’aforoeɛ yɛ ntwedeɛ nwɔtwe.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me kɔɔ atifi fam ponkɛseɛ no ano, na ɔsusuu sɛdeɛ saa nsusuiɛ no teɛ,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> ne mpia, n’adum ne ne ntam fasuo; na mpomma twa ho hyia; ne ntwemu yɛ basafa aduonu nnum, na ne trɛ yɛ basafa dummienu ne fa;",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> na ne ntam fasuo hwɛ ɛho fam abannwa so, na mmɛ wowɔ n’adum ho, ɛha ne ɛha, na n’aforoeɛ yɛ ntwedeɛ nwɔtwe.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Na dammoa ne ano pono wɔ ponkɛseɛ no adum no ho, ɛhɔ na wɔhohoro ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ho.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Na ɛpono kɛseɛ no ntwonoo no mu no, apono mmienu sisi ha, na mmienu nso sisi ha, na ɛho na wɔkum ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne asodie afɔdeɛ.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Na ntwonoo no akyi nkyɛn mu, a ɛda deɛ wɔreforo kɔ ɛpono kɛseɛ no ano no atifi fam hɔ, apono mmienu sisi hɔ, na ɛpono kɛseɛ no ntwonoo no nkyɛn mu ha nso, apono mmienu nso sisi hɔ.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Apono nnan wɔ ɔfa ha, na apono nnan nso wɔ ɔfa ha, ɛpono kɛseɛ no nkyɛn mu, apono nwɔtwe ho na wɔkum mmoa.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Na apono nnan sisi aforoeɛ no ho, ɛyɛ aboɔ a wɔasene. Ne ntwemu yɛ anammɔn mmienu ne fa, ne trɛ yɛ anammɔn ne fa, ne korɔn yɛ anammɔn baako ne fa; ɛso na wɔde adeɛ a wɔde kum ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne okum afɔdeɛ no guo;",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> na nkɔtɔkorɔ nta a ɛyɛ nsamu trɛ hyehyɛ ɛdan no mu hyia; na apono no so na wɔde ayɛyɛdeɛ nam no guo.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Na ponkɛseɛ a ɛwɔ mu no akyi na na adammoa mmienu wowɔ, abannwa a ɛwɔ mu no so, baako si atifi fam ponkɛseɛ no nkyɛn mu, na anim hwɛ anafoɔ fam, baako nso si anafoɔ fam ponkɛseɛ no nkyɛn mu, na anim hwɛ atifi fam.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Dammoa a ani hwɛ anafoɔ fam yi yɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔhwɛ efie no soɔ no dea,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> na dammoa a ani hwɛ atifi fam no yɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔhwɛ afɔrebukyia no soɔ no dea. Wɔne Sadok mma a wɔfiri Lewifoɔ no mu, a wɔbɛn AWURADE, bɛsom no no.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Na ɔsusuu abannwa no ntwemu, basafa aduonum, ne ne trɛ, basafa aduonum, ɛyɛ ahinanan; na afɔrebukyia si ɛdan no anim.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me kɔɔ ɛdan no ntwonoo mu, na ɔsusuu ntwonoo no adum no, basafa mmienu ne fa wɔ ha, na basafa mmienu ne fa wɔ ha; ne ɛpono kɛseɛ no trɛ basafa baako ne fa wɔ ha ne basafa baako ne fa wɔ ha.",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> Ntwonoo no ntwemu yɛ basafa du, na ne trɛ yɛ basafa nnum ne fa, ntwedeɛ a wɔforo kɔ mu no so; na adum sisi ntwonoo adum no anim, baako wɔ ha na baako wɔ ha."
		},
		"41": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me kɔɔ asɔredan no mu, na ɔsusuu adum no basafa mmiɛnsa trɛ wɔ ha ne basafa mmiɛnsa trɛ wɔ ha, ɛne ntomadan no trɛ.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ano kwan trɛ yɛ basafa nnum, na ano kwan no nkyɛnnkyɛn yɛ basafa mmienu ne fa wɔ ha na basafa mmienu ne fa wɔ ha; na ɔsusuu ne ntwemu, basafa aduonu ne ne trɛ, basafa du.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɛnna ɔkɔɔ dan no mu kɔsusuu ɛpono ano adum no, basafa baako, ne ɛpono no, basafa mmiɛnsa, na ɛpono no trɛ yɛ basafa mmiɛnsa ne fa;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na ɔsusuu ne ntwemu basafa du ne ne trɛ basafa du, asɔredan no anim; na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Ɛha ne kronkron mu kronkronbea.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ɛnna ɔsusuu ɛdan no fasuo, basafa mmiɛnsa, ne ɛho mpia no trɛ, basafa mmienu de twaa ɛdan no nyinaa ho hyiaeɛ.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na nkyɛn mu mpia no, pia si pia so ahodoɔ mmiɛnsa, saa ahodoɔ aduasa, na ɛkɔ ɔfasuo a ɛwɔ ɛdan no ho ma mpia no so, twa ho hyia, ɛma no sosɔ mu, nanso ɛnsosɔ ɛdan no fasuo mu;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na mpia no rekɔ soro hyia no, na emu retrɛ, na ɛdan no ho mpia no kɔ soro ara twa ɛdan no ho hyia, enti emu trɛe wɔ ɛdan no ho wɔ soro, na ɛde saa firi aseɛ deɛ no mu fa mfimfini deɛ no mu kɔ soro deɛ no mu.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na mehunuu ɛdan no ho bamma a ɛtwa ho hyia a ɛne nkyɛn mu mpia no nnyinasoɔ, ne hini korɔn duru basafa mmiɛnsa ɛne demmire no pɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Nkyɛnmu mpia no akyiri fasuo no trɛ yɛ basafa mmienu ne fa, na deɛ wɔgyaa no ɛdan no ho nkyɛn mu mpia no ho no nso saa ara.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na adammoa no ntam trɛ yɛ basafa du de twa ɛdan no ho hyia twan.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na nkyɛn mu mpia no apono ano kwan kɔ deɛ wɔgyaeɛ no so, ɛpono ano baako hwɛ atifi fam, na ɛpono ano baako hwɛ anafoɔ fam, na ɛkwan a wɔgyaeɛ no trɛ yɛ basafa mmienu ne fa twa ho hyia.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na ɛdan a ɛsi efie no akyiri adihɔ, atɔeɛ fam no trɛ yɛ basafa aduasa nnum, na ɛdan no fasuo trɛ yɛ basafa mmienu ne fa de twa ho hyia, na ne ntwemu yɛ basafa aduanan nnum.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔsusuu ɛdan no ntwemu, ɛyɛ basafa aduonum, ne afikyire adihɔ ne ɛhɔ dan no ne n’afasuo ntwemu, basafa aduonum;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na ɛdan no anim trɛ ne n’adihɔ no deɛ, apueeɛ fam, yɛ basafa aduonum.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Saa na ɔsusuu ɛdan a ɛsi n’adihɔ no anim a ɛkɔduruu n’akyi ne ɛho mmrannaa a ɛwɔ ho ntwemu, basafa aduonum, ne asɔredan no mu abannwa no ntwonoo.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Apono ase ne mpomma aniahunuankansa ne mmrannaa a ɛtwa ne mmiɛnsa no ho hyia no, aponnwa a wɔde dua adura ho ahyia no, ne fam de kɔka mpomma no ho no, ne (mpomma a wɔakatakata ho no),",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> apono ano atifi hɔnom, ɛdan no mu fam ne akyire fam ne afasuo no nyinaa twan, emu fam ne ɛho fam, ne nyinaa wɔ ne nsusuiɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na wɔayeyɛ kerubim ne mmɛ, na abɛ wɔ kerub ntam, na kerub wɔ anim mmienu;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na onipa anim hwɛ abɛ wɔ fa ha, na gyata anim hwɛ abɛ wɔ fa ha; wɔyɛɛ no ɛdan no mu nyinaa hyiae.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ɛfiri fam kɔsi pono no atifi na wɔayeyɛ kerubim ne mmɛ no asɔredan no fasuo ho.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Asɔredan no wɔ aponnwa ahinanan, na kronkronbea no anim deɛ te saa ara.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Afɔrebukyia no yɛ dua, ne korɔn yɛ basafa baako ne fa, na ne ntwemu yɛ basafa baako, na ne ntweaso ne ne nnyinasoɔ ne n’afasuo yɛ dua. Na ɔka kyerɛ me sɛ: Yei ne ɛpono a ɛsi AWURADE anim.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na asɔredan no asa ne pia kronkron no wɔ apono mmienu.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na apono no yɛ ntanta, apono mmukamu mmienu mmienu. Mmienu yɛ ɛpono baako deɛ, na ɛpono mmienu yɛ baako deɛ.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔayɛ asɔredan ano apono no so kerubim ne mmɛ, sɛdeɛ wɔyɛɛ no afasuo no ho no. Na dua ntiasoɔ wɔ ntwonoo no anim adihɔ fam.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na mpomma aniahunuankansa ne mmɛ wɔ ɔfa ha ne fa ha, ntwonoo no nkyɛn mu ne ɛdan no nkyɛn mu mpia ne nkatasoɔ mpuna no ho."
		},
		"42": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me firii adi faa atifi fam kwan so kɔɔ ɛho fam abannwa no soɔ, na ɔde me kɔɔ dammoa a ɛda adihɔ ne ɛhɔ dan no ntentensoɔ a ɛhwɛ atifi fam no ho,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ne ntwemu no, ɛyɛ basafa aduonum, ɛpono ano wɔ atifi fam, na ne trɛ yɛ basafa aduonu nnum;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ɛda abannwa a ɛwɔ fie no ntentensoɔ, ɛyɛ basafa du; abrannaa hwɛ abrannaa anim, nsamsoɔ a ɛtɔ so mmiɛnsa mu,",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na adammoa no anim na ɔkwan a ne trɛ yɛ basafa nnum wɔ fie afa mu, ɛkɔ basafa aduonum kwan a ɛwɔ mu no so; na apono no ano hwɛ atifi fam.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na soro dammoa no yɛ ntiantia, ɛfiri sɛ mmrannaa no afa fa, na ɛntrɛ sɛ ɛdan no mfimfini no ase deɛ no,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ɛfiri sɛ ɛyɛ aborɔsansa, na ɛnni adum sɛ mmannwa no adum no. Ne saa nti na wɔadwom afiri aseɛ deɛ ne mfimfini deɛ no so, firi fam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na aboɔ ban a ɛwɔ adihɔ fam siane dammoa no, ɛho fam abannwa no mu hwɛ dammoa no anim, ne ntwemu basafa aduonu nnum,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> na adammoa a ɛhwɛ ɛho fam abannwa no ntwemu yɛ basafa aduonu nnum, na hwɛ, asɔredan no anim deɛ na ɛyɛ basafa aduonum;",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> na adammoa yi pue aboɔ ban no so; ɔkwan a obi firi ɛho fam abannwa no so reba mu a ɔfa soɔ no da apueeɛ fam.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Abannwa no fasuo trɛ a ɛhwɛ apueeɛ fam no, atuntunatoɔ ne ɛhɔ dan ntentensoɔ mu na adammoa wɔ,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na ɔkwan da anim. Ɛte sɛ adammoa a ɛwɔ atifi fam no, ne ntwemu ne ne trɛ saa ara ne n’adifire akwan nyinaa ne ne nsiesieeɛ; na sɛdeɛ n’apono ano teɛ no,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> saa ara nso na adammoa a ɛwɔ anafoɔ fam no teteɛ, ɛpono ano wɔ ɔkwan no ti, ɛne ɔkwan a ɛda ɛho aban no anim, ɔkwan a wɔfiri apueeɛ fam nam so ba mu no.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Atifi fam adammoa ne anafoɔ fam adammoa a ɛsisi adihɔ no anim no ne adammoa kronkron a asɔfoɔ a wɔbɛn AWURADE no bɛdi akronkronneɛ mu akronkronneɛ no; ɛhɔ na wɔmfa akronkronneɛ mu akronkronneɛ nguguo, aduane afɔdeɛ ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne asodie ho afɔdeɛ no, na ɛhɔ yɛ kronkron.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Asɔfoɔ no hyɛne mu a, wɔmmfiri kronkronbea hɔ mmfiri adi nnkɔ ɛho fam abannwa no so, na emu hɔ na wɔmfa wɔn ntadeɛ a wɔde som nguo, na ɛyɛ kronkron. Wɔnhyehyɛ ntadeɛ foforɔ ansa na wɔabɛn deɛ ɛyɛ ɔman no deɛ ho.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na ɔwiee dan a ɛwɔ mu no susuo no, ɔde me firii adi faa ɛpono kɛseɛ a ani hwɛ apueeɛ fam no kwan so, na ɔsusu hyiaa twan,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ɔde susuo demmire no susuu apueeɛ fam deɛ no basafa ahanu aduonum, susuo demmire no so de twa hyiae.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ɔsusuu atifi fam deɛ no basafa ahanu aduonum, susuo demmire no so, de twa hyiae.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ɔsusuu anafoɔ fam deɛ no basafa ahanu aduonum, susuo demmire no so;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ɔdane kɔɔ atɔeɛ fam kɔsusuu basafa ahanu aduonum, susuo demmire no so.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Afa nnan no so na ɔsusuu no. Ɔfasuo twa ho hyia twan; ne ntwemu yɛ basafa ahanu aduonum ne ne trɛ yɛ basafa ahanu aduonum, sɛ ɛntwa kronkronbea ne anihumafoɔ deɛ ntam."
		},
		"43": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me baa ɛpono kɛseɛ a ɛhwɛ apueeɛ kwan soɔ no ano.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na hwɛ, Israel Nyankopɔn animuonyam refiri apueeɛ kwan so reba, na ne nne te sɛ nsuo bebree nne, na n’animuonyam maa asase harann.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na adeɛ a mehunuiɛ no su te sɛ adeɛ a mehunuiɛ berɛ a ɔba bɛsɛee kuro no; na ɛyɛ anisoadehunu a ɛte sɛ adeɛ a mehunuu no Asuo Kebar ho no; na mede m’anim butuu fam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na AWURADE animuonyam no baa efie hɔ ɛpono kɛseɛ a ɛhwɛ apueeɛ fam no kwan so.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na honhom no maa me so de me baa abannwa a ɛwɔ mu no so, na hwɛ, AWURADE animuonyam no ayɛ efie no ma.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na metee sɛ obi firi efie no mu ne me rekasa, na ɔbarima bi gyina me nkyɛn.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, m’ahennwa sibea ne m’anammɔn agyinaeɛ a mɛtena hɔ, Israelfoɔ mu akɔsi daa nie. Na Israel fie rengu me din kronkron ho fi bio, sɛdeɛ wɔn ne wɔn ahemfo de wɔn adwamammɔ ne wɔn ahemfo afunu yɛeɛ no, wɔn sorɔnsorɔmmea so,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> sɛ wɔde wɔn apono ase too m’apono ase ho na wɔde wɔn aponnwa nkyɛn mu sii m’aponnwa nkyɛn mu ho, maa ɔfasuo nko sii me ne wɔn ntam no, na wɔde wɔn akyiwadeɛ a wɔyɛ guu me din kronkron no ho fi maa mehyee wɔn m’abufuo mu no.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Afei deɛ, wɔnyi wɔn adwamammɔ no wɔn ahemfo afunu no mfiri me nkyɛn nkɔ akyirikyiri, na mɛtena wɔn mu akɔsi daa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Wo, onipa ba, fa asɔrefie yi kyerɛ Israel fie, na wɔn anim ngu ase, wɔn amumuyɛ ho, na ma wɔnsusu susudeɛ no.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na sɛ wɔn anim gu ase deɛ wɔayɛ nyinaa ho a, kyerɛ wɔn asɔrefie no suban ne ne nsiesieeɛ, ne n’adifire ne ne muba, ne ne su nyinaa ne n’ahyɛdeɛ nyinaa, ne ne ban nyinaa ne ɛho mmara nyinaa, na twerɛ no wɔn anim, na wɔnhwɛ ne su no nyinaa ne ɛho ahyɛdeɛ nyinaa, na wɔnni so.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Yei ne asɔrefie no ho mmara: Bepɔ no atifi ne ɛhyeɛ a ɛtwa ho hyia twan nyinaa nyɛ akronkronneɛ mu kronkron. Hwɛ, efie no ho mmara nie.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na yeinom ne afɔrebukyia no nsusuiɛ, (basafa baako yɛ basafa ne nsa mu trɛ soɔ), ne nnyinasoɔ yɛ anammɔn ne fa, na ne trɛ yɛ anammɔn baako ne fa, na anoano hini a ɛtwa ho hyia yɛ nsaama baako; na yei ne afɔrebukyia no ase.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ɛfiri fam nnyinasoɔ no so de kɔsi aseɛ faferɛ no so yɛ basafa baako, na ne trɛ yɛ anammɔn baako ne fa, na ɛfiri faferɛ kumaa no so kɔsi faferɛ kɛseɛ no soɔ yɛ basafa mmienu, na ne trɛ yɛ anammɔn baako ne fa.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na afɔrebukyia no yɛ basafa mmienu, na ɛfiri afɔrebukyia no so de kɔ soro wɔ mmɛn nnan.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na afɔrebukyia no ntwemu yɛ basafa nsia, na ne trɛ nsia, n’afa nnan, ɛyɛ ahinanan.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na faferɛ no ntwemu yɛ basafa nson, na n’afa nnan ne trɛ yɛ nson, na ano a ɛtwa ho hyia no yɛ bɛyɛ anammɔn baako, na ne nnyinasoɔ anammɔn baako ne fa twa ho hyia; na n’aforoeɛ hwɛ apueeɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Yeinom ne afɔrebukyia no ho ahyɛdeɛ, da a wɔbɛyɛ no sɛ wɔmmɔ so hyeɛ afɔdeɛ na wɔmpete so mogya no;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Asɔfoɔ, Lewifoɔ a wɔfiri Sadok asefoɔ mu a wɔbɛba abɛbɛn me sɛ wɔrebɛsom me no, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, ma wɔn nantwiburuwa na wɔmfa mmɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> na fa ne mogya no bi keka ne mmɛn nnan ne faferɛ no ahinanan ne anoano a ɛtwa ho hyia, fa yi ɛho bɔne na pata ma no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na fa bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nantwinini no, na hye no, asɔrefie no baabi a wɔayi ato hɔ, kronkronbea adihɔ fam no.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɛda a ɛtɔ so mmienu no, fa ɔpapo a ɔnni dɛm bra bɛbɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, na wɔmfa nyi afɔrebukyia no ho bɔne, sɛdeɛ wɔde nantwinini no yiiɛ no.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Sɛ wowie bɔne no yi a, fa nantwiburuwa a ɔnni dɛm ne nnwankuo mu adwennini a ɔnni dɛm bra,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na fa wɔn bra AWURADE anim, na asɔfoɔ no mfa nkyene ngu wɔn so, na wɔmfa wɔn mmɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ mma AWURADE.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Nnanson na fa ɔpapo bɔ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ daa, na nantwiburuwa ne nnwankuo mu dwennini a ɛdɛm biara nni wɔn ho nso na wɔmfa mmɔ.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Nnanson na wɔmfa mpata mma afɔrebukyia no, na wɔnnwira ho na wɔmfa nhyɛ nsa.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Na wɔwie nna no a, da a ɛtɔ so nwɔtwe de rekorɔ no, asɔfoɔ no mmɔ mo hyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne mo asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ, afɔrebukyia no so, na m’ani bɛsɔ mo, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"44": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me faa kronkronbea no anim ponkɛseɛ a ɛhwɛ apueeɛ no kwan soɔ, na ɛno deɛ, na wɔato mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Ɛpono kɛseɛ yi, wɔato mu ara, wɔrenhini, na obi remfa mu mma mu, ɛfiri sɛ AWURADE, Israel Nyankopɔn afa mu aba mu nti, wɔato mu ara.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔberempɔn no nko, ɔberempɔn a ɔyɛ nti na ɔbɛtena mu adidie, AWURADE anim. Ɔbɛfa ɛpono kɛseɛ no ntwonoo kwan so ahyɛne mu, na wafa ɔkwan no so afiri adi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me faa atifi fam ponkɛseɛ no kwan so de me baa asɔredan no anim, na mehwɛe, na hwɛ, na AWURADE animuonyam no ahyɛ AWURADE dan no ma, na mehwee fam de m’anim butui.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na AWURADE ka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba, fa w’ani hwɛ, na fa w’aso tie deɛ merebɛka akyerɛ woɔ, AWURADE fie ahyɛdeɛ nyinaa ne ne mmara nyinaa ho no nyinaa, na hwɛ no yie na wɔn a ɛfata sɛ wɔba asɔrefie no aba, na wɔn a wɔmfata no, moapam wɔn.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ka kyerɛ atuatefoɔ, Israel fie no, sɛ: Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Israel fie, mo akyiwadeɛ no nyinaa, momma no nnɔɔso mma mo,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> sɛ mode ananafoɔ mma, akoma mu momonotofoɔ ne honam mu momonotofoɔ baeɛ, sɛ wɔmmɛtena me kronkronbea ngu me fie ho fi, sɛ mode m’aduane, sradeɛ ne mogya baeɛ, na wɔsɛee m’apam, mo akyiwadeɛ nyinaa soɔ,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> nanso moanyɛ m’akronkronneɛ no ho adwuma no, na mmom mode mo ara mo nnipa asisi me kronkronbea hɔ adwuma no soɔ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Ɔnanani biara a ɔyɛ akoma mu momonotoni ne honam mu momonotoni nnhyɛne me kronkronbea, ananafoɔ a ɛwɔ Israelfoɔ mu nyinaa mu,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> na mpo Lewifoɔ a wɔafiri me ho kɔ akyirikyirie, Israel fom a wɔfomm firii me nkyɛn kɔdii wɔn abosom akyire no mu no, wɔn mpo wɔbɛsoa wɔn amumuyɛ;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> na wɔbɛyɛ me kronkronbea asomfo ayɛ asɔrefie no apono ano ahwɛfoɔ, na wɔasom asɔrefie no mu. Wɔn na wɔbɛbɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne ɔkum afɔdeɛ ama ɔman no, na wɔn ara na wɔbɛgyina wɔn anim asom wɔn.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ɛsiane sɛ wɔasom wɔn, wɔn abosom anim na wɔadanedane Israel fie amumuyɛ suntidua nti, mama me nsa so atia wɔn, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie, sɛ wɔnsoa wɔn amumuyɛ;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> na wɔntwe mmpini me mmmɛyɛ asɔfodwuma mmma me, na wɔmmmɛn m’akronkronneɛ no biara mmma m’akronkronneɛ mu akronkronneɛ ho, na wɔnsoa wɔn ahohora ne wɔn akyiwadeɛ a wɔyɛeɛ no.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Nanso mede asɔrefie no ho adwuma no bɛhyɛ wɔn nsa, ɛho som ne adeɛ biara a wɔyɛ wɔ mu no nyinaa mu.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na asɔfoɔ Lewifoɔ, Sadok mma a wɔyɛ kronkronbea hɔ adwuma, berɛ a Israelfoɔ firii me nkyɛn kɔfomm kwan no, wɔn deɛ, wɔbɛbɛn me, asom me, na wɔagyina m’anim de sradeɛ ne mogya abrɛ me, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> wɔn na wɔbɛhyɛne me kronkronbea hɔ, na wɔn na wɔbɛbɛn me pono ho abɛsom me, na wɔayɛ me som adwuma no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na sɛ wɔreba aponkɛseɛ a ɛwɔ abannwa a ɛwɔ mu no ho a, wɔnhyehyɛ nwera ntadeɛ, na kuntutam biara nnka wɔn ho berɛ a wɔresom emu fam abannwa no, aponkɛseɛ no mu ne efie no mu.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Wɔmfa nwera ahyehyɛdeɛ mmobɔ wɔn ti, a nwera pieto nhyehyɛ wɔn; wɔmmfa biribiara a ɛbɛma wɔafiri fifire mmmɔ abɔsoɔ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na wɔrefiri adi afiri abannwa no so akɔ ɔman no nkyɛn a, wɔnyiyi ntadeɛ a wɔhyɛ de someɛ no, mfa ngu kronkronbea adammoa no mu, na wɔnhyehyɛ ntadeɛ afoforɔ, na wɔamfa wɔn ntadeɛ kronkronyɛ no ankɔ nkurɔfoɔ no mu.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na wɔnnyiyi wɔn ti, nso wɔnnsi atimum, bubuo nko na wɔmmubu wɔn tiri soɔ.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na bobesa nso ɔsɔfoɔ biara nnnom berɛ a wɔrehyɛne abannwa a ɛwɔ mu no soɔ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Nanso wɔmmfa okunafoɔ ne deɛ wɔako no nnware, na mmom wɔmfa Israel fie asefoɔ mu mmammaa, anaa okunafoɔ a ɔyɛ ɔsɔfoɔ bi kunafoɔ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na wɔnkyerɛ me man akronkronneɛ ne deɛ abuo so ntam nsonsonoeɛ, na wɔmma wɔnhunu deɛ ɛho wɔ fi ne deɛ ɛho teɛ ntam nsonsonoeɛ.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na akameakamesɛm nso, wɔn ara na wɔnnyina hɔ mmu ho atɛn, m’atemmudeɛ so na wɔmmu atɛn, na wɔnhwɛ me mmara ahodoɔ ne m’ahyɛdeɛ, m’afahyɛ nyinaa mu, na wɔnyɛ me home nna kronkron.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Na wɔnnkɔ funu bi ho nnkɔgu wɔn ho fi, gye agya ne ɛna ne ɔbabanin ne ɔbabaa ne onuabarima ne onuabaa a ɔnnya nyɛɛ ɔbarima deɛ ho na wɔwɔ ho kwan sɛ wɔma wɔn ho kum.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Na ɔdwira ne ho wie a, wɔnkan nnanson mma no,",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> na ɛda a ɔrehyɛne kronkronbea akɔ emu fam abannwa so akɔsom kronkronbea no, ɔmfa ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ mmra, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Na deɛ ɛbɛyɛ wɔn agyapadeɛ deɛ, mene wɔn agyapadeɛ, na mommma wɔn kyɛfa bi wɔ Israel mu, mene wɔn kyɛfa.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Aduane afɔdeɛ ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne asodie ho afɔdeɛ no, wɔn ara na wɔnnie, na Israel mu ahyiradeɛ nyinaa nyɛ wɔn deɛ.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na nnoɔma nyinaa mu aba a ɛdi kan mfitiaseɛ no, ne nnoɔma nyinaa mu mmasoɔ afɔrebɔdeɛ a moma soɔ nyinaa no, ɛnyɛ asɔfoɔ no dea; na mo mmɔre mu deɛ ɛdi kan no, momfa mma ɔsɔfoɔ, na nhyira mmra mo fie.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Abɔfono biara ne deɛ wɔatete ne mu, nnomaa ne mmoa mu no, asɔfoɔ nnni."
		},
		"45": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na sɛ moretwe asase no so ntonto de akyɛ agyapadeɛ a, monyi so mmasoɔ afɔrebɔdeɛ asase no mu akronkronneɛ mma AWURADE; ne ntwemu nyɛ susuo basafa mpem dummienu ne ahanum, na ne trɛ yɛ mpem du; wɔbɛfrɛ no asase kronkron n’ahyeɛ nyinaa mu.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Yei mu basafa ahanu aduonum a ɛyɛ ahinanan hyia no nyɛ kronkronbea no deɛ, na basafa aduonu nnum nyɛ ne mmoa adidibea nsase ntwa ho nhyia.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na asase a moasusuo no ara mu, susu ntwemu basafa mpem dummienu ne ahanum, na ne trɛ yɛ mpem du, na yei mu na kronkronbea no, akronkronneɛ mu kronkron no ntena.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Asase no mu akronkronneɛ ne no, ɛnyɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔsom kronkronbea a wɔpinkyɛ bɛsom AWURADE no deɛ, na ɛnyɛ wɔn adan sisibea ne kronkronbea ho kronkronbea.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ntwemu basafa mpem dummienu ne ahanum no no, ne trɛ mu yɛ mpem nnum no nyɛ Lewifoɔ a wɔyɛ asɔrefie no mu asomfo deɛ, na ɛnyɛ wɔn kyɛfa, nkuro a wɔbɛtena mu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Nanso monyi kuro no kyɛfa a ne trɛ yɛ basafa mpem mmienu ne ahanum na ne ntwemu yɛ basafa mpem dummienu ne ahanum, kronkronbea mmasoɔ afɔrebɔdeɛ no ho, ɛnyɛ Israel fie nyinaa dea.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Na ɔberempɔn no deɛ no nna kronkronbea no mmasoɔ afɔrebɔdeɛ ne kuro no kyɛfa no nkyɛn mu ɛha ne ɛha, kronkronbea no mmasoɔ afɔrebɔdeɛ ne kuro no kyɛfa no anim, atɔeɛ fam, de rekɔ apueeɛ, ntwemu ne mmusuakuo no kyɛfa no mmaako mmaako deɛ no nsɛ, ɛmfiri atɔeɛ hyeɛ so nkɔ apueeɛ hyeɛ so;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> asase no na ɛnyɛ ne kyɛfa Israel mu, na m’aberempɔn anhyɛ me man so bio; na wɔmfa asase no mma Israel fie sɛdeɛ wɔn mmusuakuo no teɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Momma no nnɔɔso mma mo, Israel aberempɔn, monnyae amimdie ne nhyɛsoɔ, na monyɛ atemmudeɛ ne ateneneedeɛ, monnyae sɛ monam ɔhyɛ so gye nsase firi me nkurɔfoɔ hɔ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Monnya nsania pa ne efa pa ne bat pa.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Efa ne bat nsusuiɛ nyɛ baako, na efa nso nyɛ homer nkyɛmu du mu baako. Ne nsusuiɛ nyɛ sɛ homer baako.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na dwetɛbena nyɛ gera aduonu. Nnwetɛbena aduonu, nnwetɛbena aduonu nnum ne nnwetɛbena dunum nyɛ mo mina.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Yei ne mmasoɔ afɔrebɔdeɛ a momma soɔ; Ayuo homer mu efa nkyɛmu nsia mu baako ne atokoɔ homer mu efa nkyɛmu nsia mu baako.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na ngo ho ahyɛdeɛ nie: Ngo bat no, bat nkyɛmu du mu baako na momma mfiri susukoraa a ɛne homer a ɛdi bat du no mu; na bat du na ɛyɛ homer;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na odwan baako a ɔfiri nnwankuo mu, nnwan ahanu a ɛwɔ Israel adidibea a ɛhɔ afɔ no mu, na ɛnyɛ aduane afɔdeɛ ne ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ, na wɔmfa mpata mma wɔn, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Asase no so nnipa nyinaa mfa mmasoɔ afɔrebɔdeɛ yi mma Israel mu berempɔn no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɛyɛ ɔberempɔn no asɛdeɛ sɛ ɔmma ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ, aduane afɔdeɛ ne ahwiesa, nnapɔnna ne abosome foforɔ ne home nna wɔ Israel fie afahyɛ a wɔhyehyɛ nyinaa mu, ɔno ara na ɔmma bɔne ho afɔdeɛ, ne ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ a wɔde pata ma Israel fie no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Bosome a ɛdi kan no, da a ɛdi kan no, fa nantwiburuwa a ɔnni dɛm yi kronkronbea no ho bɔne.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɔsɔfoɔ no mfa bɔne ho afɔdeɛ mogya no bi nkeka asɔrefie no aponnwa ne afɔrebukyia no faferɛ no ntweaso nnan ne abannwa a ɛwɔ mu no ponkɛseɛ no aponnwa ho.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na bosome no da a ɛtɔ so nson no, yɛ saa ara, ma deɛ wafom anibiannasoɔ ne ne ntetekwaasɛm soɔ no nti, na momfa mpata mma efie no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bosome a ɛdi kan no da a ɛtɔ so dunan no monni Twam Afahyɛ no. Monnni paanoo a ɛntuiɛ nnanson.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɔberempɔn no mfa nantwinini bi, da no ara, mmɔ ɔno ara ne asase no so man nyinaa ho bɔne afɔdeɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na afahyɛ nnanson no nyinaa, ɔmmɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ mma AWURADE, anantwinini nson ne adwennini nson a ɛdɛm nni wɔn ho, nna nson no mu da biara, ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ nso, ɔpapo baako;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na ɔmma aduane afɔdeɛ nso, nantwie baako ne aduane efa baako, ne odwennini baako ne aduane efa baako, na ngo susutoa baako nka aduane efa baako ho.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bosome a ɛtɔ so nson da a ɛtɔ so dunum no, afahyɛ no mu no, ɔnyɛ sei ara nnanson, sɛ bɔne ho afɔdeɛ ne ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne aduane afɔdeɛ ne ngo nso deɛ."
		},
		"46": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Abannwa ponkɛseɛ a ɛhwɛ apueeɛ no, wɔnto mu adwumayɛ nna nsia no nyinaa, na homeda no deɛ, wɔnhini, na bosome foforɔ da no nso, wɔnhini.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔberempɔn no mfiri akyire, mfa ntwonoo kwan pono so mmɛgyina ɛpono kɛseɛ no aponnwa ho; na asɔfoɔ no mmɔ ne hyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne n’asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ, na ɔnkoto nsɔre, ɛpono kɛseɛ no aponnwa ho, na ɔmfiri adi, na ɛpono kɛseɛ no deɛ, wɔnnto mu kɔsi anwummerɛ.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Na asase no so nnipa no nso nkoto nsɔre ɛpono kɛseɛ no ano, home nna ne abosome foforɔ mu, AWURADE anim.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ a ɔberempɔn no mfa mmrɛ AWURADE no nie: Homeda, nnwanten nsia a wɔnni dɛm ne odwennini a ne ho nni dɛm;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ne aduane afɔdeɛ: Odwennini no deɛ, efa ne nnwanten no ho aduane afɔdeɛ a ne nsa bɛso soɔ ne ngo susutoa a ɛka efa no ho.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na bosome foforɔ da no: Nantwiburuwa a ɔnni dɛm ne nnwanten nsia ne odwennini baako a wɔnni dɛm,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ne nantwinini no ho efa ne odwennini no ho efa na ɔmfa nyɛ aduane afɔdeɛ ne nnwanten no deɛ, sɛdeɛ ne nsa bɛso soɔ, ne ngo susutoa a ɛka efa ho.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na sɛ ɔberempɔn no rebɛhyɛne mu a, ɔmfa ɛpono kɛseɛ no ntwonoo kwan so nkɔ mu, na ɔmfa hɔ ara mfiri adi.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na sɛ asase no so nnipa no reba AWURADE anim, afahyɛ no mu a, deɛ ɔfa atifi fam ponkɛseɛ no kwan so ba mu bɛsɔreɛ no, ɔmfa anafoɔ fam ponkɛseɛ no kwan so mfiri adi, na deɛ ɔfa anafoɔ fam ponkɛseɛ ano ba mu no, ɔmfa atifi fam ponkɛseɛ no ano mfiri adi; ɔnnsan mmfa ɛpono kɛseɛ a ɔfaa mu baa mu no mu mmfiri adi, na ɔnkɔ n’anim tee mfiri adi.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na ɔberempɔn no, sɛ wɔreba mu a, ɔmfra wɔn mu mmra mu, na sɛ wɔrefiri adi a, ɔne wɔn mfiri adi.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Na nnapɔnna ne afahyɛ no mu aduane afɔdeɛ nyɛ nantwinini ne aduane efa, ne odwennini ne aduane efa, ne nnwanten ho deɛ ne nsa bɛso soɔ, ne aduane efa ho ngo susutoa.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na sɛ ɔberempɔn no rebɛbɔ ayamyi hyeɛ afɔdeɛ anaa ayamyɛ asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ ama AWURADE a, ɛnneɛ wɔnhini no ɛpono kɛseɛ a ɛhwɛ apueeɛ no, na ɔmmɔ ne hyeɛ afɔdeɛ ne n’asomdwoeɛ afɔdeɛ, sɛdeɛ ɔyɛ no homeda no, na ɔmfiri adi; na n’adifire akyiri no, wɔnto ɛpono kɛseɛ no mu.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na odwanten a wadi afe a ɔnni dɛm na fa bɔ ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ ma AWURADE; anɔpa anɔpa na bɔ;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na siesie ɛho aduane afɔdeɛ daa anɔpa, efa nkyɛmu nsia mu baako, ne ngo susutoa nkyɛmu mmiɛnsa mu baako, na wɔmfa mfɔre esiam no na ɛnyɛ aduane afɔdeɛ mma AWURADE; ɛnyɛ daa ahyɛdeɛ daa;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> na monsiesie odwanten no, ne aduane afɔdeɛ ne ngo no daa anɔpa: Ɛyɛ daa ɔhyeɛ afɔdeɛ.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Sɛ ɔberempɔn no de n’agyapadeɛ no bi kyɛ ne mma no bi a, ɛyɛ ne mma no deɛ, wɔn agyapadeɛ mu kyɛfa ne no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na sɛ ɔde n’agyapadeɛ no bi kyɛ ne nkoa mu bi a, ɛnneɛ ɛnyɛ akoa no deɛ nkɔsi ahofadie afe no so, na ɛnsane nkɔyɛ ɔberempɔn no deɛ bio, ɛyɛ ɔno ara agyapadeɛ, ne mma na ɛnyɛ wɔn deɛ.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Nanso ɔberempɔn no mmfa ɔmanfoɔ no agyapadeɛ bi, mmpam wɔn mfiri wɔn kyɛfa mu; ɔno ara ne kyɛfa no bi na ɔmfa mma ne mma na wɔnnie, deɛ ɛbɛyɛ na wɔampansam me man mu onipa biara amfiri n’agyapadeɛ soɔ.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me faa ɔkwan a ɛda ɛpono kɛseɛ no nhyɛnmu no so kɔɔ adammoa kronkron a ɛyɛ asɔfoɔ dea, a ɛhwɛ atifi fam no ano, na hwɛ, afa bi wɔ hɔ, atɔeɛ fam, akyire nohoa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Ɛha ne faako a asɔfoɔ no bɛnoa asodie ho afɔdeɛ ne bɔne ho afɔdeɛ no, na wɔatoto aduane afɔdeɛ no, na wɔamfa amfiri adi ankɔ abannwa a ɛwɔ ho no so ankɔte ɔman no ho.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me firii adi baa abannwa a ɛwɔ ho no soɔ, na ɔmaa mesene kɔɔ abannwa no ntweaso nnan no ho, na hwɛ, atuntuma bi wɔ abannwa no biara ntweaso.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Abannwa no ntwea nnan no mu na ntuntuma a wɔabram ho wowɔ a ne ntwemu yɛ basafa aduonu na ne trɛ yɛ basafa dunum, ntweaso ntutuma nnan no nyinaa nsusuiɛ yɛ baako.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na bamma bi twa ntuntuma nnan no mu hyia twan, na wɔayeyɛ mmukyia, mmamma no ase, de atwa ho ahyia.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Yeinom ne aduanenoa adan a efie no mu asomfo no nnoa ɔmanfoɔ no kum afɔdeɛ wɔ hɔ."
		},
		"47": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ɛnna ɔde me sane baa asɔredan no pono ano, na hwɛ, nsuo firi asɔredan no aponnwa ase resene kɔ apueeɛ fam, (na asɔredan no anim hwɛ apueeɛ), na nsuo no resiane wɔ aseɛ, asɔredan no nifa so, afɔrebukyia no anafoɔ fam.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na ɔde me nam atifi fam ponkɛseɛ no kwan so firii adi, na ɔde me faa mfikyikwan no so, konton baa anim ponkɛseɛ a ɛhwɛ apueeɛ no kwan no so, na hwɛ, na nsuo firi nifa so resene.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ɔbarima no firi kɔɔ apueeɛ no, na susuhoma kura ne nsamu, na ɔsusuu basafa ahanum, na ɔde me twaa nsuo no, nsuo a ɛka nanpɔ soɔ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Na ɔsusuu ahanum, na ɔde me twaa nsuo no, nsuo a ɛka nankoroma. Na ɔsusuu ahanum, na ɔde me twae, nsuo a ɛka asene mu.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Na ɔsusuu ahanum, na ɛyɛ nsuo a mantumi mantwa, ɛfiri sɛ nsuo no mu dɔ a wɔboro, ayɛ sɛ nsuo a wɔntumi ntwa.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Onipa ba woahunu anaa? Na ɔde me nam asuo no ano sane bae,",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na mesane bae, na hwɛ, nnua bebree pa wɔ asuo no ano, ɛha ne ɛha.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na ɔka kyerɛɛ me sɛ: Nsuo yi firi sene kɔ apueeɛ fam kanko no mu, na ɛsiane kɔ mpaperɛ no so. Ɛpo mu na nsuo a ɛfiri sene yi korɔ, na asa nsuo no yadeɛ.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Na ɔkra teasefoɔ biara a ɛkeka ne ho, baabiara a asuo a ɛboro soɔ yi bɛkɔ hɔ no bɛnya nkwa na emu nam bɛdɔɔso bebree pa ara, ɛfiri sɛ nsuo yi bɛkɔ hɔ, na wɔasa po no nsuo yadeɛ, na nnoɔma nyinaa anya nkwa, deɛ asuo no korɔ biara.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na apofofoɔ bɛgyina ɛpo no so, ɛfiri En-gedi kɔsi En-eglaim bɛyɛ asau hatabea. Emu mpataa bɛyɛ ahodoɔ, sɛ ɛpo kɛseɛ mu nam bebree pa ara.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> N’aforɔ ne n’atɛkyɛ deɛ, wɔrensa, wɔbɛgya de ayɛ nkyene.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Na asuo no nsunoa ha ne ha na nnua a wɔdie ahodoɔ nyinaa bɛfiri; n’ahahan rempo, na n’aba rensa, ɛbɛso n’abosome mu, ɛfiri sɛ ne nsuo no, kronkronbea na ɛfiri sene. Na n’aba bɛyɛ aduane, na n’ahahan ayɛ aduro.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Sɛ AWURADE Nyankopɔn seɛ nie: Yei ne ɛhyeɛ a mode bɛkyɛ asase no ama Israel mmusuakuo dummienu no adi soɔ; Yosef deɛ nyɛ nhoma mmienu;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> na monkyɛ nni so mma obiara deɛ nyɛ sɛ ne nua deɛ, ɛfiri sɛ ɛho na maka ntam sɛ mede bɛma mo agyanom no; na asase yi bɛda hɔ ama mo, na moadi so.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na asase no hyeɛ nie: Ano a ɛda atifi fam: Ɛfiri ɛpo kɛseɛ no ano, fa Hetlon kwan a ɛkɔ Sedad no so,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hamat, Berota, Sibraim (a ɛda Damasko ne Hamat hyeɛ ntam no), Haser-hatikon a ɛda Hauran hyeɛ ho no.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ no firi ɛpo no ano kɔ Hasar-Enon, Damasko hyeɛ so, na atifi fam deɛ, ɛhyeɛ a ɛda atifi fam ne Hamat; na ɛne ano a ɛdi atifi fam no.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ a ɛda apueeɛ fam ne Yordan a ɛwɔ Hauran ne Damasko ne Gilead ɛne Israel asase ntam no, monsusu mfiri ɛhyeɛ no so nkɔ apueeɛ po no ano; na ɛne ɛhyeɛ a ɛdi apueeɛ fam no.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ a ɛda anafoɔ fam hwɛ anafoɔ no: Ɛfiri Tamar kɔ Meribat-kades nsuo a ɛnam Misraim subonhwa no ano kɔduru ɛpo kɛseɛ no ano; na ɛne ɛhyeɛ a ɛhwɛ nifa, anafoɔ fam no.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Na ɛhyeɛ a ɛda atɔeɛ fam ne ɛpo kɛseɛ no firi ɛhyeɛ no ano ara kɔsi Hamat ntentensoɔ; ɛne ɛhyeɛ a ɛdi atɔeɛ no.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na monkyɛ asase yi mu mfa, sɛdeɛ Israel mmusuakuo no teɛ.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ntonto so na monkyɛ asase no mfa nni soɔ, mo ne ananafoɔ a wɔabɛyɛ mo mu ahɔhoɔ a mo mu wɔawowo mma no, na wɔnyɛ mo sɛ wɔn a wɔwoo wɔn Israel mma mu, wɔne mo mmɔ agyapadeɛ so ntonto, Israel mmusuakuo no mu;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> na abusuakuo ko a ɔnanani bi abɛyɛ mu hɔhoɔ no, ɛhɔ ara na momma no n’agyapadeɛ, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie."
		},
		"48": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Na yeinom ne mmusuakuo no din: Ɛfiri atifi fam hyeɛ no so, Hetlon kwan nkyɛn mu a ɛrekɔ Hamat, Hasar-Enan, Damasko hyeɛ so, (deɛ ɛhwɛ atifi fam wɔ Hamat nkyɛn mu), na wɔnnya ano apueeɛ ne atɔeɛ, ɛno ne Dan, homa baako.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Na deɛ ɛdi Dan hyeɛ soɔ ɛfiri apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Aser deɛ, baako;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Aser hyeɛ soɔ firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Naftali deɛ, baako;",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Naftali hyeɛ soɔ firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Manase deɛ, baako;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Manase hyeɛ soɔ firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Efraim deɛ, baako;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Efraim hyeɛ soɔ firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Ruben deɛ, baako;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Ruben hyeɛ soɔ firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Yuda deɛ, baako.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Na deɛ ɛdi Yuda hyeɛ soɔ firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no nyɛ mmasoɔ asase a momma soɔ no, ne trɛ nyɛ basafa mpem dummienu ne ahanum. Na ne ntwemu nyɛ sɛ kyɛfa no bi mfiri apueeɛ nkɔsi atɔeɛ, na kronkronbea no nna mfimfini.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Mmasoɔ asase a monyi mma AWURADE no ntwemu nie: Susuo basafa mpem dummienu ne ahanum, na ne trɛ yɛ mpem du.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Na wɔn a mmasoɔ asase kronkron yi nyɛ wɔn deɛ nie: Asɔfoɔ deɛ, atifi fam basafa mpem dummienu ne ahanum, atɔeɛ fam trɛ nyɛ mpem nnum, apueeɛ fam trɛ mpem nnum, na anafoɔ fam ntwemu mpem dummienu ne ahanum, na AWURADE kronkronbea no nna mfimfini.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ɛnyɛ asɔfoɔ a wɔayɛ wɔn kronkron, Sadok mma mu, a wɔayɛ me som adwuma no a wɔamfom, Israelfoɔ fom no mu, sɛdeɛ Lewifoɔ no fomeeɛ no,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> na wɔnnya asase no mmasoɔ mu deɛ wɔama soɔ, akronkronneɛ mu adekronkron, Lewifoɔ no hyeɛ ho.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Na Lewifoɔ no nnya asɔfoɔ hyeɛ no nkyɛn mu ntwemu mpem dummienu ne ahanum na ne trɛ yɛ mpem nnum; ntwemu nyinaa nyɛ mpem dummienu ne ahanum, na ne trɛ nyɛ mpem nnum.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Na wɔnntɔn mu bi, na wɔnnsesa, na wɔnnane asase no adeɛ a ɛdi kan no mmma, na ɛyɛ kronkron ma AWURADE.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Na basafa mpem mmienu ahanum a ɛka ne trɛ mu, mpem dummienu ne ahanum no mu no nyɛ anihumafoɔ adeɛ mma kuro no sɛ wɔn tenabea ne ɛho asase, na kuro no nna mfimfini.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Na ne nsusuiɛ nie: Atifi fam ano: Basafa mpem mmienu ahanu aduonum; na anafoɔ fam ano: Mpem mmienu ahanu ne aduonum; na apueeɛ ano: Mpem mmienu ahanu ne aduonum; na atɔeɛ fam ano: Mpem mmienu ahanu ne aduonum.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Na kuro no nnya mmoa adidibea nsase: Basafa ɔha ne aduonu nnum atifi fam, ne anafoɔ, basafa ɔha ne aduonu nnum, ne atɔeɛ fam basafa ɔha ne aduonu nnum.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Na deɛ aka wɔ mmasoɔ asase kronkron no nkyɛn mu, apueeɛ no, basafa mpem nnum ne atɔeɛ basafa mpem nnum no, ɛnna mmasoɔ asase kronkron no nkyɛn mu na ne nnɔbaeɛ nyɛ kuro no adwumayɛfoɔ aduane;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> na kuro no adwumayɛfoɔ deɛ, wɔbɛfiri Israel mmusuakuo nyinaa mu abɛyɛ so adwuma.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Mmasoɔ asase no nyinaa yɛ basafa mpem dummienu ahanum, mmasoɔ asase kronkron no nyɛ ahinanan na ɛnka kuro no deɛ no ho.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Na nkaeɛ no nyɛ ɔberempɔn no deɛ, mmasoɔ asase kronkron ne kuro no deɛ no ho, ɛha ne ɛha, deɛ ɛda mmasoɔ asase no ho yɛ basafa mpem dummienu ne ahanum no ho kɔsi apueeɛ hyeɛ so, ne atɔeɛ fam deɛ a ɛda mpem dummienu ne ahanum no ho kɔsi atɔeɛ hyeɛ so ma no sesɛ mmusuakuo no kyɛfa soɔ no, ɛnyɛ ɔberempɔn no deɛ, na mmasoɔ asase kronkron ne asɔrefie no kronkronbea no nna ntam.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Na ɛfiri Lewifoɔ no kyɛfa ne kuro no kyɛfa a ɛda ɔberempɔn no deɛ no ntam no soɔ, deɛ ɛda Yuda hyeɛ ne Benyamin hyeɛ ntam no nyɛ ɔberempɔn no deɛ.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na mmusuakuo a aka no deɛ nie: Ɛfiri apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no, Benyamin deɛ, baako;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Benyamin hyeɛ soɔ firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Simeon deɛ, baako;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Simeon hyeɛ so firi apueeɛ de rekorɔ no: Isakar deɛ, baako;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Isakar hyeɛ soɔ firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Sebulon deɛ, baako;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> na deɛ ɛdi Sebulon hyeɛ so firi apueeɛ de kɔ atɔeɛ no: Gad deɛ, baako;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> na Gad hyeɛ a ɛwɔ anafoɔ fam a ɛkyerɛ nifa no so hyeɛ no mfiri Tamar mfa ɔham nsuo a ɛwɔ Kades ne Misraim subonhwa no nkɔsi Ɛpo Kɛseɛ no ano.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Yei ne asase a momfa ntonto nkyɛ mma Israel mmusuakuo na wɔnni soɔ no, na yeinom ne wɔn kyɛfa, AWURADE Nyankopɔn asɛm nie.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Na yeinom ne kuro no ho apono: Atifi fam deɛ no nsusuiɛ yɛ basafa mpem mmienu ahanu aduonum;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> na kuro no aponkɛseɛ no wowɔ Israel mmusuakuo no din: Atifi fam aponkɛseɛ mmiɛnsa: Ruben ponkɛseɛ, baako; Yuda ponkɛseɛ, baako; Lewi ponkɛseɛ, baako.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Na apueeɛ fam deɛ no: Basafa mpem mmienu ahanu aduonum ne aponkɛseɛ mmiɛnsa: Yosef ponkɛseɛ, baako; Benyamin ponkɛseɛ baako, ne Dan ponkɛseɛ no.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Na anafoɔ fam deɛ no nsusuiɛ: Basafa mpem mmienu ahanu ne aduonum ne aponkɛseɛ mmiɛnsa: Simeon ponkɛseɛ, baako; Isakar ponkɛseɛ, baako; Sebulon ponkɛseɛ, baako.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Atɔeɛ fam deɛ no: Basafa mpemnan ahanum, n’aponkɛseɛ mmiɛnsa: Gad ponkɛseɛ, baako; Aser ponkɛseɛ, baako, ne Naftali ponkɛseɛ no.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Deɛ ɛtwa ho hyia yɛ basafa mpem nkron. Na ɛfiri da no, kuro no din ne: AWURADE wɔ hɔ."
		}
	}
};
